\cf2 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng n\u259 m cu\u7889 i c\u7845 p ba t\u7845 t c\u7843  t\u7853 p trung v\'e0o thi c\u7917  r\u7891 i li\'ean hoan v\'e0 nh\u7919 ng c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n t\'ecnh c\u7843 m tu\u7893 i h\u7885 c tr\'f2.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\'edch nhau m\u7897 t ch\'fat. Bu\u7893 i \u273 \'f3, \u7903  c\'e1i qu\'e1n C\'e2y D\u7915 a v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i v\u7899 i nhau th\u7911  th\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7853 u\'85 th\'edch t\u7899  th\u7853 t h\u7843 ? C\'f3 l\u7915 a t\'ecnh t\u7899  hay kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i kh\u7869  ng\u7891 i s\'e1t h\u417 n, m\u7841 nh d\u7841 n \u273 \u432 a tay vu\u7889 t l\u7845 y m\'e1i t\'f3c du\u7895 i th\u7859 ng th\u417 m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch th\uc0\u7853 t ch\u7913  l\u7915 a t\'ecnh l\'e0m g\'ec? Kh\'f4ng tin t\u7899  \'e0 m\'e0 n\'f3i t\u7899  l\u7915 a t\'ecnh. H\u7913  nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t \u273 \'e1ng gh\'e9t th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\u361 ng n\u7883 u kh\u7869  kh\u7869  ng\u7843  \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gh\'e9t m\'e0 c\'f2n k\'eau th\'edch th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gh\'e9t t\uc0\u7897 i d\'e1m b\u7843 o t\u7899  l\u7915 a t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i nhau c\'e2u g\'ec ch\u7881  ng\u7891 i s\'e1t l\u7841 i m\'e0 th\'f4i. M\'f9i n\u432 \u7899 c hoa thoang tho\u7843 ng c\'f9ng v\u7899 i m\'f9i \'e1o kho\'e1c th\u417 m n\u7891 ng qu\u7879 n v\'e0o v\u7899 i nhau t\u7841 o th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng m\'e0 c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \u7871 n m\'e3i sau n\'e0y t\'f4i v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng qu\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'85\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\'ean hoan xong th\'ec ch\'fang t\'f4i h\'f2 nhau c\uc0\u7843  l\u361  \u273 \u7841 p xe ra bi\u7875 n ch\u417 i r\u7891 i ch\u7909 p \u7843 nh. H\u7891 i \u273 \'f3 nh\u7919 ng n\u259 m hai ngh\'ecn th\'ec c\'f3 c\'e1i m\'e1y \u7843 nh du l\u7883 ch l\'e0 s\'e0nh \u273 i\u7879 u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7909 p \u7843 nh \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u th\'ec ch\'fang t\'f4i \u273 \u7841 p xe v\u7873 . Ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7857 ng sau Qu\u7923 nh d\u7909 i nh\u7865  m\'e1 v\'e0o l\u432 ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  l\'e0 ch\u7859 ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7863 p nhau n\u7919 a r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t thi \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c c\'f2n c\'f3 \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\u432 \u417 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Lo c\'e1i g\'ec, nh\'e0 g\uc0\u7847 n nhau c\'e1ch c\'f3 con ph\u7889  th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p nhau \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f2n n\u7871 u thi th\'ec c\u361 ng \u7903  c\'e1i Th\u7911  \u272 \'f4 th\'f4i, \u273 i t\'ed l\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n, m\u7845 y anh ch\u7883  kh\'f3a tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u361 ng th\u7871  c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u. Kh\'e9o m\'e0 l\'ean \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u7903  chung \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i c\'e2u \u7903  chung th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 th\u7909 i t\'f4i m\u7897 t qu\u7843  r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai cho \uc0\u7903  chung m\'e0 \u7903  chung!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y l\'e0 n\'f3i th\u7871  nh\u7881  ch\u7913  ch\u7855 c g\'ec Minh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7895  c\u417  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u297 u m\'f4i r\u7891 i ngu\'fdt d\'e0i t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m h\u7885 c th\u7871  th\'ec ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u7895 . Th\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0 \u273 i xem phim \u273 \'e3 \u273 i, h\'f4m nay Qu\u7923 nh th\'edch xem phim!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c !\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a \u273 \u7841 p xe \u273 \u7871 n r\u7841 p chi\u7871 u phim r\u7891 i xem \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n m\u432 \u7901 i r\u432 \u7905 i t\u7889 i. V\u7915 a xem phim t\'f4i v\u7915 a b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i ch\uc0\u7871 t v\u7873  mu\u7897 n th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f3 s\u7907  b\u7889  m\u7865  m\u7855 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng sao \uc0\u273 \'e2u, Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o b\u7889  m\u7865  r\u7891 i h\u417 n n\u7919 a b\u7889  m\u7865  Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng tho\u7843 i m\'e1i m\'e0, th\u7871  Minh kh\'f4ng s\u7907  b\u7883  m\u7855 ng \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Minh l\'e0 con trai s\uc0\u7907  g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a xem xong phim r\u7891 i v\u7873  nh\'e0. Tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i n\'ean c\'e1i ng\'f5 quanh co v\'e0o nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u7871 ch nh\'e1i k\'eau \u7897 p o\u7841 p su\u7889 t. Tuy c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng v\u7853 y th\'f4i nh\u432 ng nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng \u7903  qu\'ea m\'e0 \u7903  ch\u7895  n\'e0y th\'ec v\u7851 n th\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f3 v\'ec s\'e1t ngo\u7841 i \'f4.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng l\'e0 d\'e2n bu\'f4n v\u7843 i v\'f3c v\u7899 i qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng n\'ean nh\'e0 c\u7917 a x\'e2y c\u361 ng khang trang v\'e0 \u273 \u7865 p l\u7855 m. D\u7915 ng l\u7841 i \u7903  ng\'f4i nh\'e0 hai t\u7847 ng nh\u432 ng to r\u7897 ng v\'e0 ho\'e0nh tr\'e1ng l\u7855 m t\'f4i l\'ed nh\'ed b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\'e0o nh\'e0 \u273 i Minh v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i nheo m\u7855 t n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 ch\'e0o b\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  Qu\u7923 nh m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\'f3 v\uc0\u7867  s\u7907  s\u7907  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'f4ng c\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t c\'f3 v\u7867  s\u7907  s\u7907  k\'eca! Ch\'e1n ch\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i h\uc0\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec v\'e0o h\'ec h\'ec, v\'e0o ch\'e0o nh\u7841 c ph\u7909  nh\u7841 c m\u7851 u m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e1 t\'f4i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai l\'e0 nh\uc0\u7841 c ph\u7909  nh\u7841 c m\u7851 u, luy\'ean thuy\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i n\'e9 \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'fa \u273 \'e1 c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i v\'e0o c\'f9ng Qu\u7923 nh ch\'e0o ba m\u7865  Qu\u7923 nh m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng, n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n kho\u7843 ng m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'fat r\u7891 i t\'f4i xin ph\'e9p \u273 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 hai \u273 \u7913 a l\'ean m\u7841 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau m\u7897 t ch\'fat ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i di \u273 \u7897 ng m\'e0 li\'ean l\u7841 c.\
