\cf2 \cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau ng\uc0\u7891 i \u7903  nh\'e0, \u273 ang \u273 \u7883 nh chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891  \u273 i c\'e2u c\'e1 li\'ean hoan v\u7899 i m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng l\u7899 p kh\'e1c th\'ec tr\u7901 i \u273 \u7893  m\u432 a.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'e0 c\u417 n m\u432 a r\'e0o m\'f9a h\u7841 . N\'f3 to v\'e0 d\u7891 n d\u7853 p v\'f4 c\'f9ng. T\u7915 ng gi\u7885 t n\u432 \u7899 c n\u7863 ng tr\u297 u g\'f5 long toong tr\'ean c\'e1i m\'e1i t\'f4n l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch th\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng ti\u7871 ng s\u7845 m \'ec \'f9ng r\u7891 i tiea s\'e9t s\'e1ng l\'f2a l\u7841 i l\'f3e l\'ean v\u7909 t t\u7855 t. \u272 ang ngh\u297  th\u7847 m ki\u7875 u n\'e0y m\u432 a xong \u273 i b\u7855 t c\'e1 th\'edch l\u7855 m th\'ec c\'f3 \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i k\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7841 ch b\u7841 ch ch\u7841 y v\'e0o t\'f4i nh\u7845 c c\'e1i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e0n th\'ec c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Minh \uc0\u417 i qua nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u417  h\u417  tr\'eau\'94\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u432 a gi\'f3 th\u7871  n\'e0y t\u7921  d\u432 ng b\u7843 o sang l\'e0 sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u432 a gi\'f3 Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i s\u7907 .. kh\'f4ng m\u432 a th\'ec n\'f3i l\'e0m g\'ec.. th\'f4i sang v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i.. Qu\u7923 nh s\u7907  l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  \u7903  nh\'e0! S\u7907  c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 s\u7907 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ai \uc0\u7903  nh\'e0 \u273 \'e2u, c\'f3 m\u7895 i Qu\u7923 nh \u7903  nh\'e0 th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i s\u7907  ch\u7913 . Th\'f4i Minh qua nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec qua \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c c\'e1i \'e1o m\u432 a t\'f4i l\u7841 ch b\u7841 ch b\'ec b\'f5m \u273 \u7841 p xe qua nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh, \u273 \u7913 ng \u7903  ngo\'e0i c\'e1i c\u7893 ng s\u7855 t t\'f4i lanh run l\'ean g\u7885 i to. Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7843 y ch\'e2n s\'e1o qua c\'e1i s\'e2n loang lo\'e1ng n\u432 \u7899 c m\u432 a r\u7891 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a cho t\'f4i. V\u7915 a th\u7845 y m\u7863 t Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i vu\u7889 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u432 a l\u259 n d\'e0i tr\'ean m\u7863 t tr\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7899 i c\'f3 t\'ed m\u432 a \u273 \'e3 s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  \u273 \u7845 y! Th\'f4i v\'e0o \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7855 t xe d\u7921 ng v\'e0o g\'f3c s\'e2n r\u7891 i t\'f4i v\'e0o nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh, Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 t\'f3t v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 m\'e0 pha cho t\'f4i c\u7889 c s\'f4 c\'f4 la n\'f3ng m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y u\uc0\u7889 ng \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4\'85 c\uc0\u361 ng bi\u7871 t Minh th\'edch s\'f4 c\'f4 la n\'f3ng \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh e th\u7865 n c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau th\'ec ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 t ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i \u273 \u7905  l\u7845 y c\u7889 c s\'f4 c\'f4 la n\'f3ng r\u7891 i c\u7847 m l\u7845 y b\'e0n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh sau \u273 \'f3 ng\u7891 i c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7913 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n phi\u7871 m v\u7899 i nhau. M\'f9i n\u432 \u7899 c hoa th\u417 m n\u7891 ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0m tooit h\u7845 y th\'edch l\u7855 m, Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i s\'e1t v\'e0o t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  c\'f3 phim xem th\'ec th\'edch nh\u7881 , \'e0 Qu\u7923 nh th\u7845 y b\u7889  Qu\u7923 nh gi\u7845 u k\u297  m\u7897 t c\'e1i c\'e1i \u273 \u297 a d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'e0 \u273 \u7845 y, \u273 \u7875  Qu\u7923 nh t\'ecm l\'ean m\u7903  vi t\'ednh xem \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i quay l\uc0\u7841 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7905  \u273 \u297 a c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \'e2u, n\u7871 u xem Qu\u7923 nh bi\u7871 t ngay!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\u7889 i \u273 \u7845 y, m\'e0 n\u7871 u \u273 \u297 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n th\'ec c\'f3 xem kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 h\'ec h\'ec! Xem xem ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7841 y xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'e0 l\u7909 c l\u7885 i m\u7897 t l\'fac sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7847 m c\'e1i \u273 \u297 a ch\u7881  nghie m\u7895 i c\'e1i ti\'eau \u273 \u7873  l\'e0 \'93Xu\'e2n th\'ec\'94 r\u7891 i c\u7847 m l\'ean tr\'ean nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai h\'ed h\u7917 ng m\u7903  m\'e1y l\'ean coi th\'ec \u273 \'fang l\'e0 \u273 \u297 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7899 n th\u7853 t. T\'f4i th\'ec th\'edch xem c\'f2n Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec \u273 \u7887  \u7917 ng h\u7871 t c\u7843  hai m\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i c\uc0\u7843 nh di\u7877 n vi\'ean n\u7919  \u273 ang m\'fat c\u7863 c cho di\u7877 n vi\'ean nam th\'ec t\'f4i h\'ed h\u7917 ng b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh d\'e1m l\'e0m th\u7871  kia kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng? Nh\'ecn n\'f3 kinh b\uc0\u7887  x\u7915  l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kinh g\'ec m\'e0 kinh?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec n\'f3 to nh\uc0\u432  th\u7871  kia c\u7855 m v\'e0o h\u7885 ng th\'ec c\'f3 m\'e0 ngh\u7865 n ng\u7841 t th\u7903  m\'e0 ch\u7871 t \'e0? H\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\u7849 n b\u7849 n c\'e1i ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 b\u7849 n, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7843  l\'e0 hai di\u7877 n vi\'ean ch\'e2u \'c2u n\'ean hai c\'e1i b\u7897  ph\u7853 n c\u7911 a h\u7885  to th\u7853 t. Nh\'ecn di\u7877 n vi\'ean n\u7919  m\'fat m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'ec ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 t di\u7877 n Vi\'ean Nam m\'fat l\u7891 n. T\'f4i nh\'ecn c\'e1i l\u7891 n cong vieo kh\'f4ng m\u7897 t s\u7907 i l\'f4ng c\u7911 a di\u7877 n vi\'ean n\u7919  th\'ec n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y nh\'ecn k\'eca kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\uc0\u7907 i l\'f4ng n\'e0o c\u7843 , c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a h\u7887 i xong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7841 p t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i m\'e0 b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7887 i linh tinh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 hay! H\uc0\u7887 i th\u7853 t th\u7871  m\'e0 b\u7843 o h\u7887 i linh tinh l\'e0 sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho bi\uc0\u7871 t ! M\'e0 sao ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'f4ng nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec ch\uc0\u7855 c m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n b\'ean h\u7885  \'edt l\'f4ng, m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\u361 ng do h\u7885  t\u7849 y th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\'f4i, m\'e0 di\u7877 n vi\'ean vi\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec h\u7885  t\u7849 y th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7891 n \u273 \u7887  au tr\u7855 ng ph\u7889 p ch\u7843 y ra th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7855 n m\u7863 t l\u7841 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Khi\uc0\u7871 m n\u432 \u7899 c kinh th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i s\u7863 c s\u7909 a n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m, l\'fac m\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7871 m ch\u7855 c Qu\u7923 nh ra nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \u7845 m t\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i. Phim l\u7841 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7895  quan h\u7879  Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Eo \uc0\u417 i! Con c\u7863 c d\'e0i th\u7871  m\'e0 \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u7853 p v\'e0o b\'ean trong nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 co gi\'e3n th\'ec ng\uc0\u7853 p v\'e0o th\'f4i, h\u7885 c sinh h\u7885 c c\'f2n g\'ec, m\'e0 ti\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7885 c \u273 \'e2u nh\u7881 , to\'e0n ph\u7843 i ng\u7891 i ch\u417 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'fac n\'e3y v\uc0\u7851 n ch\u432 a tr\u7843  l\u7901 i l\'e0 c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u l\'f4ng hay kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7887  \u7917 ng m\'e1 n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913  sao, c\'f3 ph\u7843 i t\u7849 y \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau vui v\u7867  th\'ec \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean s\u7845 m \u273 \'e1nh c\'e1i \u7847 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i. Tia s\'e9t s\'e1ng l\'f2a r\u7841 ch ngang b\u7847 u tr\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh s\u7907  qu\'e1 \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y t\'f4i run l\u7849 y b\u7849 y n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Minh \uc0\u417 i Qu\u7923 nh s\u7907 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1 l\'ean tr\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\'e9t \uc0\u273 \'e1nh b\'ean ngo\'e0i tr\u7901 i ch\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i \u7903  trong nh\'e0 \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 s\u7907  c\u417  ch\u7913 . Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t nh\'e1t ch\u7871 t bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y th\'ec c\'e1i b\'f3ng \u273 i\u7879 n t\u7855 t ph\u7909 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, m\'e0n h\'ecnh m\'e1y t\'ednh \u273 en ng\'f2m. Ch\u7855 c tia s\'e9t v\u7915 a r\u7891 i l\'e0m h\u432  h\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng d\'e2y \u273 i\u7879 n n\'ean m\u7899 i b\u7883  c\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Trong b\'f3ng t\u7889 i \u273 \u7863 c qu\'e1nh, Qu\u7923 nh \'f4m s\'e1t l\u7845 y t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7921 \'85 d\u432 ng c\u7855 t \u273 i\u7879 n l\'e0m g\'ec th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 do s\'e9t \u273 \'e1nh tr\'fang \u273 \'e2u \u273 \'f3 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i t\'f4i v\u7915 a l\u7907 i d\u7909 ng m\'e0 \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i h\'edt h\'e0 m\'f9i th\u417 m thoang tho\u7843 ng t\u7915  ng\u432 \u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh t\u7887 a ra. T\'f4i mu\u7889 n tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 hay sao m\'e0 c\uc0\u7913  \'f4m \'ecnh th\u7871  n\'e0y, nh\'e0 c\'f3 n\u7871 n kh\'f4ng? Mang ra \u273 \'e2y \u273 \u7889 t \u273 i ch\u7913 , t\u7889 i th\'f9i l\'f9i th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec nh\'ecn th\u7845 y g\'ec \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  ng\u432 \u7907 ng khi t\'f4i b\u7843 o \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y t\'f4i nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i c\u361 ng kh\u7869  n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\'fdnh \uc0\u7907 .. hay xu\u7889 ng ph\'f2ng b\u7871 p v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec \u273 i c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh run run ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y r\u7891 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i b\u7871 p. Do ch\u432 a quen nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh l\u7855 m n\'ean \u273 i l\u7841 i h\u417 i kh\'f3 kh\u259 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat. \u272 \u7907 i l\u7845 y m\'e3i xong \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y c\'e2y n\u7871 n, Qu\u7923 nh ch\'e2m l\'ean r\u7891 i b\u7843 o t\'f4i mang l\'ean ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n khu\'f4n m\u7863 t \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u7917 ng h\u7891 ng n\'ean tr\'f4ng c\'e0ng xinh h\u417 n. Nh\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i m\u7873 m m\u7873 m l\u7841 i c\'e0ng th\'eam \u273 \'f3. M\'e1i t\'f3c c\'f3 m\u7845 y s\u7907 i t\'f3c l\u432 a th\u432 a x\'f5a xu\u7889 ng khi\'ean Qu\u7923 nh lung linh nh\u432  m\u7897 t n\'e0ng c\'f4ng ch\'faa v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\'e2y ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ra ng\u7855 m Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7863 t c\'f3 nh\u7885  \'e0 m\'e0 nh\'ecn kinh th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7885  m\'e0 xinh \u7845 y, d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n nh\'ecn xinh kinh khung.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i e th\u7865 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Khen th\uc0\u7853 t hay khen \u273 \'f9a \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 l\'fac n\'e0y m\'e0 c\'f2n khen \uc0\u273 \'f9a th\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u7913  ng\'e2y ng\u432 \u7901 i ra m\'e0 ng\u7855 m Qu\u7923 nh d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n lung linh. Ngo\'e0i tr\u7901 i m\u432 a m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to h\u417 n, gi\'f3 c\u361 ng m\u7841 nh h\u417 n, Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y ra kh\'e9p c\'e1i c\u7917 a th\'ec l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng s\u7845 m vang l\'ean l\'e0m Qu\u7923 nh co r\'fam l\u7841 i ch\u7841 y v\'e0o gh\'ec ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7907  th\u7871 ! T\u7841 nh \u273 i cho con nh\u7901  \'f4ng tr\u7901 i \u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u7873  h\u7873  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u432 a th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec c\'f2n l\'e2u m\u7899 i t\u7841 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\'e1! C\u7913  y\'ean t\'e2m l\'e0 h\u7871 t \u273 \'eam!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  s\u7907  b\u7887  x\u7915 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7907  c\'e1i g\'ec, th\'f4i Minh chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \'e1o m\u432 a v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7845 y t\'f4i b\u7843 o v\u7873  th\'ec gi\u7853 t th\'f3t m\'ecnh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u416  sao l\u7841 i v\u7873 ? \u7902  \u273 \'e2y v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7873  ch\u7913 , \u273 \'eam r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh s\u7907  l\u7855 m, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i, h\'f4m nay c\'f3 m\u7895 i m\'ecnh m\'ecnh Qu\u7923 nh \u7903  nh\'e0 th\'f4i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean c\'e0ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec \uc0\u7903  m\u7897 t m\'ecnh c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  sao!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh s\u7907  m\'e0 l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\u259 n m\u7863 t chu c\'e1i m\'f4i ra, nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u361 i chun chun tr\'f4ng c\'e0ng \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau. T\'f4i h\u7845 t h\'e0m h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  Minh \u7903  c\'f9ng Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7905  \u273 \'e8 Qu\u7923 nh ra l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec l\'e0m sao. B\'e2y gi\u7901  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u7903  nh\'e0 \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y, d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng n\'f3 n\u7893 i l\'ean th\'ec kh\'f4ng k\'ecm ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y th\'f4i ch\u7913  t\'f4i ngh\u297  m\'ecnh ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng d\'e1m l\'e0m g\'ec Qu\u7923 nh, h\u417 n n\u7919 a mu\u7889 n tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh xem \'fd c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\u7871  n\'e0o. Nghe t\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7853 y Qu\u7923 nh h\u7913  gi\u7899  c\'e1i n\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 m tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh xem, cho \u259 n \u273 \'f2n b\u7889  m\u7865  kh\'f4ng nh\u7853 n ra lu\'f4n \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m, ch\u7855 c g\'ec \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec m\'e0 d\u7885 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7889 ng tay v\'e0o n\u7841 nh Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  xem! \u272 \u7897 ng v\'e0o xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  th\'e1ch th\u7913 c nh\u432 ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o Qu\u7923 nh m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4i, ra v\u7867  mu\u7889 n \u273 i v\u7873  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh v\u7897 i ch\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n n\u7855 m tay t\'f4i gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t m\'e0 b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i Qu\uc0\u7923 nh xin \u273 \u7845 y m\'e0.. \u7903  l\u7841 i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i \u7903  l\u7841 i, m\u7895 i \u273 \u7913 a m\u7897 t ph\'f2ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Th\'f4i \u7903  chung ph\'f2ng v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e8 ra r\'e1ng ch\u7883 u nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900 ! Ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, hai \u273 \u7913 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n ch\'e9m gi\'f3 linh tinh chuy\u7879 n \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 p, r\u7891 i m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a b\u7841 n th\'e2n v\'e0 m\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n ch\u417 i b\u7901 i\'85\cb1 \
\cb3 Ki\uc0\u7875 u m\u432 a l\u7841 nh tr\u7901 i c\'f2n t\u7889 i n\u7919 a n\'ean hai ch\'fang t\'f4i bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  l\u7855 m r\u7891 i. M\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\'edp l\u7841 i t\'f4i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i \uc0\u273 i ng\u7911  \u273 i, Minh bu\u7891 n ng\u7911  l\u7855 m, th\u7871  hai \u273 \u7913 a n\u7857 m chung m\u7897 t gi\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Chia c\'e1ch nhau b\u7903 i c\'e1i g\u7889 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng, Qu\u7923 nh l\u7845 y c\'e1i g\u7889 i ng\u259 n c\'e1ch hai \u273 \u7913 a r\u7891 i quay m\u7863 t v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng. \u272 en cho Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0 v\u7915 a l\'e0m xong th\'ec s\u7845 m l\u7841 i to h\u417 n, Qu\u7923 nh gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh \'f4m ch\u7863 t gh\'ec l\u7845 y t\'f4i t\'f4i c\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1 l\'ean khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7895  nh\u7865  v\'e0o b\'e0n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y, \'f4m l\'e0 v\uc0\u432 \u7907 t gi\u7899 i h\u7841 n r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  s\u7907  l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f3 cho \'f4m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho \'f4m, ch\uc0\u7881  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4m th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec ch\uc0\u7881  \u273 \u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh \'f4m r\u7891 i quay l\u7841 i. T\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 g\u7847 n nhau l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i bi\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang m\u7903  to m\u7855 t ra m\'e0 ng\u7855 m t\'f4i. Xoay nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i v\'f2ng tay l\u7841 i \'f4m qua c\'e1i eo thon nh\u7887  c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh \'f4m nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u7881  g\u7853 t khe kh\u7869 .\
