\cf2 \cb3 Do g\uc0\u7847 n nhau n\'ean t\'f4i c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u417 i th\u7903  \u7845 m \'e1p c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh, c\'f3 l\u7869  m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n v\'ec s\u7907 , m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i \'f4m nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Xoa xoa nh\u7865  c\'e1i l\u432 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tay c\uc0\u7845 m s\u7901  so\u7841 ng linh tinh!\cb1 \
\
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i l\u7841 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7901  l\u432 ng th\'f4i m\'e0 c\u361 ng linh tinh \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\'fac s\u7901  l\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 tay th\'ec du l\u7883 ch lung tung.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7901  m\u7897 t t\u7865 o th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u, th\'edch th\'ec m\u7899 i s\u7901  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai d\'ea m\'e0 ch\uc0\u7859 ng b\u7843 o th\'edch!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\'ec t\'f4i h\'f4n Qu\u7923 nh lu\'f4n. L\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean h\'f4n m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i con g\'e1i khi\u7871 n th\'f4i th\u7845 y l\u7841  l\u7855 m, nh\u432  c\'f3 m\u7897 t lu\u7891 ng \u273 i\u7879 n ch\u7841 y d\u7885 c trong ng\u432 \u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u361 ng l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'f4n n\'ean l\u7841  ch\u7859 ng k\'e9m. Hai \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  v\'e0o nhau r\u7891 i t\'f4i m\u7841 nh b\u7841 o \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i ra g\u7841  g\u7851 m Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y t\'f4i r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i ra m\'e0 l\'e0m y l\u7841 i, c\u7843  hai v\u7909 ng v\u7873  ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng nh\u432  chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p nh\u432  hai di\u7877 n vi\'ean trong phim v\u7915 a xem xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng c\u7843  hai qu\u7879 n v\'e0o nhau ng\u7885 t l\u7883 m. Qu\u7923 nh m\'fat nh\u7865  m\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\u7887  em m\u7897 t m\'ecnh bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\uc0\u7869  c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4m ch\uc0\u7863 t th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec b\u7887  l\'e0m sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i xong th\'ec c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i qu\u7845 n v\'e0o nhau m\'e0 h\'f4n m\'e0 m\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i. T\'f4i lu\u7891 n b\'e0n tay \u7903  sau l\u432 ng v\'e0o trong \'e1o r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  bung c\'e1i khuy \'e1o l\u7885 t c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ra. Qu\u7923 nh r\u7901 i t\'f4i ra r\u7891 i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t ngay m\'e0, ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng lu\u7891 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh s\uc0\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0 m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\'eat Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i th\u7853 t hay \u273 \'f9a nh\u432 ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i t\'f4i v\u7853 y th\'f4i nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n cho t\'f4i lu\u7891 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong m\'e0 s\u7901  l\u432 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xoa xoa c\'e1i l\uc0\u432 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  l\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7907 c ng\u432 \u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o b\'ean tr\'ean m\'e0 xoa xoa c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa trong c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i m\u432 a m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh \u7845 m v\'f4 c\'f9ng, xao \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u th\'edch \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3. Qu\u7923 nh \'f4m kh\u7869  t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y s\u7901  r\u7891 i nh\'e9, gi\u7901  b\u7887  tay ra \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7899 i s\u7901  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat g\'ec m\'e0 m\u7897 t ch\'fat, lu\u7891 n tay kh\u7855 p ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i b\'f3p nh\u7865  b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng b\u7887  tay ra. Xoa xoa m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i t\'f4i g\u7849 y nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'f4ng th\uc0\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng to ra ph\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao l\uc0\u7841 i kh\'f4ng to, c\u361 ng thu\u7897 c d\u7841 ng t\u7889 p trong l\u7899 p \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i v\u7915 a s\u7901  v\u7915 a \'f4m ch\u7863 t Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i ng\u7845 u nghi\u7871 n l\u7845 y b\u7901  m\'f4i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a nhau. S\u7901  m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u n\u7919 a t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh m\'fat th\'eam m\uc0\u7897 t t\u7865 o nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0 m\'fat m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 Trong \uc0\u273 \'eam t\u7889 i, \'e1nh n\u7871 n lung linh l\'e0m cho khung c\u7843 nh c\u7911 a c\u259 n ph\'f2ng th\'eam \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u7869  th\u417  m\'f4ng. Qu\u7923 nh c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ng\u259 n cho t\'f4i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e9n c\'e1i \'e1o l\'ean nh\u432 ng t\'f4i n\u7857 ng n\u7863 c \u273 \'f2i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng ch\u7883 u. Hai c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa l\u7845 p n\'f3 d\u432 \u7899 i l\u7899 p \'e1o l\'f3t nh\'ecn th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1nh s\'e1ng t\uc0\u7915  c\'e2y n\'e9n t\u7887 a ra kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7921  \u273 \u7891  s\u7897  c\u7911 a n\'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fai s\'e1t xu\uc0\u7889 ng t\'f4i h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ra ng\u7853 m l\u7845 y c\'e1i n\'fam nh\u7887  x\'edu m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t. H\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m thoang tho\u7843 ng t\u7887 a ra lan nh\u7865  v\'e0o c\'e1nh m\u361 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9i da th\uc0\u7883 t c\u7911 a m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i con g\'e1i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ng\u7917 i n\'f3i kh\'e1c l\u7841  l\u7855 m. Kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m nh\u432  trong phim, t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ra m\'e0 n\'fat th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i ch\u7881  ng\u7853 m c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa nh\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 th\'e8m kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'ean h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m c\u7843  c\'e1i qu\u7847 ng v\'fa m\'e0 n\'fat m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay th\'ec th\'f2 sang b\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh xoa xoa c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa. L\'e2u sau t\'f4i m\u7899 i kh\u7869  nh\u7843  ra m\'e0 h\u7887 i kh\u7869  Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'fat nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 \u273 au kh\'f4ng Qu\u7923 nh?\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n leo l\'e9t, Qu\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i l\u7855 c kh\u7869  \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 au\'85 ch\u7881  th\'edch th\'edch th\'f4i.. c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m v\'f2ng quanh c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa th\'eam m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u g\'ec l\'e0 ki\u7875 u g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec n\'f3 t\'ea t\'ea bu\uc0\u7891 n bu\u7891 n \u7845 y.. c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f3 ch\uc0\u7883 u nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n th\'edch h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i quay xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 m\'fat ti\u7871 p. H\u7871 t b\u7847 u v\'fa b\'ean tr\'e1i th\'ec qua b\u7847 u v\'fa b\'ean ph\u7843 i r\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng d\u7847 n c\'e1i b\u7909 ng thon nh\u7887  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\u7915 a ch\u7841 m g\u7847 n \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i r\u7889 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i! D\uc0\u7915 ng l\u7841 i.. kh\'f4ng cho n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7849 ng l\'ean t\'f4i c\u432 \u7901 i tinh ngh\u7883 ch m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho \uc0\u273 i m\'e0.. xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i nh\u432  phim l\'fac n\'e3y xem \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng cho?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 b\uc0\u7849 n b\u7849 n ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u7845 y, kinh kinh!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i ngu\'fdt d\'e0i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'ean phim n\'f3 m\'fat \uc0\u273 \u7847 y c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, cho anh m\'fat m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u. Th\'f4i cho \u273 i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng t\'fam l\u7845 y c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh gi\u7919  ch\u7863 t r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho l\'e0 kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng n\uc0\u259 n n\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, t\'f4i \u273 \'e0nh c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa r\u7891 i n\u7857 m sang b\'ean m\'e0 \'f4m r\u7891 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\'f4n Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 xoa c\'e1i m\'f4ng r\u7891 i xoa c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n, nh\u432 ng m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i n\u7855 m b\'e0n tay t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  l\'ean tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0i l\u7847 n th\'f4i nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  do t\'f4i n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i m\'e2n m\'ea khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'ean m\u7863 c k\u7879  cho t\'f4i s\u7901  so\u7841 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a d\'e1m cho tay v\'e0o, t\'f4i ch\u7881  d\'e1m xoa xoa nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\u7845 y c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n b\'ean ngo\'e0i c\'eda qu\u7847 n ng\u7911  th\'f4i. Ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  l\u7891 n ph\u7909  n\u7919  l\u7847 n n\'e0o nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n th\u7845 y mu l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i cao ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng th\u7845 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7844 n nh\u7865  nh\u7865  ba \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o t\'f4i th\u7845 y n\'f3 m\u7873 m c\'f4 c\'f9ng. N\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i ch\'e1n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh kh\u7869  h\u417 i \u273 \u7849 y t\'f4i ra m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y s\u7901  th\u7871  th\'f4i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\uc0\u7911  th\u7881  v\'e0o tai:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7901  b\'ean ngo\'e0i qu\u7847 n th\'ec c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec sao m\'e0 n\u7855 n b\'f3p vu\u7889 t ve kinh th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  ch\u7913  h\'ec h\'ec, th\'f4i cho anh s\u7901  v\'e0o b\'ean trong n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i xong t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e1nh li\u7873 u th\u7885 c lu\'f4n tay v\'e0o trong qu\u7847 n m\'e0 m\'e2n m\'ea c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n r\u7891 i. Qu\u7923 nh v\u7897 i kh\'e9p ch\'e2n l\u7841 i k\u7865 p c\u7913 ng b\'e0n tay t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 \uc0\u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u417  c\u417  m\'e0! B\u432 \u7899 ng th\u7871  h\u7843 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng l\'e0 Kh\'f4ng! Qu\uc0\u7923 nh gi\u7853 n \u273 \'f3!\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y th\'ec ti\u7871 ng s\u7845 m vang r\'ean l\'e0m Qu\u7923 nh s\u7907  co r\'fam ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i, th\u7915 a c\u417  h\u7897 i n\'e0y t\'f4i lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o s\'e2u b\'ean trong m\'e0 xoa xoa nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n cong veo. L\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  n\'ean v\u7915 a ch\u7841 m tay v\'e0o d\'f3 th\'ec con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\'ean trong c\'e1i qu\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y b\'e0n tay t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 m v\'e0o c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7853 m ch\u7853 m th\u7843  l\u7887 ng ch\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra r\u7891 i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7907 i d\u7909 ng c\u417  h\u7897 i nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec.. th\'ec cho anh vu\uc0\u7889 t ve n\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0.. c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  cho em vu\u7889 t l\u7841 i nh\'e9. Hai \u273 \u7913 a ph\u7843 i vu\u7889 t c\u7911 a nhau m\u7899 i c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a k\u7883 p chu\u7849 n b\u7883  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 th\u7885 c lu\'f4n tay v\'e0o trong qu\u7847 n qu\u417  tay m\'e0 n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\'f3n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i l\'e0m t\'f4i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i Qu\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n to th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 , c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c nh\u432  kh\'fac c\u7911 i r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y, \u273 \'fang l\'e0 c\'e1i \u273 \u7891  d\'e2m d\'ea, m\u7899 i s\u7901  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i ta m\u7897 t t\'ed th\'f4i m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c c\u7843  l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 h\'f4 k\uc0\u7879  ch\u7913 ! Ch\u7855 c c\u7911 a em c\u361 ng \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n g\'ec.. th\u7917  cho anh s\u7901  xem n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u432 a m\u7845 y \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n nh\u432 ng do Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i kh\'e9p ch\'e2n v\'e0o n\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 a xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e0nh ph\u7843 i m\'e2m m\'ea c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7901  \u273 \'e2y t\'f4i m\u7899 i nh\u7853 n r\'f5 c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\'f4ng l\u7855 m, n\'f3i ch\'fang x\'e1c l\'e0 t\'f4i c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u hay \'edt m\'e0 ch\u7881  th\u7845 y c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'f4ng m\u7885 c p\u7917  ph\'eda tr\'ean m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t nh\u7865  \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7873 m nh\u432  l\'f4ng ch\'f3 \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe th\u7845 y v\u7853 y \u273 \u7841 p cho t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'e1m b\uc0\u7843 o l\'f4ng c\u7843 m em l\'e0 l\'f4ng ch\'f3 n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  tay vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec anh v\'ed d\uc0\u7909  th\u7871  ch\u7913  c\'f3 b\u7843 o em l\'e0 ch\'f3 \u273 \'e2u he he he!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 i\u7879 u c\u432 \u7901 i mu\u7889 n gh\'e9t!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ti\u7871 p r\u7891 i \'f4m l\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh th\u7853 t ch\u7863 t b\u7857 ng tay c\'f2n l\u7841 i, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai ng\'f3n tay xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n. C\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u7845 m v\'f4 c\'f9ng, s\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u th\'edch \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3\'85\
