\cf2 \cb3 M\uc0\u432 a \u7903  ngo\'e0i m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to h\u417 n khi\u7871 n kh\'f4ng kh\'ed l\u7841 nh h\u7859 n, cho\'e0ng c\'e1i ch\u259 n qua ng\u432 \u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u432 a g\'ec m\'e0 dai th\u7871 , l\u7841 nh kinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 anh \'f4m m\'e0 v\uc0\u7851 n l\u7841 nh \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4m g\'ec to\'e0n s\uc0\u7901  m\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta!\cb1 \
