\
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh chu m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i n\'e0y l\'e0 th\uc0\u7853 t ch\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i di\u7877 n \u273 \'fang nh\u432  tr\'ean phim \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng hai ng\'f3n tay b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 ch\u7841 m v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i, N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\'ean trong \'e2m \u7881  ch\u7843 y ra r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng nh\u432 ng n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m cho ng\'f3n tay t\'f4i tr\u417 n tr\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 G\'e3i nh\uc0\u7865  nh\u7865  v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh r\'edt kh\u7869  l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i n\'e0o b\uc0\u7887  tay ra em kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f3 ch\uc0\u7883 u th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u b\u7913 t r\u7913 t kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  \u273 i.. kh\'e9o l\'e0m m\u7897 t t\'ed n\u7919 a th\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\'ec t\'f4i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng t\'e1ch nh\u7865  hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n ra, l\u7847 n m\'f2 \u273 \'fang c\'e1i h\u7897 t le m\'e0 day nh\u7865  nh\u7865  . L\'fac n\'e0y Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\u7903  g\u7845 p r\u7891 i gi\u7853 t kh\u7869  kh\u7869  l\'ean t\u7915 ng c\u417 n. T\'f4i th\u7845 y v\u7853 y th\'ec khom ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng chui v\'e0o trong ch\u259 n m\'e0 n\'fat c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c hai ba c\'e1i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7849 y t\'f4i ra m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a r\u7891 i\'85 kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i m\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u432 a tay l\'ean r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn k\uc0\u297  n\'e0y, nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c qu\'e1 Qu\u7923 nh \u417 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\'ean Qu\u7923 nh ph\u7843 i qu\u7901  tay m\'e0 n\u7855 m l\u7845 y hai \u273 \'f9a ng\'f3n tay r\u7891 i s\u7901  s\u7901  m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em.. c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t\'85 sao m\'e0 n\'f3 ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u th\u7871 \'85\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u ch\u7913  sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau m\u7845 y c\'e2u r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i \'f4m nhau, t\'f4i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ngh\u7883 ch c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i th\u7911  th\u7881 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em m\'fat cho anh nh\uc0\u432  trong phim l\'fac n\'e3y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n l\u7855 m, em kh\'f4ng m\'fat \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 b\uc0\u7849 n c\u417  ch\u7913 , nh\u432  trong phim th\'f4i m\'e0 h\'ec h\'ec, m\'fat th\u7917  cho anh nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec kh\u7869  kh\u7869  c\'fai \u273 \u7847 u xu\u7889 ng, l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i bi\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd m\'fat cho t\'f4i r\u7891 i l\'ean t\'f4i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\u7883 ch ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean. Kh\u7869  k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng Qu\u7923 nh c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c l\u7855 c l\u7855 c r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 n\'f3 c\uc0\u7913 ng th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913 ng th\'ec m\u7899 i \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  c\u7911 a em ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai cho v\'e0o m\'e0 \uc0\u273 \'fat!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho n\'f3 c\uc0\u361 ng c\u7913 ng nh\u432  l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a em ch\u7843 y ra \u273 \u7845 y, th\'f4i m\'fat cho anh \u273 i, l\'e0m gi\u7889 ng trong phim \u273 i n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n l\u7853 p l\'f2e, Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng c\'fai xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i h\'f4n m\u7897 t c\'e1i v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c sau \u273 \'f3 h\'e9 h\'e9 mi\u7879 ng ra m\'fat nh\u7865  nh\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'fat c\u7863 c t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m, nh\'edch nh\'edch c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho con c\u7863 c ti\u7871 n s\'e2u h\u417 n v\'e0o c\'e1i mi\u7879 ng xinh x\u7855 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'e1 mi\uc0\u7879 ng ra ng\u7853 m s\'e2u n\u7919 a \u273 i em.. anh th\'edch em ng\u7853 m th\u7853 t s\'e2u m\'fat Qu\u7923 nh \u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh Nghe l\u7901 i t\'f4i n\'ean h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ra m\'e0 ng\u7853 m. Qu\u7923 nh ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t l\'e0m nh\u432  trong phim n\'ean h\'e0m r\u259 ng c\u7885  nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng v\'e0o c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c khi\u7871 n cho t\'f4i h\u417 i \u273 au m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u259 n nh\u259 n c\'e1i m\u7863 t t\'f4i lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng xoa xoa c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 kh\'f3 ch\uc0\u7883 u kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\u7843  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c ra m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng c\'f3 m\'f9i g\'ec \u7845 y..!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t m\'f9i g\'ec! Th\'f4i l\'e0m ki\u7875 u 69 nh\u432  l\'e0 trong phim \u273 i, ng\u7891 i l\'ean anh \u273 \u7875  anh m\'fat cho, nh\u432  th\u7871  m\u7899 i c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe t\'f4i n\'f3i th\'ec d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra, tr\u432 \u7901 n nh\u7865  l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i r\u7891 i \'fap c\'e1i l\u7891 n v\'e0o m\u7863 t t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i m\'fat m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a m\'fat th\'e0nh th\u7841 o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  trong phim, t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng qu\u7871 t c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n m\'e0 th\'f4i. Tuy nhi\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m cho n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\u7913 a ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7885 c ch\u7885 c c\'e1i l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o trong l\u7895  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh co r\'fam ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i anh..em \u273 au!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\'ean m\uc0\u7845 t l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n trinh ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng nh\u432  m\u7845 y di\u7877 n vi\'ean tr\'ean phim n\'ean t\'f4i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh n\u7919 a m\'e0 ch\u7881  li\u7871 m b\'ean ngo\'e0i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai m\'fat m\'e1t ch\'e1n ch\'ea cho nhau th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i n\u7857 m \'f4m t\'f4i. M\u432 a m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to, ti\u7871 ng m\u432 a r\'e0o r\'e0o khi\u7871 n t\'f4i c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 s\u7907  s\u7879 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \'f4m ch\u7863 t t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7881  m\'fat cho nhau th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'f4i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i xoa xoa c\'e1i mu l\uc0\u7891 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'fat cho nhau l\'e0m g\'ec, \uc0\u273 \'e3 l\'e0m th\'ec l\'e0m \u273 \u7871 n c\'f9ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em s\uc0\u7907  \u273 au l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 au \u273 \'e2u, anh \u273 \u7885 c tr\'ean m\u7841 ng v\u7899 i nghe m\u7845 y \'f4ng anh n\'f3i l\'e0m ch\u7881  nh\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e1i sau \u273 \'f3 s\u432 \u7899 ng li\u7873 n \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 th\uc0\u7853 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y hay anh l\u7841 i l\u7915 a em?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7915 a em l\'e0m c\'e1i g\'ec.. nh\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'f4i..m\'e0 ra n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7855 c g\'ec \u273 \'e3 \u273 au.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec t\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i l\u7891 m c\u7891 m c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 lu\u7891 n nh\u7865  \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \u7843 o quanh c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i m\'fat c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ti\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khe l\uc0\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh kh\'edt l\u7855 m ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng th\u7915 a t\u7915 ng n\u7871 p th\u7883 t nh\u432  di\u7877 n vi\'ean trong phim m\'e0 hai ch\'fang t\'f4i v\u7915 a xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng h\'f2a c\'f9ng n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n l\'e0m c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n tr\u417 n nh\u7851 y. Do anh n\u7871 n l\u7853 p l\'f2e n\'ean t\'f4i kh\'f4ng th\u7875  nh\'ecn r\'f5 c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng s\u7901  c\'f3 v\u7867  n\'f3 nhi\u7873 u tr\u417 n l\u7855 m r\u7891 i. Qu\u7923  g\u7889 i xu\u7889 ng t\'f4i th\u7911  th\u7881 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u273 \'fat v\'e0o em nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh im l\u7863 ng r\u7891 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u. \u272 \u7905  hai c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh banh ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y v\'e0o \u273 \'fang c\'e1i khe m\'e0 \u7845 n v\'e0o. L\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean l\'e0m chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f5 t\'f4i v\u7851 n c\'f2n run l\u7855 m. \u7844 n v\'e0o m\'e0 c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c ch\u7881  tr\u432 \u7907 t tr\u432 \u7907 t d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe l\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng chui \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng n\u7855 m nh\u7865  con c\u7863 c t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 n\'f3 kh\'f4ng chui \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a! C\u7911 a em ch\u7855 c b\'e9, d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra n\u7919 a xem n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe l\u7901 i t\'f4i d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a, t\'f4i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c \u7845 n xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7875  \u273 \'fang c\'e1i l\u7895  m\'e0 \u7845 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y th\'ec \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'fang c\'e1i l\u7895  r\u7891 i. C\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c m\u7899 i chui v\'e0o b\'ean trong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nh\u259 n nh\u259 n m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7865  th\'f4i anh em \u273 au!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i anh nh\u7865  m\'e0..v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe t\'f4i n\'f3i v\'e0o \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ch\'fay r\u7891 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\'e0 d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i \u7845 n v\'e0o s\'e2u h\u417 n. Tr\u432 \u7901 n ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7849 y c\'e1i m\'f4ng m\u7841 nh m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'ec con c\u7863 c banh c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n nh\u7887  x\'edu l\u7847 m l\u361 i ti\u7871 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng l\'e0m cho Qu\u7923 nh gi\u7843 m c\u417 n \u273 au \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7889 ng tay l\'ean b\u7909 ng t\'f4i \u273 \u7849 y nh\u7865  r\u7891 i c\'e0o kh\u7869  m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 au qu\'e1 anh \u417 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng n\'fat lu\'f4n c\'e1i l\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i t\'f4i an \u7911 i Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a s\u7869  h\u7871 t \u273 au m\'e0 em.. d\u7847 n d\u7847 n r\u7891 i s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  \u273 \u7875  con c\u7863 c n\u7857 m s\'e2u b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n t\'f4i ch\u432 a v\u7897 i nh\u7845 p m\'e0 ch\u7881  kh\u7869  h\'f4n r\u7891 i \'f4m gh\'ec l\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh \'f4m l\u7841 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7911 a anh to th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4n nh\uc0\u7865  l\'ean \u273 \'f4i mi m\u7873 m m\u7841 i t\'f4i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7911 a anh l\'e0 g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chim anh\'85 c\uc0\u7863 c anh ch\u7913  c\'f2n c\'e1i g\'ec n\u7919 a\'85 \u7845 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong ng\u432 \u7901 i em m\'e0 em c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3 banh r\u7897 ng ra l\u7855 m \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng..m\'e0..ch\u7855 c c\u7843  hai m\u7899 i l\'e0m n\'ean em m\u7899 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 au nh\u432  v\u7853 y h\'ec h\'ec.. Nh\u7845 p m\u7897 t t\'ed n\u7919 a ch\u7855 c kh\'f4ng \u273 au \u273 \'e2u, quen ngay \u7845 y m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 .. ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i d\u7909  ng\u432 \u7901 i ta th\'f4i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u7909  c\u7843  hai c\'f9ng s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913  sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i b\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m nh\u7845 p nha nh\u7845 p nh\u7893 m c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh cho con c\u7863 c th\'f2 th\u7909 t trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n. L\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m t\'ecnh t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\'edch v\'f4 c\'f9ng. Nh\u7845 t l\'e0 khi c\'e1i con c\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\'fat ra kh\u7887 i c\'e1i l\u7895  sau \u273 \'f3 c\u7855 m ng\u7853 p v\'e0o s\'e2u trong c\'e1i l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7895 i l\u7847 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y Qu\u7923 nh cong ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean r\u7891 i \'f4m l\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0m nh\u7865  m\'e0.. h\'ec l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0y ..em th\'edch kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3\'85 s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m anh.. c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f3 t\u7843  l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng m\'e0 nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'f4i anh nh\'e9.. m\u7841 nh em \u273 au anh \u7841 ..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 au th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 h\uc0\u417 i r\'e1t r\'e1t h\u417 i t\'ea t\'ea nh\u432 ng n\'f3i chung l\'e0 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'f3 t\u7843  l\u7855 m.. Anh \u273 \u7915 ng \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i em n\u7919 a h\u417 i kh\'f3 th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7889 ng tay ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  nh\u7845 m nh\u7893 m c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\u7841 nh h\u417 n. Con c\u7863 c b\'e2y gi\u7901  di chuy\u7875 n trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n d\u7877  d\'e0ng h\u417 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a. C\'e0ng nh\u7845 p th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng r\'ean to h\u417 n, ti\u7871 ng r\'ean kh\'f4ng nh\u432  trong phim m\'e0 ch\u7881  \u432  \u7917  th\'f4i nh\u432 ng l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a th\u7903  h\u7891 ng h\u7897 c t\'f4i v\u7915 a h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh l\'e0m em s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i \'f4m l\u7845 y t\'f4i m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i. Hai th\'e2n th\u7875  qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n lung linh n\'e3ng m\u7841 n v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7899 i l\'e0m l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u n\'ean t\'f4i chri nh\u7845 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u259 m b\u7843 y ph\'fat \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u7845 n s\'e2u v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7855 n \u7891  \u7841 t tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o xong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh xoa xoa c\'e1i m\'f4ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh cho h\uc0\u7871 t v\'e0o trong \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7903  d\u7889 c t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! H\'ec h\'ec Th\u7871  anh xu\u7845 t v\'e0o em c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i n\'f3ng n\'f3ng th\'f4i..m\'e0 anh cho v\'e0o th\u7871  em c\'f3 thai th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec \uc0\u273 \u7867  ch\u7913  sao!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! C\'f3 Thai m\'e0 \u273 \u7867  \u273 \u7875  me em th\u7883 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7883 t g\'ec m\'e0 th\u7883 t.. c\'f3 ch\'e1u b\u7871  s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f2n g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'f9a v\u7899 i anh n\u7919 a\'85!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \'f4m Qu\uc0\u7923 nh r\u7891 i \u273 \u7875  Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u273 \'f9a th\u7871  th\'f4i ch\u7913  mai \u273 ia mua thu\u7889 c u\u7889 ng ch\u7855 c kh\'f4ng sao \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 th\uc0\u7853 t kh\'f4ng em nh\u7905  d\'ednh ch\u7871 t v\u7899 i em!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7853 t m\'e0.. n\'f3i ch\'fang ch\u7859 ng sao \u273 \'e2u.. h\'ec h\'ec! T\'ed n\u7919 a l\'e0m c\'e1i n\u7919 a nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho n\uc0\u7919 a gh\'e9t anh l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ve v\'ea m\'e1 c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau m\u7863 c d\'f9 con c\u7863 c b\'ean trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n \u273 \'e3 tr\u417 n tu\u7897 t m\'e0 nhoi ra ngo\'e0i.\
