\cf2 \cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai \'f4m nhau ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng s\u7899 m h\'f4m sau th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 \'e8o Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i \u259 n s\'e1ng r\u7891 i mua thu\u7889 c tr\'e1nh thai, Qu\u7923 nh u\u7889 ng xong r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai l\'ean l\u7899 p h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i c\u7845 p r\u7891 i n\'ean th\u7847 y c\'f4 ch\u7859 ng c\'f2n qu\u7843 n kh\'f3 kh\u259 n nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a. Hai \u273 \u7913 a t\u7921  \'fd chuy\u7875 n ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh nhau n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n. \u272 \u7871 n tr\u432 a th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7841 p xe c\'f9ng t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0. \u272 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7913 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m qua l\'e0m em \uc0\u273 au l\u7855 m.. gi\u7901  h\'e3y c\'f2n \'ea \u7849 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! \'ca \uc0\u7849 m nh\u432 ng s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432 ng \u273 au b\u7887  x\u7915 .. \u273 \'e3 th\u7871  c\'f2n l\'e0m m\u7841 nh n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh th\'ec m\u7899 i s\u432 \u7899 ng, h\'f4m n\'e0o cho anh l\'e0m ti\u7871 p nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0..l\'e0m ti\uc0\u7871 p th\'ec m\u7899 i th\u7845 y s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh chu m\'f4i l\'e8 l\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 \u259 n c\u417 m r\u7891 i chi\u7873 u \u273 i h\u7885 c th\'eam r\u7891 i t\u7889 i r\u7911  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i \u259 n v\u7863 t. Qu\u7923 nh h\u7885 c th\'eam kh\'e1c l\u7899 p v\u7899 i t\'f4i n\'ean kh\'f4ng \u273 i c\'f9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai \u273 i \u259 n b\'e1nh m\'ec, Qu\u7923 nh k\'e9o gh\u7871  s\'e1t t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y h\'f4m qua b\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  em nghi nghi \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i gi\u7853 t m\'ecnh t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nghi nghi th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7887 i d\'f2 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec em tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i l\'e0 c\'f3 r\u7891 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u, c\'f3 ai b\u7843 o g\'ec \u273 \'e2u. Kh\'e9o b\u7889  m\u7865  c\'f2n s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 \u7845 y ch\u7913  l\u7841 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 \'e1 t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i xui d\u7841 i em, b\u7843 o c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \u7875  m\'e0 \u259 n \u273 \'f2n \'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i t\'f4i gh\'e9 s\'e1t tai c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'ed n\uc0\u7919 a v\u7873  cho anh l\'e0m nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 l\'e0m, b\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  c\'f3 \u7903  nh\'e0 \u273 \u7845 y, v\u7873  m\'e0 h\'ed ho\'e1y c\'f3 m\'e0 toi \'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec \uc0\u273 i ch\u7895  kh\'e1c! Thu\'ea nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  m\'e0 \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i bu\u7893 i l\'fac b\u7845 y gi\u7901  thu\'ea nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  \u273 i v\u7899 i nhau \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \'f3 qu\'e1 xa x\u7881  v\'e0 c\u361 ng d\u7877  b\u7883  nh\'f2m ng\'f3 ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng nh\u432  b\'e2y gi\u7901 . B\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'e1c b\u7841 n tr\u7867  c\u7845 p hai c\u7845 p ba th\'ec c\'f3 th\u7875  d\u7877  d\'e0ng m\'e0 thu\'ea c\'f9ng nhau \u273 \u7871 n m\u7845 y ng\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe th\u7845 y t\'f4i b\u7843 o thu\'ea nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  th\'ec gi\'e3y n\u7843 y l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i kh\'f4ng v\'e0o \uc0\u273 \'e2u, v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 nh\u7905  ai bi\u7871 t th\'ec ch\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng run run v\'ec ch\u432 a v\'e0o bao gi\u7901  n\'ean \u273 \'e0nh th\'f4i. Th\u7845 y c\'e1i v\u7867  m\u7863 t v\u7915 a mu\u7889 n nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a s\u7907  c\u7911 a t\'f4i khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh b\u7853 t c\u432 \u7901 i. L\u7897  c\'e1i r\u259 ng kh\u7875 nh v\u7899 i h\'e0m r\u7855 ng tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7873 u Qu\u7923 nh kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i v\uc0\u7867  m\u7863 t mu\u7889 n nh\u432 ng s\u7907  k\'eca, th\u7871  mu\u7889 n l\'e0m v\u7899 i em th\u7853 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7911 m t\u7881 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u432 ng t\u7887  v\u7867  n\u259 n n\u7881  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\'e0y kia ch\uc0\u7855 c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u7903  nh\'e0 \u273 \'e2u, b\u7889  m\u7865  em c\'f3 c\'f4ng chuy\u7879 n g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nh\'e0 \u273 \'e2u, b\u7843 o tr\u432 a em \u259 n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh, hai \u273 \u7913 a m\'ecnh v\u7873  nh\'e0 nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7903  c\u7901  trong b\u7909 ng t\'f4i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh k\'e9o c\'e1i gh\u7871  nh\u7921 a l\u7879 t x\u7879 t d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1i n\u7873 n b\'ea t\'f4ng r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 anh d\'ea th\uc0\u7871 ? Ch\u7881  ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 l\'e0m sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7841 i em xinh qu\'e1 h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ch\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y trong \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  th\'edch th\'fa v\u7899 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3. \u258 n v\u7863 t xong r\u7891 i ch\'fang t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0, hai h\'f4m sau th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n ng\'e0y Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o t\'f4i ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 ai \u7903  nh\'e0 c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7885 c \'f4n n\'ean ch\u7881  \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i r\u432 \u7905 i s\'e1ng l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7873  r\u7891 i. Hai \u273 \u7913 a h\'ed h\u7917 ng \u273 i mua \'edt \u273 \u7891  \u259 n r\u7891 i ph\'f3ng xe v\u7873  nh\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Do c\uc0\u7843  hai \u273 \u7841 p xe n\'ean m\u7891  h\'f4i m\u7891  k\'ea ch\u7843 y ra tr\'f4ng hai \u273 \u7913 a v\u7915 a bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a \u273 \'e1ng y\'eau. V\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 v\u7915 a m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra t\'f4i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7905  \u7903  nh\'e0 n\'e0y m\'e0 b\u7889  m\u7865  v\u7873  th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\uc0\u432 \u7899 i em ch\u7913  c\'f2n sao n\u7919 a, c\'f3 th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec c\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 l\u7845 y c\'e1i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i b\'e0n g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho b\u7889  m\u7865  h\u7887 i xem tr\u432 a c\'f3 v\u7873  kh\'f4ng v\'e0 \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u th\'ec bao gi\u7901  v\u7873  r\u7891 i. N\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i b\u7889  m\u7865  \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'fat th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i c\'fap m\'e1y r\u7891 i h\'ed h\u7917 ng b\u7843 o t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7889  m\u7865  em chi\u7873 u m\u7899 i v\u7873  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\uc0\u7845 y v\u7871  b\u7871  Qu\u7923 nh l\'ean m\'e0 h\'f4n v\'e0o m\'e1 v\'e0o tr\'e1n. Qu\u7923 nh xinh x\u7855 n nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i thu\u7897 c d\u7841 ng cao, ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t m\'e9t n\u259 m m\u7845 y th\'f4i trong khi d\'f3 t\'f4i cao h\u417 n m\'e9t b\u7843 y n\'ean t\'f4i d\u7877  d\'e0ng v\u7915 a b\u7871  v\u7915 a h\'f4n tr\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng gi\u7885 t m\u7891  h\'f4i l\u7845 m t\u7845 m tr\'ean tr\'e1n khi\u7871 n t\'f4i th\u7845 y h\u417 i m\u7863 n \u7903  \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng th\'edch th\'fa v\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'f4m ch\u7863 t ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau trong v\'f2ng tay.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7883 n hai tay l\'ean vai t\'f4i, Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3ng l\uc0\u7855 m! Th\u7843  em xu\u7889 ng \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7912  th\u7843  \u273 \u7845 y! Anh th\'edch b\u7871  th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u417 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng c\u7843  hai b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i nhau. V\u7915 a l\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i v\u7915 a b\u7871  Qu\u7923 nh l\'ean tr\'ean ph\'f2ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7863 t Qu\u7923 nh xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7911  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  em \u273 i t\u7855 m c\'e1i \u273 \'e3, n\'f3ng l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i h\'ed h\u7917 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh t\uc0\u7855 m chung v\u7899 i em nh\'e9?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho.. em th\'edch t\uc0\u7855 m m\u7897 t m\'ecnh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0 cho anh t\uc0\u7855 m c\'f9ng \u273 i, t\u7855 m c\'f9ng c\u361 ng c\'f3 sao \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t c\u7911 a anh l\'e0 r\u7845 t d\u7877  \u273 \'e8 em ra trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\'ed n\'e0o g\u7885 i l\'e0 l\u432 \u417 ng thi\u7879 n c\u7843 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh m\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\uc0\u432 \u417 ng thi\u7879 n th\'ec c\'f2n ai l\u432 \u417 ng thi\u7879 n v\'e0o \u273 \'e2y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh k\u7879  t\'f4i r\u7891 i l\u7845 y c\'e1i v\'e1y tr\u7855 ng h\u7891 ng \u273 em v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m. T\'f4i h\'ed h\u7917 ng b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Hay t\'ed n\uc0\u7919 a em kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n l\'f3t nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i l\u432 \u7901 m m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng m\uc0\u7863 c kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0\'85 kh\'f4ng m\uc0\u7863 c \u273 i, \u7903  nh\'e0 t\'ed n\u7919 a ch\u7881  c\u7847 n v\u7841 ch l\'ean l\'e0 anh c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\'ecn \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i th\'eam g\'ec n\u7919 a v\'e0 mang \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m, kh\'f4ng cho t\u7855 m c\'f9ng n\'ean t\'f4i ch\u7881  c\'f2n c\'e1ch \u7903  ngo\'e0i m\'e0 \u273 \u7907 i. M\u7899 i v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'ean trong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u417 i em qu\'ean kh\u259 n t\u7855 m mang cho em!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7902  \u273 \'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Trong t\uc0\u7911  c\u7841 nh \u273 \u7891  l\'f3t c\u7911 a em \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7903  t\u7911  ra th\u7845 y m\u7845 y c\'eda \u273 \u7891  l\'f3t c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh, kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7865  mua cho hay Qu\u7923 nh t\u7921  ch\u7885 n nh\u432 ng b\u7897  \u273 \u7891  n\'e0o nh\'ecn c\u361 ng b\u7855 t m\u7855 t l\u7855 m. H\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c do tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i n\'ean t\'f4i ch\u7859 ng nh\'ecn r\'f5 m\'e0u s\u7855 c n\'f3 \u273 \u7865 p th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7845 y m\u7897 t \'e1i kh\u259 n t\u7855 m \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh h\'e9 c\u7917 a th\'f2 tay ra, t\'f4i m\u7897 t l\'e1ch ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong lu\'f4n.\
