\cf2 \cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a th\u7845 y t\'f4i v\'e0o th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 a tay che hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u ng\u7921 c r\u7891 i c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. L\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i r\u7891 i qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 a cho em xong r\u7891 i ra ngay bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7912  ra \u273 \u7845 y, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y t\u7855 m c\'f9ng c\u417 ! M\'e0 sao ph\u7843 i che th\u7871  kia?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y ch\u7913  sao n\u7919 a, c\'f3 th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i h\u7887 i, th\'f4i \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'e2u! V\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i th\'ec anh kh\'f4ng ra \u273 \'e2u, anh l\'e0 anh t\u7855 m c\'f9ng em lu\'f4n \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i c\uc0\u7903 i ph\u259 ng qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m m\'e0 kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec n\u7919 a, tay th\'ec v\u7851 n che hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa v\'e0 c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n. C\u7903 i xong \u273 \u7875  con c\u7863 c m\u7873 m m\u7873 m \u273 ung \u273 \u432 a t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh nh\'ecn \uc0\u273 i, t\u7889 i h\'f4m g\'ec m\u7845 t \u273 i\u7879 n c\'f3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y g\'ec \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec m\'e0 t\u7915  t\u7915  b\u7887  tay m\'ecnh ra, l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i nh\'ecn r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\u7871  n\'e0o. Hai c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa nh\u7887  x\'edu nh\u432 ng h\u7891 ng r\u7921 c nh\'ecn \u273 \'e3 m\u7855 t l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'fa c\uc0\u7911 a qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng to nh\u432 ng c\'e2n \u273 \u7889 i tr\'f2n tr\u7883 a v\'f4 c\'f9ng, qu\u7847 ng v\'fa th\'ec b\'e9 x\'edu ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng to nh\u432  m\u7897 t s\u7889  di\u7877 n vi\'ean trong nh\u7919 ng phim sex m\'e0 t\'f4i xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ph\'eda d\uc0\u432 \u7899 i th\'ec c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n cong veo l\'ean tr\'f4ng \u273 \'e3 m\u7855 t v\'f4 c\'f9ng, n\'f3 kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u l\'f4ng m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh xo\u259 n xo\u259 n \u7903  ph\'eda b\'ean tr\'ean th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y t\'f4i ch\u259 m ch\'fa nh\'ecn v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7891 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao nh\'ecn c\'e1i \uc0\u7845 y c\u7911 a em khi\u7871 p th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh th\uc0\u7845 y n\'f3 \u273 \u7865 p h\'ec h\'ec! Mu\u7889 n kh\'e1m ph\'e1 n\'f3!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m g\'ec kh\'e1m h\uc0\u7871 t c\'f2n ph\'e1 c\u7911 a em c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'e2u n\'f3i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i kh\u7869  h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\'f4m g\'ec ph\'e1 trinh nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\'f3 \u273 au kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i \u273 au m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i nh\u432 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i chung l\'e0 th\'edch. M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u nh\'f3i nh\'f3i \u273 au l\u7855 m \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! H\'f4m nay n\u7871 u l\'e0m th\'ec l\'e0m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  nh\'e9, anh ch\u7881  s\u7907  nh\u7865  em kh\'f4ng s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i nh\u432  di\u7877 n vi\'ean trong phim \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 g\'e0o \u7847 m l\'ean r\u7891 i k\'eau s\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai c\'f9ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7855 m r\u7917 a cho nhau. Qu\u7923 nh nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng con c\u7863 c t\'f4i th\'ec m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m g\'ec n\'f3 c\uc0\u7913 ng l\u7855 m m\'e0 sao h\'f4m nay n\'f3 m\u7873 m th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng th\'ec n\'f3 m\u7873 m ch\u7913  sao m\'e0 c\u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u th\'ec n\'f3 m\u7899 i c\u7913 ng bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900 ! Th\u7871  \u273 \u7875  em kh\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng xem th\u7871  n\'e0o nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i xong th\'ec ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\'e0ng n\u7855 m nh\u7865  l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c vu\u7889 t ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m. Do c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c c\u7897 ng th\'eam v\u7899 i b\'e0n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh khi\u7871 n con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y! Nh\'ecn n\'f3 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7915 a n\'f3i v\u7915 a c\u432 \u7901 i khi\u7871 n c\'e1i r\u259 ng kh\u7875 nh l\u7897  ra nh\'ecn c\'e0ng duy\'ean d\'e1ng h\u417 n. Qu\u7923 nh vu\u7889 t con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i th\'ec t\'f4i m\'e2m m\'ea xoa xoa hai c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa sau \u273 \u7885  g\u7849 y nh\u7865  n\'f3 l\'ean khi\u7871 n cho Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng b\u7883  k\'edch th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i r\u7891 i t\'f4i n\'f3i kh\u7869  v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u7921 c em \u273 \u7865 p th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843  nh\u432 ng m\'e0 em v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3 b\'e9 b\'e9 sao \u273 \'f3!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, to qu\'e1 kh\'e9o nh\'ecn x\u7845 u \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i n\'f3i xong th\'ec b\'e0n tay b\'ean d\uc0\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e3 m\'f2 m\u7851 m xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u432 \u7899 t nh\u7865 p r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n h\'f2a c\'f9ng v\u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915  tr\'ean ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng l\'e0m cho c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u417 n tr\u417 n, t\'f4i nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'e1ch c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n gi\u7919 a m\'e0 day h\u7897 t le.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'e9p ch\'e2n l\u7841 i k\u7865 p l\u7845 y b\'e0n tay t\'f4i th\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao t\uc0\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 k\u7865 p tay anh th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em bu\uc0\u7891 n.. kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Day ch\uc0\u7895  n\'e0y s\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432 ng m\'e0 em v\u7851 n c\u7843 m th\u7845 y kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u sao \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f3 ch\uc0\u7883 u nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i h\'ec h\'ec, anh th\u7845 y \u7903  trong phim day ch\u7895  n\'e0y ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c l\u7855 m c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, c\'e0ng day c\'e0ng ra n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7895  n\'e0y l\'e0 ch\u7895  k\'edch th\'edch c\'f2n g\'ec, ai \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng ra n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec day ti\u7871 p th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u run l\'ean, \u7903  hai m\'e9p n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n nh\u7851 y nh\u7851 y tu\'f4n ra, do ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  c\'e1i l\u7891 n n\'e0o n\'ean khi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  c\'e1i l\u7891 n t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'e0y v\'f2 c\'e1i khe l\uc0\u7891 n m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u r\u7891 i t\'f4i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'fat cho anh nh\uc0\u432  t\u7889 i h\'f4m g\'ec nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m g\'ec ch\uc0\u432 a t\u7855 m m\'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng k\'eau b\u7849 n m\'e0 b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 nag t\u7855 m m\'fat k\'eau b\u7849 n l\'e0 sao? Th\'f4i m\'fat cho anh \u273 i m\'e0, anh th\'e8m l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y.. c\u7921 c k\'ec th\'e8m lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m l\'fac n\'e0o m\'e0 anh ch\u7843  th\'e8m!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'e3i t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e2u nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i c\u361 ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, tay vu\u7889 t d\u7885 c con c\u7863 c cho n\'f3 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean r\u7891 i m\u7899 i kh\'e9 h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ra li\u7871 m nh\'e8 nh\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7873 m m\u7841 i ch\u7841 m v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c l\'e0m cho t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, r\u432 \u7899 n ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c cho con c\u7863 c chui v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ra m\'e0 k\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Mu\uc0\u7889 n \u7845 n v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng em \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec h\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng ra ch\u7913 ..\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m y\'eau r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh xo\u259 n t\'edt \u7903  c\'e1i g\u7889 c c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i sang m\u7897 t b\'ean r\u7891 i h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m th\u7853 t s\'e2u v\'e0o m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng l\u7855 m r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  h\'e0m r\u259 ng c\u7885  nh\u7865  v\'e0o con c\u7863 c, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 au nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng h\u417 i t\'ea t\'ea.\cb1 \
\cb3 Run run hai ch\'e2n, vu\uc0\u7889 t m\'e1i t\'f3c m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 Qu\u7923 nh \u417 i\'85 anh t\'ea h\u7871 t c\u7843  con c\u7863 c r\u7891 i.. m\'fat l\'e0m anh s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  trong phim cho v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng em \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i h\'ed h\uc0\u7917 ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\'fat m\u7841 nh h\u417 n, c\'f3 v\u7867  chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'ean h\'e0m r\u259 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\u7885  c\u7885  v\'e0o c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng ch\'f3p ch\'e9p kh\u7869  kh\u7869  vang l\'ean l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch th\'fa v\'f4 c\'f9ng. Li\u7871 m cho c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 m ti\u7871 p xu\u7889 ng hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i li\u7871 m sang \u273 \'f9i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 v\uc0\u7867  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 h\u7885 c t\u7853 p \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng g\'ec trong c\'e1i \u273 \u297 a phim sex m\'e0 hai ch\'fang t\'f4i l\'e9n l\'fat xem h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c.\
