\cf2 \cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec t\'f4i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 b\uc0\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean r\u7891 i th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 t anh m\'fat cho em nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng! Em kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 g\'ec \uc0\u273 \'e2u m\'e0 kh\'f4ng cho, m\'fat s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd, t\'f4i ng\u7891 i th\u7909 p xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ra ng\u7853 m l\u7845 y c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n cong veo m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m d\u7885 c c\'e1i khe t\u7915  tr\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7849 y t\'f4i ra nh\u432 ng c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i ch\u7841 m v\'e0o r\u7891 i th\'ec c\'f3 v\u7867  s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m, Hai b\'e0n tay b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7905  l\'ean v\'e0i t\'f4i r\u7891 i kh\u7869  r\'ean nh\u7919 ng ti\u7871 ng \u432  \u432  b\'e9 x\'edu trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7849 ng m\u7863 t l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec m\'e0 kh\u7869  e l\u7879  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i h\u417 i d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a. \u272 \u7905  l\u7845 y ch\'e2n Qu\u7923 nh g\'e1c l\'ean vai t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i lu\u7891 n v\'e0o hai c\'e1i m\'e9p m\'e0 li\u7871 m. L\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i nh\'ecn r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4i n\'f3 h\uc0\u7891 ng h\'e0o ch\u7859 ng k\'e9m g\'ec v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng di\u7877 n vi\'ean trong c\'e1i \u273 \u297 a t\'f4i v\u7915 a xem c\u7843 , c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n th\'ec c\'f2n kh\'edt v\'e0 b\'e9 x\'edu h\u417 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n \u273 \u7909 c \u273 \u7909 c tr\'e0n ra hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n th\u7853 t l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u, t\'f4i chu c\'e1i m\'f4i m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t r\u7891 i li\u7871 m th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh. Qu\u7923 nh r\'ean to h\u417 n r\u7891 i \u7845 n nh\u7865  \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\'e0o h\'e1ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bi\uc0\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh s\u432 \u7899 ng n\'ean t\'f4i c\'e0ng m\'fat m\u7841 nh, \u273 \u7871 n khi Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'e3 th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  cho anh \u273 \'fat v\'e0o nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  t\u7881 nh gi\u7845 c m\u7897 ng Qu\u7923 nh m\u7903  to \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'fat v\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng m\'e0 trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m ch\u7853 t th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec \u273 \'fat v\'e0o ki\u7875 u g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7893 ng m\'f4ng l\u7841 i anh doggy, c\'e1i ki\u7875 u \u7845 y bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nheo m\u7855 t t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i quay l\u7841 i, ch\u7889 ng hai tay v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i ch\u7893 ng c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean th\u7853 t cao m\'e0 nh\'f4 ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ra \uc0\u273 \u7857 ng sau, kh\u7869  kh\'e0ng c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c qu\'e9t d\u7885 c d\u7885 c c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m nh\'e9t v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7853 t l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng nh\u7901  c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n nhi\u7873 u c\u7897 ng th\'eam v\u7899 i h\'f4m g\'ec t\'f4i ph\'e1 trinh r\u7891 i n\'ean kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'f3 kh\u259 n khi t\'f4i \u7845 n v\'e0o n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'f4t n\u7917 a th\'ec t\'f4i h\u7887 i Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n \uc0\u273 au kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i th\u7889 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i nh\u432 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 au nh\u432  h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? Th\u7871  anh \u7845 n s\'e2u v\'e0o nh\'e9?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m \u7845 n v\'e0o. Nh\'ecn con c\u7863 c khu\u7845 t d\u7847 n trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n \u273 \u7887  au l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n khi hai c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i v\u7899 i b\u7909 ng ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  v\'e0o c\'e1i m\'f4ng cong veo tr\u7855 ng ph\u7889 p th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i nh\'fan ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c th\'f2 th\u7909 t trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n l\'e0m cho Qu\u7923 nh s\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 i\'ean l\'ean, n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n m\u7895 i l\'fac ch\u7843 y ra m\u7897 t chi\u7873 u khi\u7871 n c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c tr\u417 n tu\u7897 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a nh\u7845 p t\'f4i v\u7915 a v\'e9o nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh nh\uc0\u7845 p th\u7871  n\'e0y s\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh x\'f5a m\'e1i t\'f3c ra r\u7891 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u li\'ean t\u7909 c, Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u r\'ean kh\u7869  kh\u7869  t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 ng \u432  \u432  trong c\u7893  h\u7885 ng th\'ec t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7841 nh n\u7919 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3..m\uc0\u7841 nh h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7915 ng cho v\'e0o s\'e2u qu\'e1 anh nh\'e9..em h\u417 i th\u7889 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.. kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c .. c\u7913  cho v\u7915 a v\u7915 a th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i! Anh cho v\u7915 a v\u7915 a th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7855 m h\u7871 t con c\u7863 c v\'e0o trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n nh\u432 ng t\'f4i nh\u7845 p v\u7915 a \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7875  cho c\u7843  hai s\u432 \u7899 ng, Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 quen v\u7899 i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c con c\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7855 m v\'e0o s\'e2u b\'ean trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n r\u7891 i n\'ean c\'e0ng \u273 \u7883 t th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ra c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u, n\'f3 l\'e0m con c\u7863 c tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lu\uc0\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng v\'ea v\'ea c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a em l\'e0m con c\u7863 c anh tr\u7855 ng tinh r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  \'e1? Em nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c th\u7871  \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  ! \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\'f4i \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean cho con c\u7863 c tu\u7897 t ra kh\u7887 i c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n r\u7891 i quay l\u7841 i nh\'ecn. Th\u7845 y con c\u7863 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh che mi\u7879 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i n\'f3 nhi\uc0\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec.. nhi\uc0\u7873 u c\'e0ng s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913  sao! Th\'f4i ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng anh \u273 \u7883 t ti\u7871 p n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh chu m\'f4i l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i l\'e0m ki\uc0\u7875 u kh\'e1c \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u kh\'e1c l\'e0 ki\u7875 u n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec ki\uc0\u7875 u \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y n\'e0y, anh \u273 \u7905  m\u7897 t ch\'e2n em l\'ean, trong phim c\u361 ng c\'f3 ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a1\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Ch\u417 i ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y lu\'f4n. N\'e0o nh\u7845 c ch\'e2n l\'ean n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n nh\u7845 c m\u7897 t ch\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean, t\'f4i \u273 \u7905  l\u7845 y m\u7897 t ch\'e2n r\u7891 i cong ch\'e2n xu\u7889 ng lu\u7891 n \u273 \'fang con c\u7863 c m\'e0 \u7845 n v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y kh\'f3 kh\u259 n v\u7899 i t\'f4i l\u7855 m khi\u7871 n \u273 \'fat m\'e3i m\'e0 con c\u7863 c c\u7913  tr\u432 \u7907 t ra tr\u432 \u7907 t v\'e0o c\'e1i khe m\'e0 ch\u432 a chui v\'e0o l\u7895 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'fai xu\u7889 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 n\'f3 c\uc0\u7913  ch\u7885 c su\u7889 t \u7903  ngo\'e0i th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! Ch\uc0\u432 a \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o th\'f4i ch\u7913  \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o th\'ec qu\'e1 s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, n\'f3 tr\u417 n qu\'e1 n\'ean khoongv \'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra n\u7919 a em \u417 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng l\u7921 a m\'e0 \u7845 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c cho c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c ng\u7853 p v\'e0o b\'ean trong. Qu\u7923 nh \u7913  l\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7865  th\'f4i anh v\'e0o r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7905  ch\'e2n Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7845 p. C\'e1i ki\u7875 u n\'e0y th\'ec con c\u7863 c kh\'f4ng chui \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o s\'e2u b\'ean trong m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c v\'e0 m\u7897 t n\u7917 a con c\u7863 c v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'ednh v\'ec th\uc0\u7871  c\'e1i l\'e0m cho c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a qu\u7923 nh t\'ea h\u417 n, n\'f3 l\u7841 i c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c h\u417 n n\u7919 a. V\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 t v\u7915 a n\'fat m\u7841 nh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0 d\'f4i m\'f4i \u273 ang th\'e8m kh\'e1t s\u7921  \'e2u y\u7871 m t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y s\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3\'85 s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng h\u417 n ki\u7875 u doggy nh\u432 ng m\'e0.. m\u7887 i ch\'e2n qu\'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec.. th\uc0\u7871  c\'e0ng l\'e0m m\u7841 nh nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i nh\u7845 p m\u7841 nh h\u417 n, \u273 \u7871 n khi n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n tu\'f4n ra th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u th\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i n\uc0\u7857 m lu\'f4n xu\u7889 ng n\u7873 n nh\'e0 t\u7855 m anh \u273 \u7883 t c\'e1i n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng banh l\u7891 n ra \u273 \u7907 i con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\u7855 m s\'e2u v\'e0o n\'ean trong. C\'e1i n\u7873 n nh\'e0 t\u7855 m kh\'e1 tr\u417 n n\'ean t\'f4i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\'e3i m\u7899 i tr\u7909  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0 nh\'e9t con c\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7919  hai c\'e1i ch\'e2n t\'f4i nh\u7845 p li\'ean h\u7891 i r\u7891 i b\u7855 n \u7847 m \u7847 m tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o th\u7853 t s\'e2u b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895 . Qu\u7923 nh cong l\u432 ng d\u7853 y, tay \'f4m l\u7845 y h\'f4ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho v\'e0o h\uc0\u7871 t b\'ean trong \u273 i..em th\'edch anh cho v\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\uc0\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'f3 c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 \uc0\u7845 m \u7845 m s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m anh \u7841 .. t\'ea ph\'e1t \u273 i\'ean lu\'f4n \u7845 y..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  cho v\'e0o xong u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a \u273 \'f9a ngh\u7883 ch trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m \u273 \u7871 n khi c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u417 i l\u7841 nh th\'ec m\u7899 i m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  v\'e0o m\'e0 t\'f3t v\'e0o trong nh\'e0. Th\u7901 i b\u7845 y gi\u7901  ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 c\'e1i g\'ec hay ho n\'ean c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7913 a m\u7903  nh\u7841 c l\'ean nghe r\u7891 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'ea v\'ea c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa trong c\'e1i \'e1o t\'f4i n\'f3i kh\uc0\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\u7891 n em c\'f2n r\'e1t kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng.. ch\uc0\u7855 c ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c v\u7899 i l\u7841 i quen c\'e1i \u7845 y c\u7911 a anh r\u7891 i n\'ean n\'f3 kh\'f4ng r\'e1t n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  \u273 i mua thu\u7889 c u\u7889 ng lu\'f4n nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Nh\u432 ng anh \u273 i \u273 i, em \u7903  nh\'e0 th\'f4i, \u273 i c\'f9ng m\'e0 c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o bi\u7871 t ng\u7841 i l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i ph\'f3ng xe \u273 \u7841 p \u273 i mua thu\u7889 c ng\u7915 a thai cho Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i v\u7873 . C\u7843  hai ngh\u7883 ch c\u7843  bu\u7893 i tr\u432 a r\u7891 i \'f4m nhau ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u.\
