\cf2 \cb3 Hai r\uc0\u432 \u7905 i d\u7853 y, c\u417 n gi\'f3 tho\u7843 ng tho\u7843 ng l\'f9a t\u7915  c\'e1i c\u7917 a s\u7893  ph\'eda b\'ean h\'f4ng nh\'e0 v\'e0o l\'e0m t\'f4i t\u7881 nh h\u7859 n. C\'e1i v\'e1y c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ph\u7845 t ph\u417  l\'fac ph\u7891 ng l\'fac x\u7909 p l\'e0m t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n l\u7845 p l\'f3 ph\'eda b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Lu\uc0\u7891 n tay v\'e0o vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  th\u7911  th\u7881  v\'e0o tai Qu\u7923 nh m\u7863 c d\'f9 Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang ng\'e1i ng\u7911 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh li\uc0\u7871 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i nh\'e9. Anh th\'e8m l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y, d\u7909 i d\u7909 i m\u7855 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u7853 y m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'e0 th\'e8m ngay \'e0, nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea \u273 \'ea ti\u7879 n, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u7903  trong l\u7899 p c\'f3 \u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i n\'e0o \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7841 i y\'eau em l\'e0 m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n, m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n c\u361 ng v\'ec nh\'ecn th\'e8m l\u7855 m \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh b\uc0\u7855 t em m\u7863 c th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. R\'f5 gh\'e9t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i r\'f5 gh\'e9t th\'ec t\'f4i c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7915  m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i chui \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o trong c\'e1i v\'e1y \u273 ang bay ph\u7847 m ph\u7891 ng m\'e0 h\'f4n c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n c\u7911 a qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y v\u7853 y th\'ec th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e2n d\uc0\u7841 ng to ra \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i li\u7871 m l\'e1p c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n. Kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u m\u7899 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 ng\u7911  m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0 c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 m\'f9i n\u7891 ng n\u7891 ng c\u7911 a n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\uc0\u7869  kh\u7869  banh hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng ra, t\'f4i ch\u7885 c l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o h\u7897 t le g\u7849 y g\u7849 y cho n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n tu\'f4n ra th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a r\u7891 i v\'e9n c\'e1i v\'e1y l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh \uc0\u273 \'fat v\'e0o nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913 ng ch\u432 a m\'e0 \u273 \'fat?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913 ng r\u7891 i! Th\u7871  mu\u7889 n m\'fat c\u7911 a anh cho n\'f3 c\u7913 ng \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\u7911 m t\u7881 m g\u7853 t \u273 \'e0u th\'ec t\'f4i t\u7909 t lu\'f4n c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c v\u7849 y v\u7849 y tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7887 m d\u7853 y \u273 \'fat con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t, c\'f4ng nh\u7853 n l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'e8m c\'eda c\u7843 m gi\'e1c hai \u273 \u7913 a qu\u7845 n qu\'fdt b\'ean nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'fat cho chon c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c th\'ec t\'f4i v\u7899 i qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i \u273 \'e8 nhau ra m\'e0 l\'e0m t\'ecnh, l\u7847 n n\'e0y th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i l\'ean b\u7909 ng t\'f4i m\'e0 nh\'fan m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n tu\'f4t ra t\u7841 o th\'e0nh nh\u7919 ng ti\u7871 ng nh\'f3p nh\'e9p kh\'e1 vui tai. Kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u hai \u273 \u7913 a ham hay sao m\'e0 l\'e0m t\'ecnh \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 n m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng m\u7899 i ngh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Chia tay Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0 trong ni\u7873 m kho\'e1i c\u7843 m th\'edch th\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'85\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian th\u7845 m tho\'e1t tr\'f4i nhanh \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7897  t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  n\'f3 nhanh \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nho\uc0\u7857 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'ec \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7871 n l\'fac c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7913 a thi \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c. Do b\u7889  m\u7865  c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t n\'ean ch\u7859 ng ng\u259 n c\u7845 m g\'ec ch\'fang t\'f4i c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'ean th\'e0nh ph\uc0\u7889  nh\u7853 p h\u7885 c c\u7843  hai thu\'ea hai ph\'f2ng tr\u7885  nh\u7887  nh\u7887  s\'e1t nhau, c\u7843  hai mu\u7889 n \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng b\u7889  m\u7865  kh\'f4ng cho n\'ean \u273 \'e0nh ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7919 ng ng\'e0y b\'ecnh y\'ean c\u7911 a hai \u273 \u7913 a b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \'edt l\u7841 i thay v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng s\'f3ng gi\'f3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u n\u7893 i l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u432  th\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7879  th\'ec c\u7843  hai \u273 i h\u7885 c s\'e1ng \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u th\'ec v\u7873  n\u7845 u c\u417 m r\u7891 i \u259 n c\'f9ng nhau. \u272 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u th\'ec c\u7843  hai \u273 i l\'e0m th\'eam \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i m\u7883 t m\u7899 i v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m \uc0\u273 \'f3 chi\u7873 u th\u7913  b\u7849 y, Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i l\'e0m c\'f2n t\'f4i th\'ec \u273 i nh\u7853 u v\u7899 i t\u7909 i b\u7841 n v\'f9 h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 sinh nh\u7853 t m\u7897 t th\u7857 ng trong l\u7899 p. \u272 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i hai gi\u7901  m\u7899 i v\u7873  th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y c\u7917 a ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh v\u7851 n kh\'f3a.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i l\u7841  v\'ec Qu\u7923 nh ch\u432 a bao gi\u7901  \u273 i l\'e0m v\u7873  mu\u7897 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7843 , l\'fac n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 c\'e1i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i tr\u7855 ng \u273 en n\'ean t\'f4i b\u7845 m m\'e1y cho Qu\u7923 nh. Ti\u7871 ng chu\'f4ng \u273 \u7893  d\'e0i nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ai nh\u7845 c m\'e1y c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec, t\'f4i lo l\u7855 ng l\u7855 m, ra c\'e1i qu\'e1n n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7847 u h\u7867 m ng\u7891 i nh\'e2m nhi c\u7889 c tr\'e0 n\'f3ng, tr\u7901 i m\'f9a Thu n\'ean t\u7889 i c\u361 ng se l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang xoa xoa vai \u273 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh v\u7873  th\'ec th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang \'f4m eo m\u7897 t ai \u273 \'f3 t\u7915  chi\u7871 c xe m\'e1y m\u7899 i c\'e1u c\u7841 nh r\u7891 i b\u432 \u7899 c xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 v\u7867  t\'ecnh t\u7913  l\u7855 m, nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\u7843 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i n\'f3ng m\u7855 t l\u7855 m r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng c\u7913  \u273 \u7875  nguy\'ean kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec. \u272 \u7907 i c\'e1i th\u7857 ng \u273 i xe m\'e1y \u273 i v\u7873 , Qu\u7923 nh l\u7919 ng th\u7919 ng \u273 i v\'e0o trong d\'e3y tr\u7885  th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i \u273 i sau.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh m\u7903  c\u7917 a th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i kh\u7869  g\u7885 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 i l\'e0m sao m\'e0 v\u7873  mu\u7897 n th\u7871  v\u7907  y\'eau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  h\u417 i b\u7845 t ng\u7901  v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\'f4i \u7903  \u273 \u7857 ng sau n\'ean Qu\u7923 nh gi\u7853 t th\'f3t ng\u432 \u7901 i quay l\u7841 i. C\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng Qu\u7923 nh kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 em c\'f3 ch\'fat b\uc0\u7853 n \u273 i ch\u417 i v\u7899 i t\u7909 i b\u7841 n, anh b\u7843 o anh \u273 i sinh nh\u7853 t m\'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 th\'ec nh\uc0\u7853 u xong v\u7873  r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y em \u7903  nh\'e0 n\'ean anh \u273 \u7907 i, h\'f4m nay cho anh ng\u7911  c\'f9ng nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n t\u7847 m ba h\'f4m sang ph\'f2ng Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7911  c\'f9ng r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai \'e2n \'e1i v\u7899 i nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a th\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m y\'eau m\'e0 b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t k\'eca! L\u7841 i th\'e8m \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'fac n\'e0o m\'e0 ch\uc0\u7859 ng th\'e8m.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i lu\uc0\u7891 n lu\'f4n tay v\'e0o trong c\'e1i \'e1o kho\'e1c m\u7887 ng m\'e0 xoa xoa c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa. Th\u7845 y c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t h\u417 i l\u7879 ch l\u7879 ch m\u7897 t t\'ed t\'f4i nghi r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng k\u7879 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\u7869  l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7887  tay ra \u273 i, x\'f3m tr\u7885  nh\'ecn th\u7845 y h\u7871 t r\u7891 i k\'eca!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 ai, \uc0\u273 \'eam t\u7889 i th\u7871  n\'e0y, s\u7901  c\'e1i coi n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i b\'f3p nh\uc0\u7865  r\u7891 i k\'e9o Qu\u7923 nh v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a l\u7841 i c\'e1i c\u7841 ch r\u7891 i n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i l\u7841 i th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 xoa con c\u7863 c lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  nh\u7919 ng th\'e1ng cu\u7889 i c\u7845 p \u273 \u7871 n b\'e2y gi\u7901  Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng b\u7841 o d\u7841 n trong chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3. C\'f3 l\u7869  d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1i khu\'f4n m\u7863 t ng\'e2y th\u417  l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n b\'e0 lu\'f4n kh\'e1t khao d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a l\'fat n\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh s\'f3c con c\u7863 c th\'ec t\'f4i lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o trong c\'e1i qu\u7847 n m\'e0 x\'f5a oa c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n. Hai ng\'f3n tay ch\u7841 m xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i khe th\'ec \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n \u7891  \u7841 t ch\u7843 y ra r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i t\u7911 m t\u7881 m b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao h\'f4m nay h\uc0\u259 ng th\u7871 , bao nhi\'eau l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! T\uc0\u7841 i anh l\'e0m em th\'e8m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m anh l\uc0\u7855 m kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh c\'fai xu\u7889 ng nhanh ch\'f3ng c\u7903 i c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i ra r\u7891 i m\'f3c con c\u7863 c cho v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng m\'fat ngon l\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng m\'fat th\'ec t\'f4i c\'e0ng s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0 n\u7855 m nh\u7865  m\'e1i t\'f3c \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7855 t th\u7853 t s\'e0nh \u273 i\u7879 u c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh m\'e0 nh\u7845 p v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  \u273 \u7875  Qu\u7923 nh m\'fat ch\'e1n ch\'ea \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'fat th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i n\uc0\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i anh m\'fat l\u7891 n cho n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em th\'edch l\'e0m ki\uc0\u7875 u 69 c\u417 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, v\u7851 n th\'e8m c\u7863 c c\u7911 a anh h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\'ed nh\u7843 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i m\'fat ti\u7871 p.\
