\cf2 \cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh c\u7903 i h\u7871 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o r\u7891 i leo l\'ean c\'e1i gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c gh\'e9p s\u417  s\'e0i m\'e0 li\u7871 m m\'fat nhau theo ki\u7875 u 69.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m, t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c l\'e0 th\u7857 ng \u273 i c\'f9ng Qu\u7923 nh k\'edch th\'edch th\u7871  n\'e0o th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Banh hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\uc0\u7891 n ra r\u7891 i t\'f4i ng\u7853 m th\u7853 t s\'e2u v\'e0o c\'e1i mu m\'e0 m\'fat r\u7891 i ch\u7885 c c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7907 i v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n ngo\'e1y m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7895  l\u7891 n Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng c\'f2n h\u7891 ng h\'e0o nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 h\u417 i th\'e2m \u273 en l\u7841 i v\'ec t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0m kh\'e1 nhi\u7873 u. C\'e0ng li\u7871 m th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng m\'fat m\u7841 nh h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng t\'f3p t\'e9p vang l\'ean th\u7853 t to m\u7895 i khi Qu\u7923 nh nh\'e8 nh\'e8 ng\u7853 m m\u7895 i c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c, t\'f4i th\'ec ch\u7859 ng k\'e9p m\'fat c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n t\u7897 p t\u7897 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, n\'f3 ch\u7843 y nh\u7877 u xu\u7889 ng c\u7843  c\'e1i m\u361 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\uc0\u7871 m l\'e1p ch\'e1n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 n l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i r\u7891 i c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c nh\'e9t lu\'f4n v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n \u432 \u7899 t nh\u7865 p m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec em mu\uc0\u7889 n c\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\uc0\u7903 i \u273 \u7897 ng m\'e0 mu\u7889 n c\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a r\u7891 i \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\'fan. C\'e1i gi\u432 \u7901 ng k\'eau k\u7869 o k\u7865 t h\'f2a nh\u7883 p theo nh\u7919 ng c\'fa nh\'fan c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh. C\u7889  g\u7855 ng Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0m sao \u273 \u7875  c\u7843  c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c ng\u7853 p l\'fat v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n n\'f3 r\u7901 i ra m\u7897 t t\'ed n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'e0ng nh\'fan m\u7841 nh th\'ec t\'f4i c\'e0ng b\'f3p m\u7841 nh c\'e1i v\'fa m\'e0 h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 kh\'f4ng v\u7907 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3.. l\uc0\u7891 n em s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m\'85em th\'e8m qu\'e1\'85!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u7849 y h\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m th\'ec nh\'fan m\uc0\u7841 nh \u273 i em.. anh th\'edch m\'e0..v\u7907  y\'eau!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\'fan m\u7841 nh, m\'e1i t\'f3c l\'f2a x\'f2a tr\'f4ng c\'e0ng kh\'eau g\u7907 i. \u272 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\'fan ch\'e1n ch\'ea th\'ec t\'f4i l\u7853 t Qu\u7923 nh xu\u7889 ng ch\u7891 m l\'ean m\'e0 nh\u7845 p th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y th\'ec c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n nho\'e9t n\u432 \u7899 c ra h\u7901 n, Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng run l\'ean v\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng, tay tay gh\'ec ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y m\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  c\u7889  g\u7855 ng cho con c\u7863 c ngo\'e1y s\'e2u b\'ean trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e1n ki\uc0\u7875 u b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec t\'f4i l\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7907 c Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0o ch\uc0\u7893 ng m\'f4ng anh doggy!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ngo\'e1i l\u7841 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Doggy m\uc0\u7841 nh nh\u432  l\'fac n\'e3y \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh th\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 s\u7907  ph\'f2ng b\'ean nghe th\u7845 y kh\'f4ng v\u7907 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ph\'f2ng b\'ean c\uc0\u7841 nh v\u7873  qu\'ea r\u7891 i, h\'f4m nay em th\'e2y hai \u273 \u7913 a h\u7885 c c\'f9ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng m\'ecnh kh\u259 n g\'f3i v\u7873  r\u7891 i..l\'e0m m\u7841 nh m\u7899 i s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7891 ng \u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7841 nh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng r\'ean to. D\'e3y tr\u7885  tr\u7889 ng ho\'e1c kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai Qu\u7923 nh r\'ean to th\u7871  c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng ai bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7845 p ch\'e1n th\'ea th\'ec con c\u7863 c t\'f4i gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t phun \u273 \u7847 y tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n \u273 ang r\u7897 ng to\'e1c \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh v\'f2ng tay ra \u273 \u7857 ng sau, \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\u7889  k\'e9o s\'e1t v\'e0o r\u7891 i r\'ean kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7855 n s\'e2u v\'e0o trong n\u7919 a \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e0o s\'e2u c\'f2n g\'ec n\uc0\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai \'e2n \'e1i v\u7899 i nhau m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec l\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 vu\u7889 t ve nhau. Xoa xoa l\u7845 y c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'fac n\'e3y anh th\uc0\u7845 y anh n\'e0o \u273 \'e8o em v\u7873  \u273 \u7845 y? Nh\'ecn c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 \u7865 p trai nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u417 i ng\u7905  ng\'e0ng khi t\'f4i n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Nh\'ecn bi\u7875 u hi\u7879 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0 t\'f4i bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i. Nghe t\'f4i h\u7887 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh g\u432 \u7907 ng c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7841 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'f4i m\'e0 anh, c\'f9ng h\u7885 c v\u7899 i em \u7845 y m\'e0, h\'ec h\'ec th\u7871  anh ghen \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'e2ng qu\uc0\u417  t\'f4i b\u7843 o l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i ghen m\u7897 t t\'ed, xinh g\'e1i nh\u432  em d\u7877  b\u7883  t\'e1n m\u7845 t l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i d\u7909 i d\u7909 i m\'e1 v\'e0o tay t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\'e0 gi\u7919  \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9. Kh\'f4ng c\u7849 n th\u7853 n l\'e0 m\u7845 t \u273 \u7845 y, em l\'e0 em c\'f3 h\u417 i nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'e1n \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai \'f4m nhau ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau th\'ec m\u7899 i d\u7853 y. Chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891  r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai \u273 i h\u7885 c \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 i l\'e0m th\'eam c\'f2n Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec c\'f3 vi\u7879 c n\'ean \u7903  l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng.\
