\cf2 \cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian tr\'f4i qua nhanh th\u7845 m tho\'e1t t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t n\u259 m th\u7913  nh\u7845 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Sang n\uc0\u259 m th\u7913  hai th\'ec c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c nhi\u7873 u n\'ean t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ch\'fa \'fd \u273 \u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh n\u7919 a, m\u7863 c d\'f9 \u7903  g\u7847 n nhau nh\u432 ng kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch xa d\u7847 n d\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch hay v\'ec t\'ecnh c\u7843 m m\'e0 ch\'fang t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\'ecnh y\'eau phai nh\u7841 t d\u7847 n cho \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t h\'f4m.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m \uc0\u273 \'f3 cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n, t\'f4i ph\u7843 i t\u259 ng ca trong khi \u273 \'f3 Qu\u7923 nh thi \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ngh\u7881 . T\'f4i l\'e0m \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n ch\'edn gi\u7901  t\u7889 i nh\u432 ng do \u273 \'f4ng kh\'e1ch qu\'e1 n\'ean h\u7871 t h\'e0ng qu\'e1n \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a s\u7899 m n\'ean t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7873  nh\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n d\'e3y tr\u7885  \u273 \'f3 th\'f4i nh\u432 ng gi\u7901  hai ch\'fang t\'f4i chuy\u7875 n ph\'f2ng \u273 \u7871 n \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau r\u7891 i v\'e0 thu\'ea lu\'f4n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\'f2n c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec tr\u7843  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7873  s\u7899 m l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u432 \u7903 ng n\'f3ng l\'ean t\'f4i h\'ed h\u7917 ng mua \'edt b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t v\u7873  cho Qu\u7923 nh v\'ec Qu\u7923 nh th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n b\'e1nh ng\u7885 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a v\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 nghi v\'ec c\'f3 c\'e1i xe m\'e1y m\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 nh\'ecn th\u7845 y tr\u432 \u7899 c kia. Quay sang c\u259 n ph\'f2ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u7903  cu\u7889 i g\'f3c th\'ec th\u7845 y \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a im \u7881 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y h\u417 i l\u7841  v\'ec b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh v\u7873  nh\'e0 l\'e0 m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra lu\'f4n ch\u7913  ch\u7859 ng bao gi\u7901  \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a th\u7871  n\'e0y d\'f9 l\'e0 tr\u7901 i t\u7889 i. H\u417 n n\u7919 a bi\u7871 t t\'f4i h\'f4m nay t\u259 ng ca v\u7873  mu\u7897 n n\'ean \u273 \'e1ng nh\u7869  Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i m\u7903  c\u7917 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  th\u7845 y l\'e0 l\u7841  t\'f4i nh\u7911  th\u7847 m, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 l\u7841 i c\'f9ng b\u7841 n \u273 \'e8 \u273 i \u259 n g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y r\u7891 i. T\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'f4i ti\u7871 n \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i c\u7917 a g\u7895  xanh b\u7907 t b\u7857 ng g\u7895  \u7885 p \u7865 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a ti\u7871 n s\'e1t \u273 \u7871 n th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y ti\u7871 ng r\'ean \u432  \u432  kh\u7869  kh\u7869  trong ph\'f2ng vang ra. C\'e1nh c\u7917 a g\u7895  m\u7887 ng manh kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7881  \u273 \u7875  ng\u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i \'e2m thanh trong \u273 \'f3 ph\'e1t ra r\'f9 c\'f3 l\u7869  \u273 \'e3 c\u7889  g\u7855 ng k\'ecm n\'e9n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghi\'eang \uc0\u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i gh\'e9 s\'e1t v\'e0o th\'ec \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ti\u7871 ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u431 \'85.anh \u417 i..m\u7841 nh ch\'fat n\u7919 a \u273 i.. em \u273 \'e3 l\u7855 m..s s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m anh \u417 i..\u432 .\u432 .\u273 \'e3 qu\'e1.. th\'edch qu\'e1 ..\u432 .\u432 . nhanh l\'ean..anh \u7845 y s\u7855 p v\u7873  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a nghe ti\u7871 ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\'ean nh\u432 u v\u7853 y th\'ec \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i c\u361 ng c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i nam gi\u7899 i vang l\'ean:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng sao \uc0\u273 \'e2u.. n\'f3 c\'f3 v\u7873  ngay \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 em s\u7907 .. h\'f4m nay n\'f3 b\u7843 o t\u259 ng ca c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. Em th\'edch anh l\'e0m m\u7841 n h\u7843 ? V\u7853 y th\'ec anh l\'e0m cho s\u432 \u7899 ng n\'e0y.. \u272 \u7883 t cho banh c\'e1i l\u7891 n \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c1p s\'e1t tai v\'e0o t\'f4i c\'f2n nghe r\'f5 h\uc0\u417 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7919 ng ti\u7871 ng ph\'e0nh ph\u7841 ch th\u7853 t to vang l\'ean n\u7919 a. Trong tim th\u7855 t l\u7841 i v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i ph\u7843 n b\u7897 i t\'f4i th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7871 u gi\u7901  \u273 \u7841 p c\u7917 a v\'e0o c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0m g\'ec v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng vi\u7879 c s\u7843 y ra tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t. T\'f4i v\'f2ng ra sau, nh\'e0, tr\'e8o qua t\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i h\'e9 h\'e9 c\'e1i c\u7917 a s\u7893  ph\'f2ng t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i c\uc0\u7917 a s\u7893  n\'e0y g\u7847 n nh\u432  t\'f4i \'edt khi m\u7903  nh\u432 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  ngo\'e0i. H\'e9 h\'e9 c\'e1nh c\u7917 a c\'e1u b\u7849 n b\u7909 i n\u7891  t\'f4i nghi\'eang m\u7855 t v\'e0o trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 nh t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7853 p v\'e0o m\u7863 t t\'f4i khi\u7871 n t\'f4i v\'f4 c\'f9ng s\u7919 ng s\u7901 . Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng cho th\u7857 ng kia \u7903  ph\'eda sau doggy th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\'e1m tay v\'e0o th\'e0nh gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng nh\u7893 ng c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean th\u7853 t cao c\'f2n th\u7857 ng kia \u7903  \u273 \u7859 ng sau \u7845 n m\u7841 nh con c\u7863 c v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn r\'f5 c\'e1i th\'e2n c\uc0\u7863 c t\'f4i th\u7845 y n\'f3 nh\u7851 y n\u432 \u7899 c tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m n\'ean m\u7899 i ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  nh\'ecn m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i l\u7853 t ng\u432 \u7907 c Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i m\'e0 l\'e0m ki\u7875 u truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng. L\u7847 n n\'e0y t\'f4i th\u7845 y r\'f5 Qu\u7923 nh gh\'ec ch\u7863 t th\u7857 ng kia th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng k\'ecm \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'f2ng m\'ecnh n\u7919 a, t\'f4i quay l\u7841 i r\u7891 i ph\'e1 c\u7917 a v\'e0o lu\'f4n. C\u7843  hai ng\u7905  ng\'e0ng tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t t\'f4i v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  t\'f4i v\u7873  v\'e0o l\'fac n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn n\'e9t s\uc0\u7907  h\'e3i l\u7897  r\'f5 tr\'ean khu\'f4n m\u7863 t xinh x\u7855 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\'e0o \u273 i r\u7891 i ta n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe nh\uc0\u432  v\u7853 y c\u7843  hai cu\u7889 ng cu\u7891 ng m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o v\'e0o, Qu\u7923 nh v\u7851 n s\u7907  h\'e3i l\u7855 m r\u7891 i l\u7855 p b\u7855 p kh\'f4ng n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u g\'ec, c\'f2n th\u7857 ng \u272 \'e0n \'f4ng kia th\'ec m\u7863 c qu\u7847 n \'e1o xong r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'f4i.. t\'f4i xin l\uc0\u7895 i.. t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \'fd ch\u7859 ng qua t\'f4i kh\'f4ng k\'ecm n\'e9n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t t\'f4i \u7847 ng \u7853 c chu\u7849 n b\u7883  ch\u7843 y ra v\'ec gi\u7853 n v\'ec th\u7845 y ch\'e1n n\u7843 n. T\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  b\'e2y gi\u7901  thanh minh ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng th\'e9 th\'f4i, c\u7853 u v\u7873  \u273 i, s\'e1ng mai ch\'edn gi\u7901  \u7903  qu\'e1n caf\'e9 \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f5 ch\'fang ta n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7857 ng \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng \u273 \'f3 l\u7855 p b\u7855 p v\'e2ng d\u7841  r\u7891 i v\u7897 i v\'e0ng ch\u7841 y ra s\'e2n n\u7893  con xe m\'e1y m\'e0 ph\'f3ng m\u7845 t h\'fat. Qu\u7923 nh l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i l\u7855 p b\u7855 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em..e\'85m xin l\uc0\u7895 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ai c\'f3 l\uc0\u7895 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2u h\u7871 t, anh mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i em l\'e0 em c\'f3 c\'f2n y\'eau anh kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u kh\'f3c m\'e0 n\u7845 c nh\u7865 . T\'f4i \u273 \u432 a h\u7897 p kh\u259 n gi\u7845 y cho r\u7891 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\'f3 c\'f2n y\'eau anh kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\'fat th\'edt tr\u7843  l\u7901 i :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a\'85\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Y\'eau hay kh\'f4ng m\'e0 em c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 sao. Th\u7871  em c\'f3 y\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i kia kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em.. c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i b\u7921 c v\u7899 i th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  n\'e0y n\'ean t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec em bi\u7871 t c\'e1i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\'fac n\'e0y g\'e0o to l\'ean r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t g\'ec h\u7871 t em xin l\u7895 i hu hu..em sai r\u7891 i tha l\u7895 i cho em ..\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ti\uc0\u7871 n l\u7841 i Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i anh \u273 i.. em c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng? C\'f3 kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Gi\uc0\u7885 ng t\'f4i \u273 anh l\u7841 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 a tay qu\u7879 t n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t r\u7891 i g\u7853 t nh\u7865  \u273 \u7847 u m\u7897 t c\'e1i. Nh\u432 ng v\u7915 a g\u7853 t nh\u7865  \u273 \u7847 u xong Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869 .. t\u7841 i anh kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m em nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'ean em m\u7899 i th\u7871  n\'e0y.. em sai r\u7891 i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7855 c nh\u7865  \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  ai sai ai \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng c\'f2n quan tr\u7885 ng n\u7919 a em \u7841 , anh mu\u7889 n h\u7887 i th\'eam em v\u7899 i n\'f3 l\'e0m m\u7845 y l\u7847 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7897 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean anh \u7841 \'85 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ph\uc0\u7843 i l\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7873 n kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7847 n th\u7913  ba anh \u7841 .. anh tha l\u7895 i cho em.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\uc0\u7903  d\'e0i t\'f4i bi\u7871 t c\'f3 l\u7869  t\u7915  \u273 \'e2y m\u7845 t Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i n\'ean t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i th\uc0\u7871  l\'e0 anh bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i, gi\u7901  anh \u273 i l\'e0m m\u7879 t. Anh mu\u7889 n ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i.. c\'f3 g\'ec s\'e1ng mai ch\'fang ta n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh van n\'e0i t\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i kh\u7869  g\u7841 t nh\u7865  tay ra r\u7891 i ra \u273 \'f3ng l\u7841 i c\'e1i c\u7917 a, v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m r\u7917 a qua c\'e1i m\u7863 t r\u7891 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng n\u7857 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\u7857 m quay m\u7863 t v\'e0o t\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f3c th\'fat th\'ed c\'f2n t\'f4i tr\u7857 n tr\u7885 c m\'e3i m\'e0 kh\'f4ng ng\u7911  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n s\'e1ng th\'ec t\'f4i thi\u7871 p \u273 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y, s\u7917 a so\u7841 n \u273 \u7891  r\u7891 i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh ra qu\'e1n caf\'e9 v\'e0 b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho th\u7857 ng kia xu\u7889 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chung \uc0\u7903  qu\'e1n caf\'e9 n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean y\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y t\u7889 t cho m\'ecnh sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i v\u7873  nh\'e0 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891  r\u7891 i d\u7885 n ra ch\u7895  kh\'e1c \u7903  lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f3c th\'fat th\'edt nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e0nh d\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  cho t\'f4i, t\'f4i thu\'ea lu\'f4n nh\'e0 tr\u7885  c\u361 ng g\u7847 n \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c n\u259 m h\u7885 c th\u7913  ba c\u7911 a m\'ecnh, Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec c\u361 ng v\u7853 y. N\'f3i chung t\'ecnh y\'eau \u273 \u7847 u qua nhanh l\u7855 m, d\'f9 m\u7899 i ch\u7881  h\u417 n m\u7897 t n\u259 m sau th\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng qu\'ean d\u7847 n \u273 i cu\u7897 c t\'ecnh \u273 au \u273 \u7899 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 kh\'e1c x\u432 a kh\'e1 nhi\u7873 u, \u259 n ch\u417 i h\u417 n s\'e0nh \u273 i\u7879 u h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n y\'eau c\'e1i th\u7857 ng m\'e0 t\'f4i k\u7875  n\u7919 a m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 l\u7841 i y\'eau m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng kh\'e1c s\'e0nh \u273 i\u7879 u h\u417 n r\u7891 i.\
