\cf2 \cb3 Cu\uc0\u7897 c \u273 \u7901 i c\'f3 qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u ng\'e3 r\u7869 . Sau khi qu\'ean \u273 i Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i tham gia ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng \u7903  c\'e1c nh\'f3m t\'ecnh nguy\u7879 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n v\'e0 t\'f4i k\u7875  \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7889 i t\'ecnh th\u7913  hai c\u7911 a t\'f4i cho \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n b\'e2y gi\u7901 \'85\cb1 \
\
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'f3 l\'e0 Huy\u7873 n, m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i con g\'e1i k\'e9m t\'f4i ba tu\u7893 i, khi t\'f4i l\'ean h\u7885 c n\u259 m th\u7913  4 th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o nh\u7853 p h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7899  nh\u7845 t h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 otoi c\'f3 m\u7897 t bu\u7893 i t\'ecnh nguy\u7879 n \u7903  m\u7897 t ng\'f4i tr\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7887  c\'e1ch ch\u7895  ch\'fang t\'f4i ch\u7915 ng s\'e1u m\u432 \u417 i km.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\'f9ng qu\'ea v\u7899 i t\'f4i n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \'e0u hai anh em n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n tho\u7843 i m\'e1i l\u7855 m, h\'f4m \u273 i t\'ecnh nguy\u7879 n Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 xe n\'ean t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f3n Huy\u7873 n l\'fac s\'e1ng s\u7899 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7901 i th\'e1ng ch\'edn, bu\u7893 i s\'e1ng h\u417 i l\u7841 nh, t\'f4i \u273 \'e8o Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n \u273 i\u7875 m t\u7853 p k\u7871 t. Huy\u7873 n v\u7883 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o eo t\'f4i, v\u7851 n gi\u7919  kho\u7843 ng c\'e1ch nh\u432 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n vui v\u7867  l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh Minh nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t l\'fac th\'ec vui nh\u432 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  c\'f3 m\u7897 t n\u7895 i bu\u7891 n g\'ec kh\'f3 t\u7843  l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i tr\'eau Huy\uc0\u7873 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7895 i bu\u7891 n g\'ec m\'e0 kh\'f3 t\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a nh\u432 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'f3 t\u7843  l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n troll Huy\u7873 n ti\u7871 p n\'ean t\'f4i tr\'eau;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  \u273 \'fang r\u7891 i. N\u7895 i bu\u7891 n \u273 i nh\'e0 v\u7879  sinh.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2y Huy\u7873 n v\'e9o t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Gh\'e9t. Troll em \'e0! Mu\u7889 n \u273 i th\'ec d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, s\'e1ng s\u7899 m kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3p phanh xe \uc0\u273 \'e1nh c\'e1i k\'e9t m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\'f4i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, d\u7921 ng xe th\'ec Huy\u7873 n m\u7903  to tr\'f2n m\u7855 t ra n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 th\uc0\u7871  \u273 i th\u7853 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bu\uc0\u7891 n th\'ec \u273 i th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng l\u7869  \u273 i \u273 \'f9a h\u7887 i th\u7871  c\u361 ng h\u7887 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\'ec t\'f4i ph\'ec c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m l\u7841 i \u273 i ti\u7871 p. Nh\'e9o t\'f4i th\'eam c\'e1i n\u7919 a Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'e1m \uc0\u273 \'f9a em \'e0..!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  chuy\u7879 n tr\'f2 v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n. T\'f4i v\u7889 n c\u361 ng \u273 \u7875  \'fd Huy\u7873 n nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i v\'ec c\'f4 b\'e9 c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e0u n\'e2u \u273 \u7865 p l\u7855 m. N\'f3 trong veo nh\u432  \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t m\'e8o v\u7853 y. H\'f4m \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7871 n m\u7845 y ng\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7901 ng ch\'fang t\'f4i t\'ecnh nguy\'ean, d\u7841 y c\'e1c em ch\u417 i tr\'f2 ch\u417 i m\'faa h\'e1t c\'e1c ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  khi c\'e1c em tan h\u7885 c ch\'fang t\'f4i m\u7899 i ngh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i tr\'ean \'f4 t\'f4 m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a h\'e1t h\'f2 ch\'e1n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i xu\u7889 ng \u259 n, t\'f4i th\'ec v\u7851 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7899 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng \u273 o\'e0n nh\u432 ng mu\u7889 n ch\u259 m s\'f3c Huy\u7873 n h\u417 n n\'ean ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh r\u7891 i tr\'eau \u273 \'f9a n\'e0y n\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u v\u7873  t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a Huy\u7873 n v\u7873  nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\'e0 l\u432 \u7907 n v\'f2ng v\'f2ng h\u7891  ch\u417 i. Sen b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\'e0n r\u7891 i n\'ean t\'f4i mua m\u7845 y c\'e1i \u273 \'e0i sen c\u7843  ngai c\'f9ng b\'f3c ngh\u7883 c r\u7891 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i v\'e9n m\'e1i t\'f3c l\'ean l\'ed nh\'ed n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  ch\u7883  \u7845 y l\u7841 i ph\u7843 n b\u7897 i anh nh\u432  v\u7853 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\'f2n kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  hu\u7889 ng chi l\'e0 em! Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 do anh kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhu c\u7847 u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'ecn t\'f4i b\u297 u m\'f4i r\u7891 i h\u7913  l\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh ngh\uc0\u297  ch\u7883  \u7845 y d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng th\u7871  ch\u7855 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nheo m\uc0\u7855 t t\'f4i n\'f3i l\u7841 i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c lu\'f4n, l\'fac l\'e0m v\u7899 i th\u7857 ng kia h\u259 ng h\'e1i l\u7855 m c\u417  m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n th\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec ti\u7871 n s\'e1t l\u7841 i, t\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i h\u7887 i d\'f2.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0m v\u7899 i anh c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng k\'e9m \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Em nghe anh k\u7875  \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7883  \u7845 y v\u7899 i anh c\u361 ng c\'f3 nhu c\u7847 u cao v\'e3i nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Quay l\uc0\u7841 i t\'f4i l\u7915  m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i \u7845 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o tr\'e1n Huy\u7873 n m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\uc0\u7867  con h\u7887 i linh tinh. Kh\'f4ng tr\u7843  l\u7901 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ra v\u7867  g\u7853 t g\'f9 r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\u7871  l\'e0 em bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i, ch\u7913 ng t\u7887  anh c\u361 ng thu\u7897 c lo\u7841 i d\'e2m d\'ea!\cb1 \
\cb3 Quay l\uc0\u7841 i t\'f4i h\u7845 t h\'e0m r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f3 mu\u7889 n anh d\'e2m d\'ea lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e1ch \uc0\u273 \u7845 y, \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o em \u273 \'e1nh ch\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y th\'ec \uc0\u273 \'e1nh n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i v\'f2ng tay ra lu\'f4n m\'e0 \'f4m l\uc0\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n. Huy\u7873 n cho ngay c\'e1i c\'f9i ch\u7887  v\'e0o b\u7909 ng t\'f4i \u273 au \u273 i\u7871 ng. \'d4m c\'e1i b\u7909 ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng th\'ec Huy\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ha ha! Cho ch\uc0\u7871 t. \u272 \u7915 ng t\u432 \u7903 ng em d\u7877  b\u7855 t n\u7841 t nghe ch\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i gi\uc0\u7843  b\u7897  v\u7851 n \'f4m b\u7909 ng k\'eau \u273 au m\'e0 kh\'f4i n\'f3i c\'e2u n\'e0o. Huy\u7873 n l\'fac n\'e0y m\u7899 i h\u417 i s\u7907 , kh\u7869  lay nh\u7865  t\'f4i r\u7891 i ho\u7843 ng h\u7889 t n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh..anh c\'f3 sao kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u7845 y, em xin l\u7895 i, em \u273 \'e1nh nh\u7865  m\'e0..\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n gi\u7843  b\u7897  \u273 \u7871 n khi Huy\u7873 n c\'fai s\'e1t th\u7845 p ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i b\u7853 t d\u7853 y \'f4m ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n m\'e0 h\'f4n l\'ean lu\'f4n m\'f4i Huy\u7873 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7883  b\u7845 t ng\u7901  n\'ean Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng g\'ec c\u7843 , l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i m\u7897 t ph\'e1t r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  \u273 \u7849 y t\'f4i ra r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'e1m l\uc0\u7915 a em\'85 d\u7895 i lu\'f4n!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\'e2ng qu\uc0\u417  b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7915 a th\'ec m\u7899 i h\'f4n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  ha ha!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\'f3 v\u7867  d\u7895 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i v\u7899 i t\'f4i c\'e2u n\'e0o khi\u7871 n t\'f4i ph\u7843 i d\u7895  d\'e0nh m\'e3i. N\'f3i chung l\'e0 con g\'e1i d\u7877  d\u7895  d\'e0nh l\u7855 m. M\u7897 t h\u7891 i r\u7891 i hai \u273 \u7913 a l\u7841 i vui c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i nhau sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i \u273 \'e8o Huy\u7873 n v\u7873  nh\'e0. M\u7885 i chuy\u7879 n t\'ecnh c\u7843 m c\u7913  \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7873 u di\u7877 n ra nh\u432  v\u7853 y cho \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t h\'f4m tr\u7901 i m\u432 a kh\'e1 to.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n b\u7853 n h\u7885 c th\'eam \u7903  tr\u432 \u7901 ng kh\'f4ng mang \'e1o m\u432 a, xe th\'ec l\u7841 i b\u7883  h\u7887 ng n\'ean kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. H\'f4m \u273 \'f3 m\u432 a to gi\'f3 c\u361 ng m\u7841 nh n\'ean Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o t\'f4i qua \u273 \'f3n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Mua v\uc0\u7897 i c\'e1i \'e1o m\u432 a ti\u7879 n l\u7907 i r\u7891 i t\'f4i phi xe qua, nh\'ecn Huy\u7873 n co ro tr\u432 \u7899 c c\u7893 ng tr\u432 \u7901 ng t\'f4i v\u7915 a bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a th\u432 \u417 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n n\u417 i, v\u7913 t c\'e1i \'e1o m\u432 a ra th\'ec Huy\u7873 n c\u7847 m l\u7845 y m\u7863 c v\'e0o r\u7891 i t\'f3t l\'ean xe t\'f4i, n\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch r\u7845 t t\u7921  nhi\'ean:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0o \uc0\u273 i v\u7873 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i quay l\uc0\u7841 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7873  l\'e0 v\u7873  \u273 \'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec v\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 tr\u7885  c\u7911 a em ch\u7913  v\u7873  \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng h\uc0\u7887 i anh b\u7853 n g\'ec \'e0 m\'e0 t\u7921  nhi\'ean nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  n\u7871 u b\u7853 n th\'ec th\'f4i, \'e0 m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 mua \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e1o m\u432 a cho em th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n kh\'f4ng b\u7853 n g\'ec r\u7891 i, h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  \u273 \u432 a anh v\u7873  cho anh c\'e1i g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7873  nh\'e0 em l\'e0m b\'e1nh x\'e8o cho \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i v\uc0\u7867  nh\'ed nh\u7843 nh c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m t\'f4i bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432 ng th\'edch v\'f4 c\'f9ng, \u273 i tr\u7901 i m\u432 a gi\'f3 to n\u7919 a n\'ean hai c\'e1i \'e1o m\u432 a ti\u7879 n l\u7907 i ch\u7859 ng th\u7845 m v\'e0o \u273 \'e2u c\u7843 , n\'f3 r\'e1ch t\u7913  tung khi\u7871 n cho t\'f4i v\'e0 Huy\u7873 n \u432 \u7899 t nh\u7865 p. V\u7873  \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0, Huy\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0o nh\'e0 t\u7855 m r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em thay qu\uc0\u7847 n \'e1o \u273 \'e3, \u432 \u7899 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ra v\u7867  d\'e2m d\'ea b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ha ha! T\'ed v\'e0o ng\'f3 tr\uc0\u7897 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u7845 t h\'e0m Huy\u7873 n tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7841 i th\'edch \u259 n \u273 \'f2n \'e0? Em h\u7885 c v\'f5 th\'eam r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u258 n \u273 \'f2n m\'e0 nh\'ecn tr\u7897 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec t\u7897 i g\'ec m\'ecnh kh\'f4ng nh\'ecn nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i v\'e0o nh\'e0 t\u259 m thay \u273 \u7891 . Ph\'f2ng tr\u7885  c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n c\u361 ng gi\u7889 ng ph\'f2ng tr\u7885  c\u7911 a t\'f4i, n\'f3 b\'e9 b\'e9, c\'f3 m\u7897 t c\'e1i g\'e1c x\'e9p ph\'eda tr\'ean, b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i k\'ea m\u7897 t c\'e1i t\u7911  nh\u7887  m\u7897 t ch\u7895  \u273 \u7875  n\u7845 u n\u432 \u7899 ng, m\u7897 t ch\u7895  ng\u7891 i h\u7885 c v\u7899 i c\'e1i gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0 h\u7871 t ch\u7895  lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng t\'f4i r\'fat c\'e1i kh\u259 n lau \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7853 t c\'e1i m\'e1y s\u7845 y t\'f3c th\u7893 i v\'f9 v\'f9 h\u417 i n\'f3ng v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i cho \u273 \u7905  l\u7841 nh .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n thay \u273 \u7891  m\u7845 y ph\'fat xong th\'ec \u273 i ra, c\'e1i b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o \u7903  nh\'e0 nh\'ecn Huy\u7873 n nh\'ed nh\u7843 nh v\'f4 c\'f9ng, n\u7871 u m\u7863 c b\u7897  \u273 \u7891  n\'e0y ra ngo\'e0i nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 o\'e1n Huy\u7873 n ch\u7855 c ch\u7881  h\u7885 c sinh c\u7845 p hai ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  b\u7883  ng\u7845 m n\u432 \u7899 c m\u432 a n\'ean Huy\u7873 n h\u7855 t x\'ec m\u7845 y c\'e1i, t\'f4i nh\'ecn \u273 i\u7879 u b\u7897  bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i qu\'e1 n\'ean b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i ra \uc0\u273 \'e2y anh d\'f9ng m\'e1y s\u7845 y th\u7893 i cho, \u273 \u7843 m b\u7843 o h\u7871 t h\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f2a v\'f4i ch\uc0\u7841 y \u273 \u7871 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y! Anh d\'f9ng m\'e1y s\uc0\u7845 y m\'e0 s\u432 \u7903 i th\'ec l\u7845 y ti\u7873 n \u273 \'e2u ra h\u7843 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7903 i t\'ed th\'ec t\u7889 n bao nhi\'eau ti\u7873 n \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i b\u7883  nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u th\'ec c\u361 ng ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i k\'e9o Huy\uc0\u7873 n xu\u7889 ng ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh s\u7845 y cho Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4 c\'e1i t\'f3c r\u7891 i th\u7893 i nh\u7865  v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i cho Huy\u7873 n \u7845 m l\'ean. M\'f9i n\u432 \u7899 c hoa v\u7899 i m\'f9i da th\u7883 t c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u432 a th\u7853 t s\u7921  c\'f3 th\u7875  thay \u273 \u7893 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'ecnh b\'f3ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7845 y xong t\'f3c th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  em l\'e0m b\'e1nh x\'e8o cho, c\'e1i b\'e1nh x\'e8o n\'e0y kh\'f4ng gi\u7889 ng b\'e1nh x\'e8o mi\u7873 n T\'e2y \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9,\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'edch n\u7845 u ki\u7875 u g\'ec th\'ec n\u7845 u, anh kh\'f4ng k\'e9n ch\u7885 n h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t anh m\'e0 kh\'f4ng k\'e9n ch\u7885 n m\u7899 i l\'e0 l\u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7853 t th\u7873 ! Kh\'f4ng k\'e9n ch\u7885 n m\u7897 t t\'ed n\'e0o lu\'f4n nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i chu\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7891  n\u7845 u, t\'f4i th\'ec l\u7845 y m\u7845 y quy\u7875 n truy\u7879 n tranh ra ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7885 c, c\u7843  hai v\u7915 a l\'e0m v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m h\u7887 i d\'f2 t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y l\'fac n\'e3y s\uc0\u7845 y t\'f3c cho em th\u7871 , ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c nh\'ecn v\'e0o kh\'e9o l\u7841 i b\u7843 o anh l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau em \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 ! Gi\u7889 ng th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng g\'ec m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng, c\'f3 m\'e0 gi\u7889 ng ch\u259 m con n\'edt h\u417 n thi \u273 \'fang!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Nh\'ecn l\u7841 i m\'ecnh \u273 i m\'e0 b\u7843 o em con n\'edt!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec \uc0\u273 \'fang m\'e0, em c\'f3 tin gi\u7901  em m\u7863 c b\u7897  n\'e0y ra \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 h\u7887 i m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f4ng ai b\u7843 o em l\'e0 sinh vi\'ean \u273 \u7841 i h\u7885 c m\'e0 to\'e0n b\u7843 o em l\'e0 h\u7885 c sinh c\u7845 p hai kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'ecn l\u7841 i m\'ecnh m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec. M\'f9i b\u7897 t r\'e1n tr\'ean ch\u7843 o th\u417 m n\u7913 c l\'e0m t\'f4i ph\'e1t th\'e8m. Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m xong hai ch\'fang t\'f4i nh\'e2m nhi ng\u7855 m m\u432 a r\u417 i \u273 \u7871 n t\u7847 m t\u7889 i.\
