\cf2 \cb3 M\uc0\u432 a m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to s\u7845 m \u273 \'ec \u273 \'f9ng nh\u432 ng Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng s\u7907 . T\'f4i ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y m\uc0\u432 a th\u7871  n\'e0y em kh\'f4ng s\u7907  s\u7845 m \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7907  c\'e1i g\'ec anh, n\'f3 c\'f3 l\'e0m m\'ecnh ch\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 s\u7907 \'85 s\'e1ng l\'f2e l\'f2e c\'f3 khi l\u7841 i th\'edch.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 M\uc0\u432 a m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to, c\'e1i s\'e2n tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 l\'ean \u273 \u7871 n m\u7855 t c\'e1 ch\'e2n r\u7891 i. T\'f4i s\u7907  n\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0o ph\'f2ng tr\u7885  n\'ean b\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913  ki\u7875 u n\'e0y n\u432 \u7899 c kh\'e9o v\'e0o nh\'e0 em nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e0o l\'e0m sao \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh, ch\u7911  nh\'e0 \u273 \'e3 x\'e2y th\'eam c\'e1i v\'e1ch ng\u259 n ba m\u432 \u417 i ph\'e2n r\u7891 i kia k\'eca, kh\'f4ng v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u. Ch\u7895  em l\'e0 ch\u7895  cao nh\u7845 t \u7903  \u273 \'e2y r\u7891 i n\'ean c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng s\u7907 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n linh tinh \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i m\u7883 t th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'f3i qu\'e1 r\u7891 i th\'f4i anh v\u7873  nh\'e0 n\u7845 u c\u417 m \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7902  \u273 \'e2y ch\u417 i v\u7899 i em, v\u7873  l\'e0m g\'ec, \u273 \u7875  em ch\u7841 y \'f9 ra ch\u7907  mua \'edt \u273 \u7891  v\u7873  \u259 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7905  ph\u7843 i n\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7914  \u273 \u7841 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u th\'ec Huy\u7873 n c\u7847 m c\'e1i \'f4, x\u7855 n qu\u7847 n l\'ean r\u7891 i b\'ec b\'f5m l\u7897 i qua c\'e1i s\'e2n \u273 i ra ngo\'e0i mua \'edt \u273 \u7891 . Hai ch\'fang t\'f4i \u259 n c\u417 m n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7901  th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 \u7883 nh v\u7873 , ng\'f3 ra ngo\'e0i s\'e2n th\'ec \'f4i th\'f4i, n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e3 m\u7845 p m\'e9 ngang b\'e1nh xe r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7899  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0ng n\'f3i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i h\'f4m nau \uc0\u7903  \u273 \'e2y m\'e0 ng\u7911  \u273 \u7845 t anh nh\'e9, \u7903  s\'e2n \u273 \'e3 ng\u7853 p th\u7871  n\'e0y anh x\'e1c \u273 inh ra ngo\'e0i ng\'f5 ng\u7853 p \u273 \u7871 n y\'ean xe !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u7853 p \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u th\'ec ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i v\u7873  ch\u7913 , ng\u7911  \u7903  \u273 \'e2y th\'ec c\'f3 m\'e0 th\u7883 t lu\'f4n em \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9. L\'fac \u273 \u7845 y l\u7841 i \u273 \u7893  t\u7841 i anh d\'e2m d\'ea!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o em xem. \u272 \'e1 cho c\'e1i th\'ec l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y l\u7841 i b\u7843 o sao m\'e0 em \'e1c nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec t\u7887  v\u7867  kh\'f4ng ch\u7845 p Huy\u7873 n. Ng\'f3 ra ngo\'e0i s\'e2n th\'ec c\'f4ng nh\u7853 n m\u432 a to th\u7853 t, n\u432 \u7899 c l\'eanh l\'e1ng, m\'e0 c\'e1i ng\'f5 v\'e0o nh\'e0 tr\u7885  th\'ec ng\u7853 p \u273 \u7871 n ngang th\'e2n xe r\u7891 i. Ki\u7875 u n\'e0y m\'e0 d\u7855 t xe ra th\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u7871 t m\'e1y. Ch\u7895  n\'e0y c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 h\'e0ng s\u7917 a xe n\'e0o x\'e1c \u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0 d\u7855 t xe v\u7873  nh\'e0 r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  m\u7897 t ph\'fat r\u7891 i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, \u7903  \u273 \'e2y lu\'f4n h\'ec h\'ec, \u273 \u7875  anh l\u7897 i ra d\u7855 t c\'e1i xe v\'e0o \u273 \'e3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u259 m h\u7903  l\'e0m c\'e1i c\u7847 u b\u7855 c qua c\'e1i th\u7873 m \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i d\u7855 t xe v\'e0o nh\'e0. C\'e1i nh\'e0 tr\u7885  \u273 \'e3 b\'e9 n\'ean khi d\u7855 t c\'e1i xe v\'e0o th\'ec trong nh\'e0 ch\u7853 t k\'edn ch\u7859 ng c\'f2n ch\u7895  n\'e0o n\u7919 a c\u7843 . Hai \u273 \u432 a ng\u7891 i tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7845 y c\'e1i m\'e1y t\'ednh x\'e1ch tay ra m\'e0 ch\u417 i m\u7845 y game \u7903  trong \u273 \'f3.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u417 i ch\'e1n c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t gi\u7901  r\u7891 i. Huy\u7873 n ng\'e1p ng\u7855 n ng\'e1p d\'e0i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i \uc0\u273 i ng\u7911  anh nh\'e9, chia \u273 \'f4i gi\u432 \u7901 ng.. b\u7857 ng c\'e1i g\u7889 i, l\'e9ng ph\'e9ng sang b\'ean ch\u7895  em l\'e0 em \u273 \'e1nh \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n b\u7853 t c\'e1i \u273 \'e8n ng\u7911  r\u7891 i \u273 \u7863 t c\'e1i g\u7889 i ra gi\u7919 a gi\u432 \u7901 ng sau \u273 \'f3 n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng. M\u432 a \u7903  ngo\'e0i v\u7851 n \'e2m \u7927 , ti\u7871 ng l\u7897 p b\u7897 p tr\'ean c\'e1i m\'e1i ng\u7889 i \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 n vang l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7857 m hai anh em n\'f3i chuy\'ean m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Huy\u7873 n lim dim m\u7855 t ng\u7911 . Nh\'ecn khu\'f4n m\u7863 t hi\u7873 n d\u7853 u v\u7899 i \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i \u273 \u7887  m\u7885 ng t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'ecnh c\uc0\u7843 m l\'fac n\'e0y c\'f3 l\u7869  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i y\'eau m\'e0 l\'e0 th\u7845 y th\u432 \u417 ng th\u432 \u417 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat g\'ec \u273 \'f3. H\'ecnh \u7843 nh c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i hi\u7879 n trong t\'e2m tr\'ed nh\u432  ng\'e0y \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 a tay vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  m\'e1i t\'f3c c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n l\'ean ph\'eda tai \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i ng\u7855 m khu\'f4n m\u7863 t m\u7897 t c\'e1ch k\u297  h\u417 n. \u272 \'f4i m\'f4i m\u7845 p m\'e1y l\'e0m t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'fai xu\u7889 ng h\'f4n nh\u7865  m\u7897 t c\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 S\uc0\u7855 p ch\u7841 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o m\'f4i c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n t\'e1t nh\u7865  v\'e0o m\'e1 t\'f4i r\u7891 i m\u7903  m\u7855 t n\u7903  n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i tinh ngh\u7883 ch r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t ngay m\'e0! Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea nh\u432  th\u7871  kia th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\u7875  l\u7851 n v\'e0o \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng gi\u7903  tr\'f2!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Xinh qu\'e1 th\'ec anh h\'f4n tr\uc0\u7897 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i ch\u7913  c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u. H\'f4n th\'ec th\'edch b\u7887  x\u7915  l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. Nh\'ecn \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i c\u7911 a em m\'e0 kh\'f4ng h\'f4n ai th\'ec k\u7875  c\u361 ng l\u7841  \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 . C\u7845 p ba ch\u7855 c l\'e0 h\'f4n \u273 \u7847 y r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh ngh\uc0\u297  ai c\u361 ng nh\u432  anh? H\'ec h\'ec m\'e0 c\'f3 r\u7891 i to\'e0n h\'f4n tr\u7897 m th\'f4i. C\'f3 th\u7857 ng b\u7841 n th\'e2n em c\u432 \u7905 ng h\'f4n h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y \u273 \'fang l\'e0 con g\'e1i th\u7901 i nay, ch\u7881  th\u7871  l\'e0 gi\u7887 i th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7841 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng con trai c\'e1c anh d\u7909  d\u7895 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t ai d\u7909  ai, c\'f3 gi\u7887 i th\'ec c\u432 \u7905 ng h\'f4n anh \u273 i xem n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i xong th\'ec Huy\u7873 n qu\'e0ng tay ra \'f4m t\u7891 i t\u7891 i l\u259 n qua c\'e1i g\u7889 i, \u273 \'e8 l\'ean t\'f4i r\u7891 i h\'f4n lu\'f4n. M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7881  m\'f4i ch\u7841 m m\'f4i th\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i lu\u7891 n lu\'f4n \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o b\'ean trong xem Huy\u7873 n ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o. Kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  Huy\u7873 n nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch ngon l\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ch\'fang t\'f4i b\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i nhau. M\'f9i da th\u7883 t c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m cho con c\u7863 c b\'ean trong qu\u7847 n c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Do v\uc0\u7851 n m\u7863 c c\'e1i qu\u7847 n jean \u273 \u7875  ng\u7911  n\'ean con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'e0m t\'f4i kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u l\u7855 m. Qu\u7847 n nhau m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Huy\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i xoa xoa ng\u7921 c t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3ng b\u7915 ng l\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7847 n em kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i ch\u7913  l\'e0m sao n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u g\'ec ? H\'f4n th\u7871  \u273 \u7911  r\u7891 i nh\'e9, gi\u7901  th\'ec \u273 i ng\u7911  bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u432 ng tay t\'f4i t\u7921  nhi\'ean v\'f2ng qua c\'e1i h\'f4ng m\'e0 \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i b\u7909 ng thon nh\u7887  c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n. N\u7871 u so s\'e1nh v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Huy\u7873 n m\u361 m m\u297 m h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y t\'f4i cho\'e0ng tay qua \u273 \u7875  \'f4m th\u7871  th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  nguy\'ean nh\u432  v\u7853 y. \'d4m m\u7897 t l\'fac thi t\'f4i lu\u7891 n nh\u7865  l\'ean ph\'eda tr\'ean. M\u7899 i qua c\'e1i bung th\'f4i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 ch\u7863 n tay t\'f4i l\u7841 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i tay, \uc0\u273 \u7883 nh l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7883 nh s\u7901 .. h\'ec h\'ec.. th\'f4i n\'e0o cho anh s\u7901  c\'e1i kh\'e1m ph\'e1 xem to kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7865  em b\u7843 o c\u7845 m cho \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng s\u7901 .. s\u7901  l\'e0 h\u7887 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7887 ng g\'ec m\'e0 h\u7887 ng, m\'e0 \u7903  \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 m\u7865  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 s\u7907  c\u417  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang \u273 \u7845 u kh\u7849 u nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i b\u7845 t th\'ecnh l\'ecnh lu\u7891 n tay l\'ean m\'e0 ch\u7897 p lu\'f4n c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n xoa xoa, H\u417 n v\u7897 i g\u7841 t tay t\'f4i ra r\u7891 i \u273 \'e1 m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 b\u7843 o kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  c\u7889  t\'ecnh \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u7901  c\'f3 sao \u273 \'e2u, m\'e0 anh th\u7845 y c\'f3 v\u7867  to\'e0n \'93l\'e1\'94 th\'f4i ch\u7913  ch\u7859 ng th\u7845 y \'93x\'f4i\'94 \u273 \'e2u c\u7843 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec to\'e0n \'93l\'e1\'94 \u273 \u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, ph\u7843 i v\u7841 ch ra xem th\u7921 c h\u432  n\'f3 th\u7871  n\'e0o ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i xong th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 v\u7897 i \u273 \u432 a tay m\'ecnh l\'ean che hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng Huy\u7873 n v\u7915 a \u273 \u432 a l\'ean th\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng lu\u7891 n tay \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o m\'e0 \'f4m tr\u7885 n l\u7845 y c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i \'e1o l\'f3t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u273 \u7841 p m\u7841 nh t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7887  ra kh\'f4ng th\'ec b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0! Cho anh s\uc0\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i \'f4m tr\uc0\u7885 n Huy\u7873 n v\'e0o v\'f2ng tay m\'ecnh. Huy\u7873 n c\u7855 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o tay t\'f4i t\u432 \u7903 ng t\'f4i b\u7887  ra nh\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n s\u7901  v\'e0 b\'f3p nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\u7855 n n\u7919 a d\u7847 n d\u7847 n d\u7909 i m\'e1 v\'e0o c\'e1nh tay t\'f4i.\
