\cf2 \cb3 H\'f4n nh\uc0\u7865  l\'ean t\'f3c t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y! Anh s\u7901  nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i ch\u7913  c\'f3 m\u7841 nh \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 c\u7855 n anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0m sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c! Anh c\u7913  h\'f9ng h\u7893  nh\u432  th\u7871 ? M\'e0 ch\u7855 c l\'e0 anh s\u7901  nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? \'c0 m\'e0 ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'ec Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c c\u7911 a em kh\'f4ng to b\u7857 ng c\u7911 a ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean anh m\u7899 i b\u7843 o to\'e0n \'93l\'e1\'94 ch\u7913  g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7881 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i, nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u h\'f4n \u273 \'e1nh c\'e1i ch\u7909 t v\'e0o m\'e1 r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 v\'e0o trong ch\u7913 ng ki\u7871 n hi\u7879 n v\u7853 t \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0 anh n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'f4i nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  ngo\'e0i l\u7899 p \'93l\'e1\'94 m\'e0 c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec ch\u7855 c l\'e0 c\u361 ng b\u7857 ng \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec th\'f4i. T\'f4i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c m\'e2m m\'ea c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  c\'fai xu\u7889 ng h\'f4n l\'ean tai r\u7891 i c\'e1i c\u7893  thon d\'e0i tr\u7855 ng h\u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 So v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Huy\u7873 n tr\u7855 ng h\u417 n nh\u432 ng nh\u7887  ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n. M\'e2n m\'ea c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa \u7903  b\'ean ngo\'e0i m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec t\'f4i lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o ph\'eda trong b\'f3p trong c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n m\'e0 c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n to th\u7853 t, v\u7915 a xoa xoa \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai ba c\'e1i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y ! Th\uc0\u7871  to ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i tr\'eau hoa:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  to th\u7853 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec b\'e9 sao m\'e0 v\'fa to th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 th\'edch \uc0\u273 \'e1nh n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Huy\u7873 n lu\u7891 n tay ra ph\'eda sau bung c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t m\'ecnh ra cho t\'f4i s\u7901  d\u7877  h\u417 n, c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n to h\u417 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u7913  \u273 \u7875  cho t\'f4i xoa xoa b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i th\u7911  th\u7881  m\'e0 t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh v\uc0\u7899 i ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh h\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7855 c l\'e0 d\'ednh v\u7899 i nhau su\u7889 t nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng d\'ednh \u273 \'e2u, h\u7891 i cu\u7889 i c\'e2p ba v\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u n\u259 m nh\u7845 t th\'ec c\'f2n d\'ednh v\u7899 i nhau ch\u7913  sau n\'e0y th\'ec c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng xa\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng l\'e0m cho ch\u7883  \u7845 y th\'e8m ch\u7913  g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Anh gi\u7889 ng lo\u7841 i y\u7871 u sinh l\'fd l\u7855 m \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y? C\'e1i \u273 \'f3 l\'e2m tr\u7853 n m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  h\'ec h\'ec. Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 anh kh\'f4ng quan t\'e2m ch\u7883  \u7845 y th\'ec ch\u7883  \u7845 y m\u7899 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900 ! C\'f3 l\u7869  th\u7871  nh\u432 ng c\u7889  g\u7855 ng lo bao th\u7913  c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n kh\'f4ng h\u7887 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7845 y n\u7919 a m\'e0 t\'f2 m\'f2 chuy\u7879 n Qu\u7923 nh v\u7899 i th\u7857 ng kia. Huy\u7873 n v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  cho t\'f4i xoa xoa c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa Huy\u7873 n h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\u7855 t g\u7863 p qu\u7843  ch\u7883  \u7845 y v\u7899 i anh kia anh th\u7845 y th\u7871  n\'e0o, ch\u7855 c l\'fac \u273 \'f3 ghen l\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 . Mai kia ch\u7891 ng em m\'e0 th\u7871  kh\'e9o nh\u7843 y v\'e0o c\u7847 m k\'e9o c\u7855 t c\u7909 t lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\'ecnh t\uc0\u297 nh tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec l\'fac \uc0\u273 \'f3 c\u361 ng bu\u7891 n, c\u361 ng ghen l\u7855 m. N\'f3i chung l\'e0 th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i n\'f3i c\uc0\u7909 t l\u7911 n th\u7871  th\'ec Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i h\u7887 i d\u7891 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 ch\uc0\u7883 a \u7845 y c\'f3 k\u7875  l\'e0m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng h\u7845 t h\'e0m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec k\uc0\u7875  nh\u432  th\u7871  ch\u7913  c\'f2n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o n\u7919 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Mi\'eau t\uc0\u7843  chi ti\u7871 t \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Ph\u7909  n\u7919  ai d\'e1m k\u7875  chi ti\u7871 t, m\'e0 chi ti\u7871 t th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7871  ch\u7913  c\u361 ng c\'f3 th\'eam th\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i chung th\'ec v\u7851 n mu\u7889 n nghe chi ti\u7871 t t\u7915  l\'fac t\'e1n r\u7891 i b\u7883  d\u7909  d\u7895  ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7887 i nhi\u7873 u l\u7841 i t\u7913 c \u273 i\'ean l\'ean \'e0, l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0m th\'ec c\u361 ng nh\u432  phim sex th\'f4i. Em xem phim sex th\'ec c\'f2n l\u7841  g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 em ch\u432 a xem!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n tr\u7843  l\u7901 i t\'f4i v\u7853 y khi\u7871 n t\'f4i h\u417 i ng\u7841 c nhi\'ean nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7915 a anh \'e0! T\u7847 m tu\u7893 i em m\'e0 kh\'f4ng xem m\u7899 i l\u7841  \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 em n\'f3i d\uc0\u7889 i anh l\'e0m g\'ec ch\u432 a xem th\u7853 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\'f4m n\'e0o anh cho xem!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kinh l\uc0\u7855 m, em nghe b\u7841 n em k\u7875  kinh l\u7855 m\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 kinh?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec n\'f3 k\uc0\u7867  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 o\u7841 n m\'e0 m\'fat nhau \u7845 y.. kinh kinh\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7881 m h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'fat g\'ec m\'e0 kinh?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i c\'f2n h\u7887 i n\u7919 a, m\'fat c\'e1i \u7845 y \u7845 y \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a xem m\'e0 bi\u7871 t m\'fat n\'f3 kinh l\'e0 sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec con b\uc0\u7841 n em k\u7875  ch\u7913  c\'f2n sao n\u7919 a, n\'f3 xem r\u7891 i th\'ec n\'f3 mi\'eau t\u7843  l\u7841 i th\'f4i, nh\'ecn xu\u7889 ng th\u7845 y c\u7843 m gi\'e1c t\u7921  nhi\'ean kinh kinh, m\'e0 anh v\u7899 i ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7855 c l\'e0 m\'fat nhau ph\u7843 i bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 . Eo ngh\u297  m\'e0 kinh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kinh g\'ec m\'e0 kinh, anh b\uc0\u7843 o r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng kinh m\'e0, m\'fat ngon l\'e0 \u273 \u7857 ng kh\'e1c, kh\'f4ng tin c\u7913  v\u7841 ch ra xem, anh m\'fat nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh lu\'f4n l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y kh\'e9o m\'e0 th\'edch qu\'e1 \u7845 y ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i quay ra. \u272 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7875  t\'f4i xoa c\'e1i v\'fa m\u7841 nh h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u432 a nh\u7865  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ngon tay g\u7849 y g\u7849 y l\'ean c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa xem Huy\u7873 n c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a g\u7849 y \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n g\u7841 t tay r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng l\'e0m th\uc0\u7871  n\u7919 a, em bu\u7891 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng m\'e0 c\'f2n bu\u7891 n, th\'f4i kh\'f4ng s\u7901  b\'ean tr\'ean n\u7919 a s\u7901  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho! Cho tay xu\uc0\u7889 ng l\'e0 \u259 n \u273 \u7841 p \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7887 i th\'ec d\u7841 p xem n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i lu\uc0\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng lu\'f4n nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  m\u7899 i qua c\'e1i c\u7841 p qu\u7847 n th\'f4i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 kh\'e9p ch\'e2n l\u7841 i, hu\'fdch c\'f9i ch\u7887  ra sau r\u7891 i cong ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tay t\'f4i kh\'f4ng lu\uc0\u7891 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i n\u7919 a, tuy nhi\'ean th\'ec v\u7851 n \u273 \u7911  mon men s\u7901  so\u7841 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n cong veo ph\'eda tr\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9 \uc0\u7903  ngo\'e0i c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t th\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n m\u361 m m\u297 m v\'f4 c\'f9ng, Huy\u7873 n nh\u7887  ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao c\'e1i g\'ec c\u361 ng m\'fap h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghi\'eang c\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Huy\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i l\u432 \u7901 m m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh cho tay xu\uc0\u7889 ng n\u7919 a em la l\'ean \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 La \uc0\u273 i xem tr\u7901 i m\u432 a c\'f3 ai kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Anh b\u7855 t n\u7841 t em!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i \'f4m s\'e1t Huy\u7873 n v\'e0o, h\'f4n c\'e1i ch\u7909 t l\'ean m\'e1 r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e2u! Anh b\u7855 t n\u7841 t \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 b\u7855 t n\u7841 t, c\u432 ng em qu\'e1 th\'f4i, anh s\u7901  m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i h\'f4n l\'ean m\'e1 l\'ean tai r\u7891 i b\u7887  tay ra quay Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i. Huy\u7873 n th\'edch l\u7855 m r\u7891 i n\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7873 m nh\u361 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\u259 ng c\u7913 ng nh\u432  l\'fac t\'f4i th\'f2 tay xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n n\'e0y m\u7863 t \u273 \u7889 i m\u7863 t l\'ean b\'e0n tay ph\'eda sau t\'f4i t\u7915  t\u7889 n xoa xoa nh\u7865  l\u432 ng r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m l\u7847 m lu\u7891 n l\'e1ch qua qua c\'e1i c\u7841 p qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i m\'f4ng tr\'f2n l\u7859 n r\u7891 i xoa ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xoa m\'f4ng th\'ec Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  y\'ean cho t\'f4i l\'e0m nh\u432 ng l\'e1ch nh\u7865  ng\'f3n tya xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i khe th\'ec Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i kh\'e9p ch\'e2n l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\'e0ng kh\'e9p ch\'e2n th\'ec t\'f4i c\'e0ng n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7841 nh h\u417 n. C\'f3 l\u7869  Huy\u7873 n s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m n\'ean g\'e1c ch\'e2n lu\'f4n l\'ean \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i xoa xoa xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang th\u7853 t l\'e0 gi\u7889 ng h\u7885 c sinh c\u7845 p hai, c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t s\u7907 i l\'f4ng n\'e0o c\u7843 . D\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tr\u7887  t\'f4i g\'e3i g\'e3i m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'ec \'f4i th\'f4i n\u432 \u7899 c ra nhi\u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng, c\u7843 m t\u432 \u7903 ng nh\u432  Huy\u7873 n \u273 ang \u273 \'e1i ra v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7843  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n t\'f4i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e1i d\u7847 m \'e0? \u431 \u7899 t h\u7871 t c\u7843  qu\u7847 n r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! C\'f3 m\'e0 anh \u273 \'e1i d\u7847 m th\'ec c\'f3 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \'e1i m\'e0 \u432 \u7899 t h\u7871 t th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y th\'ec Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t n\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t t\u7921  d\u432 ng n\'f3 th\u7871  \u273 \u7845 y ch\u7913 , m\'e0 t\u7841 i anh em m\u7899 i th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  t\u7841 i anh h\'ec h\'ec! Th\u7871  cho anh ng\u7855 m n\'f3 c\'e1i nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7845 y x\u7845 u m\'f9, c\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 ng\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u7855 m th\'ec m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t l\'e0 x\u7845 u m\'f9 hay x\u7845 u nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 X\uc0\u7845 u l\'e0 x\u7845 u m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 X\uc0\u7845 u th\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i ng\uc0\u7891 i d\u7853 y k\'e9o lu\'f4n c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n xu\u7889 ng, Huy\u7873 n gi\u7919  gi\u7919  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i c\u361 ng \u273 \'e0nh \u273 \u7875  cho t\'f4i k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i. C\'e1i qu\u7847 n v\u7915 a qua kh\u7887 i b\u7865 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 a tay \'fap xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 che c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i.\
