\cf2 \cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7863 c k\u7879 , l\u7897 t xong c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n ra r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Che th\uc0\u7871  kia th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 anh nh\'ecn \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em x\uc0\u7845 u h\u7893 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m c\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 x\u7845 u h\u7893  c\u417  ch\u7913  n\'e0o cho anh nh\'ecn c\'e1i n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i nh\uc0\u7865  nh\'e0ng g\u7905  b\'e0n tay c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n ra kh\u7887 i c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n. C\'e1i mu l\u7891 n m\'fap m\'e1p d\u7847 n d\u7847 n hi\u7879 n ra tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Mu c\uc0\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n cao v\'f4 c\'f9ng, so v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec nh\'f4 h\u417 n h\u7859 n, \u273 \u7863 c bi\u7879 t l\'e0 mu l\u7891 n ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\'e0i s\u7907 i l\'f4ng t\u417  th\'f4i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n v\u7897 i v\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a hai tay che l\u7841 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y! L\u7841 i c\u432 \u7901 i em r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Xua xua tay n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng ch\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i c\u432 \u7901 i ch\'ea em \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u7915 a m\u7855 t h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ph\uc0\u7843 i th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7853 t ch\u7913  \u273 \'f9a l\'e0m g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m b\u7887  tay ra th\'ec t\'f4i ng\u7855 m ngh\'eda \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n h\u7891 ng r\u7921 c, So s\'e1nh v\u7899 i c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec n\'f3 kh\'edt v\'e0 h\u7891 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c l\'fac t\'f4i l\'e0m v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\'ecn th\'ec n\'f3 h\u417 i th\'e2m v\'e0 c\'f3 m\u7897 t \'edt m\'e9p th\u7883 t l\u7891 i ra r\u7891 i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng kh\'edt r\u7883 t nh\u432  c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n. Ng\u7855 m n\'f3 r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a tay vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t m\u7845 y c\'e1i sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i n\u7857 m b\'ean c\u7841 nh m\'e2n m\'ea c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n e th\u7865 n n\u7919 a, k\'e9o c\'e1i ch\u259 n m\u7887 ng che ngang ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c c\u7911 a em x\u7845 u \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 em l\uc0\u7841 i ngh\u297  c\u7911 a em x\u7845 u?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec kh\'f4ng gi\uc0\u7889 ng c\u7911 a m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a b\u7841 n em n\'ean em ngh\u297  th\u7871  th\'f4i. H\u7891 i t\u7853 p qu\'e2n s\u7921  t\u7855 m c\'f9ng b\u7885 n n\'f3 t\u7855 m c\'f9ng, \u273 \u7913 a n\'e0o \u273 \u7913 a \u7845 y to\'e0n l\'f4ng m\'e0 em ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\'e0i s\u7907 i thui \'e0, nh\'ecn bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i \u417 i l\'e0 bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i \u7845 y, t\u7909 i n\'f3 b\u7843 o tr\u7867  con ch\u432 a k\u7883 p l\u7899 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nghe th\uc0\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'f9ng kh\u7909 c. Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i \u273 a t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n anh n\uc0\u7919 a l\u7841 i tr\'eau em h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u7909 m mi\u7879 ng l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'eau g\'ec, anh c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i l\u361  t\u7909 i b\u7841 n em \u7845 y, gi\u7901  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \u7847 y ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7843 i t\u7881 a r\u7891 i t\u7849 y l\'f4ng cho s\u7841 ch \u273 \u7845 y \'e0! Kh\'f4ng nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1, ch\u7881  c\u7847 n \'edt \'edt th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 qu\'e1 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n th\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'f4ng em th\u7845 y l\'e0m sao \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'f4ng th\'ec li\uc0\u7871 m th\'edch ch\u7913  c\'f3 l\'e0m sao n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Eo kinh! Li\uc0\u7871 m g\'ec m\'e0 li\u7871 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m trong phim ng\u432 \u7901 i ta li\u7871 m \u273 \u7847 y c\'f2n g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y l\'e0 \u273 \'f3ng ch\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i th\u7853 t \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'f3ng th\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i li\u7871 m ch\u7913 , m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 xem phim \u273 \'e2u tinh vi!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n th\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec ng\u7853 m mi\u7879 ng lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng n\'f3i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e2u n\'e0o. \u272 \'fang l\'e0 Huy\u7873 n ng\'e2y th\u417  n\'ean d\u7877  d\u7909  v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a \'f4m v\u7915 a th\u7911  th\u7881  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n t\'f4i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7891 i h\u7885 c qu\'e2n s\u7921  t\u7855 m c\'f9ng c\'f3 th\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a n\'e0o to b\u7857 ng em kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i g\'ec to b\uc0\u7857 ng em kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u7921 c ch\u7913  c\'f2n c\'e1i g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\uc0\u361 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 a to \u273 \u7913 a nh\u7887  th\'f4i, c\'f3 \u273 \u7913 a nh\'ecn nh\u432  hai l\u432 ng \u7845 y, c\'f2n c\'f3 \u273 \u7913 a th\'ec to h\u417 n c\u7911 a em nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u7879  s\u7879  h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c m\'e2n m\'ea c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t. L\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u7901  c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n n\'ean c\'f3 l\u7869  Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, m\'e2n m\'ea c\'e0ng l\'e2u th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\'e0ng ra nhi\u7873 u. M\'fat c\'e1i d\'e1i tai \u273 \'e1nh c\'e1i t\u7897 p m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh h\'f4n c\'e1i \uc0\u7845 y c\u7911 a em nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n kinh b\u7887  x\u7915  h\'f4n g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 hay! B\uc0\u7849 n anh ch\u7883 u c\u417  m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em th\uc0\u7845 y k\'ec k\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\'ec c\'e1i g\'ec, d\uc0\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i ch\uc0\u7891 m d\u7853 y lu\'f4n, v\'e9n c\'e1i \'e1o \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa ra r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ng\u7853 m v\'e0o m\'e0 m\'fat. N\'fam v\'fa c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n to h\u417 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh m\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u432 ng c\'e1i qu\u7847 ng v\'fa th\'ec b\'e9 h\u417 n. M\u7899 i ng\u7853 m v\'e0o m\'fat th\'f4i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  c\'e1i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'ea m\'ea \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7901 i s\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i n\'ean Huy\u7873 n run run l\u7855 m. T\'f4i r\'ea \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m d\u7885 c t\u7915  c\'e1i v\'fa xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i b\u7909 ng r\u7891 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9i n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ngai ng\'e1i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i v\u7883  khai khai \u273 \u432 a l\'ean m\u361 i, C\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u m\u361 i v\u7915 a ch\u7841 m v\'e0o mu l\u7891 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n v\'f4i che l\u7841 i, n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i kh\'f4ng li\uc0\u7871 m n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0! Cho anh li\uc0\u7871 m c\'e1i \u273 i.. c\'f3 sao \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng b\uc0\u7849 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m d\u7885 c lu\'f4n c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n. M\u7899 i li\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai c\'e1i th\'f4i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n cong m\'ecnh l\'ean r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 o\'e1n Huy\u7873 n th\'edch l\u7855 m n\'ean \u273 \u432 a hai tay \u273 \u7905  c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i tr\u7855 ng h\u7891 ng banh r\u7897 ng ra r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  m\'e0 th\u7893 i v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7915 ng th\u7893 i v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 em bu\u7891 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! \u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i anh kh\'f4ng th\u7893 i n\u7919 a, banh r\u7897 ng ch\'e2n ra anh li\u7871 m cho n\'e0o. Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Anh th\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a.. ch\u7881  th\u7845 y t\'ea t\'ea c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f2n ch\'ea anh b\u7849 n n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n b\u7887  x\u7915  l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, th\'f4i nh\'e9, kh\'f4ng li\u7871 m l\'e1p nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec c\u7913  li\u7871 m th\'f4i, t\u7897 i g\'ec m\'e0 kh\'f4ng li\u7871 m c\u417  ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t gh\'e9t th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\'f3i v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng t\'f4i m\u7863 c k\u7879 , c\'fai xu\u7889 ng nh\'e2m nhi li\u7871 m l\'e1p c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u259 ng m\u7885 ng. L\'e2u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ham mu\u7889 n n\u7919 a. Li\u7871 m l\u7891 n Huy\u7873 n t\'f4i l\u7841 i ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n c\u7843 nh Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng \u273 \'e3 t\u7915 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u417 n h\u7913 ng t\'ecnh n\u7893 i l\'ean, t\'f4i qu\'e9t m\u7841 nh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o \u273 \u361 ng c\'e1i l\u7895  r\u7891 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng banh ra ng\u7849 y nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'ean h\u7897 t le.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'f4i m\'e0 Huy\u7873 n run b\u7855 n l\'ean r\u7891 i v\'f4i che tay c\u7911 a m\'ecnh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0.. anh..em bu\uc0\u7891 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bu\uc0\u7891 n g\'ec m\'e0 bu\u7891 n.. li\u7871 m c\'e0ng s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913  bu\u7891 n c\'e1i g\'ec.. \u273 \u7875  anh li\u7871 m cho n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng banh ch\'e2n ra t\'f4i n\'fat th\'eam v\'e0i c\'e1i tr\'ean mu l\u7891 n r\u7891 i li\u7871 m v\'f2ng quanh l\'ean b\u7865 n r\u7891 i c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i thon nh\u7887  c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e2n Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\u7887  h\u417 n ch\'e2n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n vu\u7889 t th\'f4i th\'ec c\u361 ng th\'edch th\'fa l\u7855 m r\u7891 i. Li\u7871 m l\'e1p m\'e3i Huy\u7873 n k\'e9o t\'f4i l\'ean \'f4m m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913  nh\u432  \u259 n th\u7883 t em \u7845 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ngon l\'e0nh qu\'e1 ch\uc0\u7913  sao, ki\u7875 u nh\u432  tr\u7867  con m\u7899 i l\u7899 n \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\uc0\u7867  con m\u7899 i l\u7899 n m\'e0 l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 \u273 i t\'f9 \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 i t\'f9 th\'ec c\u361 ng l\'e0m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai l\u7841 i qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i, t\'f4i day day c\'e1i h\u7897 t le r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh li\uc0\u7871 m cho em r\u7891 i th\'ec b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 t em m\'fat cho anh nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u7901 ! Em c\'f3 b\u7843 o anh m\'fat cho em \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0 anh t\u7921  nguy\u7879 n \u273 \u7845 y ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ..l\'e0m cho s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m l\u7841 i cho c\'f4ng b\u7857 ng ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 h\'f4, ph\uc0\u7909  n\u7919  lu\'f4n \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n v\u7915 a n\'f3i th\u7871  t\'f4i b\u297 u m\'f4i b\u7843 o l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 l\'e0 ph\u7909  n\u7919  ch\u432 a m\'e0 tinh t\u432 \u7899 ng c\u417  ch\u7913 \cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec con g\'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c day c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n, t\'f4i bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i l\'e0 mi\u7879 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd nh\u432 ng ki\u7875 u g\'ec r\u7891 i c\u361 ng c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 m\'fat cho t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Day th\'eam m\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a th\'ec c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng. So v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 v\uc0\u7867  kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Huy\u7873 n m\u7899 i kh\u7869  kh\'e0ng lu\u7891 n nh\u7865  tay xu\u7889 ng v\'e0o trong qu\u7847 n r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i. L\u7845 y tay l\u7855 c l\u7855 c n\'f3 r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3 v\uc0\u7915 a to v\u7915 a d\'e0i th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o trong nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'fat th\u7915 a \u7845 y ch\u7913  h\'ec h\'ec, \u273 \u7867  c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hu\u7889 ng chi b\'e9 t\'ed th\u7871  n\'e0y, th\'f4i m\'fat cho anh \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng r\u7891 i nghi\'eang \u273 \u7847 u, g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u tr\'ean b\u7909 ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ra m\'e0 m\'fat nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'f4i m\'f4i xinh x\u7855 n ng\u7853 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c r\u7891 i th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f3 s\u7907  b\u7849 n kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7849 n kinh!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i l\'e0 b\uc0\u7849 n th\'f4i nh\u432 ng Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u m\'fang m\u7841 nh d\u7841 n h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat. M\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7881  l\'e0 c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n Huy\u7873 n c\u361 ng nu\u7889 t tr\u7885 n con c\u7863 c v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng m\'ecnh m\'e0 m\'e2n m\'ea. Do ch\u432 a m\'fat l\u7847 n n\'e0o n\'ean hai h\'e0m r\u259 ng c\u7885  v\'e0o th\'e2n c\u7863 c l\'e0m t\'f4i \u273 au \u273 i\u7871 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khom ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i ch\u7881  d\u7841 y Huy\u7873 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n th\'ec Hao ti\u7871 p thu nhanh l\u7855 m, ch\u7859 ng m\u7845 y ch\u7889 c l\'e0m cho con c\u7863 c t\'f4i b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n li\u7871 m ti\u7871 p hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i l\'ean b\u7909 ng n\u7919 a. C\'f3 l\u7869  Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 cu\u7889 n v\'e0o c\'e1i \u273 am m\'ea x\'e1c th\u7883 t n\'ean t\'f4i ch\u7881  th\u7871  n\'e0o th\'ec Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, t\'f4i \u273 \'e8 Huy\u7873 n xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho anh \uc0\u273 \'fat v\'e0o nh\'e9?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'ean n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u273 \'fat nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i kh\'f4ng em \u273 au.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Nh\u7865 , m\'e0 em nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\u7855 c l\'e0 \u273 \'fat m\u7897 t ph\'e1t th\'ec ng\u7853 p lu\'f4n h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i em d\'e2m l\u7855 m \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nheo m\u7855 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'ec t\'f4i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  r\u7891 i ch\'e0 n\'f3 d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n. Ch\u7881  nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m cho n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n trong c\'e1i l\u7895  t\u7913 a ra th\u7853 t l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u. Huy\u7873 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng banh r\u7897 ng c\'e1i l\u7891 n m\'ecnh ra ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'f3 l\uc0\u7869  Huy\u7873 n v\u7851 n s\u7907  \u273 au n\'ean v\u7851 n run run ch\u7913  ch\u432 a tho\u7843 i m\'e1i \u273 \u7875  t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng c\'e1i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'ea m\'ea kho\'e1i l\u7841 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e0i tr\uc0\u7901 i m\u432 a m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t to h\u417 n, t\'f4i k\u7879  tr\u7901 i m\u432 a, k\'ea c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c t\'f9 t\'f9 \u273 \'fang c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m \u7845 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 Do n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n qu\'e1 nhi\'eau n\'ean d\u7877  d\'e0ng \'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i chui \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895 . Ch\u432 a v\u7897 i \u7845 n s\'e2u v\'e0o t\'f4i kh\u7869  h\u7887 i Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 \uc0\u273 au kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng anh \uc0\u7841 .. cho v\'e0o n\u7919 a \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? C\u7845 m k\'eau \u273 au \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng v\u7841 ch kh\u7869  hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra. T\'f4i cong c\'e1i h\'f4ng \u7845 n m\u7841 nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\'ec con c\u7863 c ng\u7853 p l\'fat v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7891 n.\
