\cf2 \cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u7913  l\'ean m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\'ec t\'f4i n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng \'f4m l\u7845 y r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 au \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i th\u7889 n\'85 h\u417 i nh\'f3i m\u7897 t c\'e1i..anh l\'e0m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i ch\u7913 .. \u7845 n m\u7841 nh \u273 \'e1nh c\'e1i th\u7909 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i v\'e0o th\u7871  th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec n\'f3 c\u361 ng n\u7857 m \u7903  trong r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y! L\u7891 n c\u7911 a em \u7845 m th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
