\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 \'85 nh\u432 ng m\'e0 nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7845 p nh\u7893 m tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i cho con c\u7863 c th\'f2 th\u7909 t b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n. Do n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ra th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u th\'eam v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n mu\u7889 n \'e2n \'e1i v\u7899 i t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'ean m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n nh\u7845 p nh\u7865  sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7841 nh l\'ean th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u r\'edt kh\u7869  m\'e0 r\'ean to.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7889 ng m\u7897 t tay xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng m\u7897 t tay t\'f4i xoa c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n \uc0\u273 au n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u v\u7883 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o h\'f4ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em th\'edch c\'e1i c\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c.. v\'e0o s\'e2u.. n\'f3 bu\u7891 n bu\u7891 n t\'ea t\'ea s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? V\u7853 y anh \u7845 n v\'e0o s\'e2u nh\'e9?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec t\'f4i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u7845 n v\'e0o s\'e2u h\u417 n. N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n nh\u7847 y nh\u7851 y tu\'f4n ra th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u t\u7841 o th\'e0nh t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 ng nh\'e9p nh\'e9p vui tai v\'f4 c\'f9ng. C\'e1i gi\u432 \u7901 ng k\u7869 o k\u7865 t h\'f2a c\'f9ng nh\u7883 p nh\u7845 p c\u7911 a t\'f4i. Ch\u7889 ng tay ch\'e1n th\'ec t\'f4i c\'fai nu\u7889 ng n\'fat c\'e1i v\'fa r\u7891 i xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7841 i b\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho em l\'ean tr\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\u7857 m l\'ean tr\'ean r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\'f3 bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \'e2u?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec c\uc0\u7913  nh\'fan nh\u432  c\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a \u7845 y !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u7921 a n\'e0y m\'e0 nh\'fan c\'f3 m\'e0 g\u7851 y lu\'f4n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u n\'f3 m\uc0\u7899 i g\u7851 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i l\u7845 y hai c\'e1i ng\'f3n tay g\u7849 y g\u7849 y l\'ean c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa c\u259 ng tr\'f2n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n. Huy\u7873 n l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7889 ng tay l\'ean ng\u7921 c t\'f4i m\'e0 nh\'fan ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3p m\uc0\u7841 nh c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh l\'ean ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0m m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  anh \u273 \u7905  m\'f4ng cho nh\'fan m\u7841 nh l\'ean n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lu\uc0\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7905  hai c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\'fan m\u7841 nh h\u417 n nh\u432 ng m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 hai ba ph\'fan th\'ec Huy\u7873 n kh\'e9p ch\'e2n m\'ecnh l\u7841 i, \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng che che c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u417 i\'85 em bu\u7891 n \u273 \'e1i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c s\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 \u7845 y m\'e0.. c\u7913  nh\'fan tho\u7843 i m\'e1i xem c\'f3 \u273 \'e1i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  \u273 \'e1i l\'e0 \u432 \u7899 t h\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u431 \u7899 t c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i \u273 \u7905  cho Huy\u7873 n nh\'fan m\u7841 nh h\u417 n, c\'e1i gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'fac n\'e0y rung m\u7841 nh cho Huy\u7873 n d\u7853 p m\u7841 nh m\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7881  v\'e0i ph\'fat sau th\'ec Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a, l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh lu\'f4n, n\u432 \u7899 c phun ra \u432 \u7899 t \u273 \u7851 m c\u7843  \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u7903  g\u7889 c c\u7863 c t\'f4i. Huy\u7873 n c\'fai xu\u7889 ng n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i em \uc0\u273 \'e1i ra r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e2y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u273 \'e1i m\'e0 l\'e0 l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh n\'ean n\u432 \u7899 c ra nhi\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \u7845 y.. xem phim nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i s\u7869  bi\u7871 t ngay m\'e0. \u272 \'fang l\'e0 c\'f2n ph\u7843 i d\u7853 y nhi\u7873 u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913  t\u7841 i anh d\u7909  d\u7895  em m\u7899 i th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \u7845 y ch\u7913 . Ch\u7881  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\u7909  d\u7895  con g\'e1i nh\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i ta kh\'f4ng ai b\u7857 ng th\'f4i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7843  hai c\'f9ng s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913  m\u7895 i m\'ecnh anh \u273 \'e2u h\'ec h\'ec, nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t \u7917 ng h\u7891 ng kia l\'e0 anh bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng th\'ec n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec m\'e0 anh ch\uc0\u432 a ra \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7903  to tr\'f2n m\u7855 t ra Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec n\uc0\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng anh l\'e0m cho m\u7897 t c\'e1i bi\u7871 t ngay!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ng\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ra n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng th\'ec t\'f4i v\'e1c hai ch\'e2n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u7863 t l\'ean c\u7893  r\u7891 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c nh\u7845 p l\'ean h\u7891 . Hao g\'e0o l\'ean ch\u7855 c v\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 khi\u7871 n t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh xu\uc0\u7845 t v\'e0o trong nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng em s\u7907  c\'f3 b\u7847 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng sao \uc0\u273 \'e2u u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\'e0, b\u7855 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong m\u7899 i c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
