\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n thay th\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c Qu\u7923 nh trong tr\'e1i tim t\'f4i. Th\u7845 m tho\'e1t th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng m\u7897 t n\u259 m tr\'f4i qua, t\'ecnh y\'eau c\u7911 a hai ch\'fang t\'f4i c\'e0ng l\'fac c\'e0ng m\u7863 n n\u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'fac n\'e0y th\'ec t\'f4i g\u7863 p l\u7841 i Qu\u7923 nh, ho\u7843 n c\'e0nh c\u361 ng tr\u7899  tr\'eau kh\'f4ng k\'e9m. T\'f4i l\'e0m th\'eam v\'e0 c\'f3 n\u259 ng l\u7921 c n\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m tr\u432 \u7903 ng m\u7897 t chi nh\'e1nh b\'e1n h\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m \uc0\u273 \'f3 \u273 ang ng\u7891 i ti\u7871 p kh\'e1ch qu\'e1n caf\'e9 th\'ec th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i v\'e0o, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u7853 n ra ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  c\u7911 a t\'f4i h\'f4m n\'e0o n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\'e2y gi\u7901  tr\'f4ng gi\'e0 d\u7863 n h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u. Trang \u273 i\u7875 m c\u361 ng \u273 \u7853 m h\u417 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n ng\'e2y th\u417  nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c. Tay c\u7847 m tut thu\u7889 c l\'e1 r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7845 y b\'e0n m\u7901 i kh\'e1ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'f4 t\'ecnh Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\u7853 n ra t\'f4i n\'ean v\u7897 i quay b\u432 \u7899 c \u273 i th\'ec t\'f4i xin ph\'e9p kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i quay ra b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7851 n c\'f2n tr\'e1nh m\u7863 t anh h\u7843 ? Cho anh s\u7889  t\'ed ch\'fang ta n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i anh \uc0\u7841 , em \u273 ang trong ca l\'e0m vi\u7879 c m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Trong ca l\'e0m vi\uc0\u7879 c th\'ec cho anh s\u7889  c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  sao, coi anh l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng c\u7911 a em \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i kh\u7869  \u273 \u7885 c s\u7889  cho t\'f4i. L\u432 u l\u7841 i s\u7889  t\'f4i quay ra ti\u7871 p kh\'e1ch \u273 \u7871 n tr\u432 a th\'ec c\u7847 m m\'e1y g\u7885 i cho Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  m\u7897 t ch\'fat r\u7891 i ra g\u7863 p t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7885 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i th\u259 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao d\uc0\u7841 o n\'e0y tr\'f4ng gi\'e0 \u273 i th\u7871 ? Ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau kh\'f4ng ch\u259 m lo cho \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'f3i b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng h\u417 i kh\'edch kh\'edch c\u7911 a t\'f4i khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng t\u432 ng t\u7913 c. Bi\u7871 t v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng ngh\u297  m\'ecnh c\'f3 l\u7895 i n\'ean Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7881  kh\u7869  m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\'f3 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 ch\u259 m c\u417  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Xinh nh\u432  em th\'ec sau anh thi\u7871 u g\'ec g\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau, m\'e0 sao l\u7841 i \u273 i l\'e0m ti\u7871 p th\u7883  thu\u7889 c l\'e1 th\u7871  n\'e0y? Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 i h\u7885 c n\u7919 a \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 \uc0\u273 i h\u7885 c ch\u7913  anh? Nh\u432 ng thi l\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u m\'f4n qu\'e1 n\'ean r\u7843 nh \u273 i ti\u7871 p th\u7883  thu\u7889 c l\'e1 ki\u7871 m ti\u7873 n \u273 \u7875  h\u7885 c l\u7841 i h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai t\'e2m s\u7921  chuy\u7879 n c\u361  r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u7889  \'fd cho Qu\u7923 nh nh\'ecn th\u7845 y \u7843 nh Huy\u7873 n xinh x\u7855 n t\'f4i \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m m\'e0n h\'ecnh ch\u7901  c\u7911 a \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\'e9n c\'e1i m\'e1i t\'f3c r\u7845 t \u273 \'fang ki\u7875 u c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i h\u7845 t h\'e0m h\u7887 i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kia l\'e0 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau anh \u273 \u7845 y \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! H\'ec h\'ec! K\'e9m em ba tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7843 o n\'e0o, tr\'f4ng tr\u7867  v\u7899 i xinh th\u7871 ? V\u7853 y khi n\'e0o c\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t, v\'ec c\'f4 \u7845 y c\'f2n \u273 i h\u7885 c. C\'e2u h\u7887 i khi n\'e0o c\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1ng nh\u7869  anh h\u7887 i em m\u7899 i \u273 \'fang ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'fai xu\u7889 ng c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai c\uc0\u432 \u7899 i m\'e0 c\u432 \u7899 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  \u273 \'e2u, c\'e1i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 h\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c y\'eau em \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\'fang em chia tay l\'e2u l\uc0\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh k\u7875  s\u417  qua cho t\'f4i c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n. R\u7891 i t\'f4i m\u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i \u259 n, ti\u7879 n th\u7875  mua cho Qu\u7923 nh c\u7843  m\u7897 t t\'fat thu\u7889 c \u7911 ng h\u7897  Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7913  t\'f4i kh\'f4ng h\'fat thu\u7889 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i g\u7863 p Huy\u7873 n c\u7843  hai \u273 i ch\u417 i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 m\'e0 \'e2n \'e1i, h\'ecnh \u7843 nh c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'f4i l\'fac l\u7841 i hi\u7879 n ra b\u7903 i t\'ecnh \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec kh\'f3 qu\'ean l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0m th\uc0\u7883  tr\u432 \u7901 ng n\'ean m\u7845 y h\'f4m sau t\'f4i l\u7841 i \u273 i g\u7863 p kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng, ch\u7855 c c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7889  t\'f4i h\'ean n\'ean kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng h\'fat thu\u7889 c m\'e0 lo\u7841 i \u273 \'fang thu\u7889 c c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ti\u7871 p th\u7883  n\'ean t\'f4i mang c\u7843  t\'fat thu\u7889 c ra bi\u7871 u kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn t\'fat thu\uc0\u7889 c t\'f4i l\u7841 i nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean t\'f4i nh\u7855 n tin:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay c\'f3 ph\uc0\u7843 i \u273 i l\'e0m kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7853 n ra s\u7889  t\'f4i Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7855 c l\'e0 l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'fac r\u7891 i m\u7899 i nh\u7845 c m\'e1y g\u7885 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \'e0? Em r\uc0\u7843 nh.. c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n g\'ec th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh mu\uc0\u7889 n m\u7901 i em caf\'e9 th\'f4i c\'f3 \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u7841  c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7841 ! T\u7847 m hai gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u anh nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai gi\uc0\u7901  chi\u7873 u t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n qu\'e1n caf\'e9 ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7907 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n. Qu\u7923 nh \u259 n m\u7863 c gi\u7889 ng ki\u7875 u h\u7891 i x\u432 a hai \u273 \u7913 a v\u7851 n c\'f2n y\'eau nhau th\u7855 m thi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay sao \uc0\u259 n m\u7863 c gi\u7889 ng ng\'e0y x\u432 a th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'eau t\'f4i Qu\u7923 nh tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em mu\uc0\u7889 n \u259 n m\u7863 c gi\u7889 ng ng\'e0y x\u432 a xem anh c\'f2n th\'edch em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i tr\'eau l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch th\'ec v\uc0\u7851 n th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i quan tr\u7885 ng y\'eau l\u7841 i m\u7899 i kh\'f3 ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  chuy\u7879 n nh\'e0 c\u7917 a, h\'f3a ra b\u7889  Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 b\u7879 nh n\'ean l\'e0m vi\u7879 c b\u7883  h\u7841 n ch\u7871 , kh\'f4ng c\'f2n sung t\'fac nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn k\uc0\u297  c\'e1i khu\'f4n m\u7863 t h\'f4m nay trang \u273 i\u7875 m nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng t\'f4i th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh gi\'e0 \u273 i tr\'f4ng th\u7845 y. Tuy nhi\'ean th\'ec c\'e1i v\u7867  d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o l\u7851 n \u273 i \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'fac, t\'f4i \u273 \u7873  c\u7853 p \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7845 y, tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  l\'e0m em th\u7887 a m\'e3n l\u7855 m nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m t\'f4i m\'e0 b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7841 i th\'edch tr\'eau em nh\u432  th\u7871  \u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec \uc0\u273 \'fang c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, anh c\'f3 n\'f3i \u273 i\'eau \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'e1c g\'ec anh, ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 c\'f4 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau m\u7899 i n\'e0y c\u361 ng th\u7871  \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Nh\'ecn m\u7863 t xinh th\u7871  kia em \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\u361 ng gi\u7887 i l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec tr\'eau l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 h\u417 n em kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y? \u272 o\'e1n th\u7917  coi?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m y\'eau, \'e1nh m\u7855 t c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh tuy bu\u7891 n nh\u432 ng t\'f4i bi\u7871 t v\u7851 n c\'f2n y\'eau t\'f4i l\u7855 m. Nghe t\'f4i h\u7887 i v\u7853 y th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  th\'ec ch\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec em h\uc0\u7885 c t\u7853 p nhi\u7873 u ch\u7913  sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nheo m\u7855 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i, t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c l\'e0 ki\u7875 u n\'e0y c\u361 ng qua nhi\u7873 u anh l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, \u273 i ti\u7871 p th\u7883  thu\u7889 c l\'e1 th\u7871  n\'e0y l\u7841 i d\u7877  b\u7883  \u273 ong \u273 \u432 a n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  d\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e0 kh\'e0 t\'f4i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  gi\u7901  c\'f3 c\u7847 n anh \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7845 y v\u7853 y tr\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  ra tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7845 y t\u7915  l\'e2u r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i nh\u432  l\'fac x\u432 a n\u7919 a m\'e0 c\u7847 n anh \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o nh\'e9, gi\u7901  l\'e0 ch\u7881  c\'f3 th\u7921 c h\'e0nh v\'e0 n\'e2ng cao tay ngh\u7873  th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? Th\u7871  gi\u7901  anh v\u7899 i em th\u7921 c h\'e0nh c\'e1i nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i th\u7853 t d\'e0i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 th\uc0\u7853 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y? Th\u7921 c h\'e0nh \u273 \u7875  r\u7891 i b\u7841 n g\'e1i anh th\u7883 t em \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 th\uc0\u7883 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y, gi\u7901  c\'f3 bao nhi\'eau qu\u7843  \u273 \'e1nh ghen, lo\u7841 ng qu\u7841 ng \u259 n ngay ca a x\'edt v\'e0o m\u7863 t th\'ec toi \u273 \u7901 i lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau anh l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 d\'e3 man \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871  \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i k\uc0\u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh chuy\u7879 n t\'f4i v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n, d\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng \u273 \'e1 \u273 \u432 a th\'eam v\'e0i c\'e2u chuy\u7879 n sex v\'e0o khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh h\u417 i \u273 \u7887  m\u7863 t nh\u432 ng th\'edch th\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i th\uc0\u7859 ng ra l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh th\'edch c\'e1i ki\u7875 u c\u7911 a t\'f4i n\'ean t\'f4i mu\u7889 n th\u7917  h\u7887 i Qu\u7923 nh m\u7897 t c\'e2u:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  m\'e0 g\u7841  em \u273 i th\u7921 c h\'e0nh c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng nh\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7921 c h\'e0nh ch\'e1n v\u7899 i em h\u417 n m\u7897 t n\u259 m c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a, do sai l\u7847 m c\u7911 a em m\'e0 em kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7921 c h\'e0nh v\u7899 i anh n\u7919 a c\'f2n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y l\'e0 v\u7915 a h\u7885 c v\u7915 a l\'e0m th\'f4i, gi\u7901  m\u7899 i chu\u7849 n m\'e0. H\u417 n n\u7919 a c\u7843 m x\'fac th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'fac sai l\'fac \u273 \'fang \u273 \'e2u em, l\'fac \u273 \'f3 ai m\'e0 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7871 u th\'edch th\'ec em chi\u7873 u lu\'f4n..\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chi\uc0\u7873 u anh m\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau em bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh c\u361 ng toi \'e0, \u273 \u7847 y v\u7909  \u273 \'e1nh ghen \'e1c l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ha ha! Em c\'f3 ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 \u273 \'e1nh ghen, gi\u7901  \u273 \u7897 c th\'e2n vui t\'ednh r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a nh\u259 n nh\u7903  m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a t\'ecnh trong c\u7843  hai con ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 ang ngu\u7897 i l\u7841 nh t\u7915  l\'e2u b\u7895 ng b\'f9ng ch\'e1y r\u7921 c tr\u7903  l\u7841 i.\
