\cf2 \cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai g\u7917 i xe r\u7891 i t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a Qu\u7923 nh v\'e0o nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  ngay c\u7841 nh qu\'e1n caf\'e9. V\'e0o trong thang m\'e1y Qu\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e0o nh\'e0 ngh\uc0\u7881  v\u7899 i em kh\'f4ng s\u7907  em g\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau \u273 \u7871 n \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec s\uc0\u7907  g\'ec? Anh v\u7851 n tin em nh\u432  ng\'e0y x\u432 a th\'ec vi\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 ph\u7843 i s\u7907 !\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\u7911 m t\u7881 m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec ch\'fang ta s\u7889 ng l\u7841 i nh\u7919 ng g\'ec c\u7911 a m\u7845 y n\u259 m v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c anh nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n mu\u7889 n tr\'eau \u273 \'f9a Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Li\uc0\u7879 u c\'f3 gi\u7887 i nh\u432  m\u7845 y n\u259 m v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\u361 ng n\u7883 u c\u7885  nh\u7865  m\'e1 v\'e0o ng\u7921 c t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng k\'e9m \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ngh\uc0\u7881  Qu\u7923 nh bu\u7897 c t\'f3c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean r\u7891 i quay l\u7841 i nheo m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7855 m c\'f9ng em nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7855 m c\'f9ng c\'f3 ph\u7843 i k\'ec l\u432 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913 . Ch\u7855 c d\u7841 o n\'e0y c\u361 ng t\u7855 m c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau m\'e3i r\u7891 i, b\u7883  k\'ec l\u432 ng nhi\u7873 u n\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  s\u7907  k\'ec l\u432 ng \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng s\uc0\u7907  l\u7855 m m\'e0 em c\u361 ng \u273 \u7847 y ng\u432 \u7901 i k\'ec l\u432 ng ch\u7913  \u273 \'e2u m\u7895 i m\'ecnh anh \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 ai, t\uc0\u7855 m c\'f9ng th\'ec t\u7855 m c\'f9ng ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ra k\'e9o c\'e1i r\'e8m c\u7917 a s\u7893  r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m c\u7903 i c\'e1i v\'e1y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n c\'e1i l\u432 ng m\u7873 m m\u7841 i m\u7887 ng manh nh\u432 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  Qu\u7923 nh g\u7847 y h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c. Tr\'ean vai Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n x\u259 m m\u7897 t con b\u432 \u7899 m nh\u7887  v\u7899 i m\u7897 t \u273 \'f3a hoa h\u7891 ng c\'e1ch \u273 i\u7879 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7845 y h\'ecnh x\u259 m th\u7871  t\'f4i kh\u7869  h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u7841 o n\'e0y ch\u417 i b\u7901 i kinh nh\u7881 , tr\u432 \u7899 c em kh\'f4ng th\'edch x\u259 m m\'e0 sao gi\u7901  x\u259 m th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\'e1n \uc0\u273 \u7901 i th\'ec x\u259 m th\'f4i, em c\u361 ng th\u7845 y \u273 \u7865 p m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7847 m ch\u7853 m ti\u7871 n l\u7841 i t\'f4i \u273 \u7863 t tay l\'ean b\u7901  vai r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  k\'e9o quai v\'e1y xu\u7889 ng. C\u7843 m x\'fac ng\'e0y x\u432 a d\u7847 n d\u7847 n hi\u7879 n v\u7873 . C\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t \u273 en tuy\u7873 n hi\u7879 n l\'ean \'f4m l\u7845 y b\u7847 u v\'fa. Ng\u7921 c Qu\u7923 nh tr\u432 \u7899 c kia c\'f2n s\u259 n l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7873 m nh\u361 n r\u7891 i, t\'f4i th\u7847 m ngh\u297  \'93Ki\u7875 u n\'e0y ch\u7855 c l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u \'f4ng b\'f3p l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y\'94.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\'e9o c\'e1i v\'e1y xu\uc0\u7889 ng th\u7855 t l\u432 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh v\'f2ng tay ra \u273 \u7857 ng sau th\'e1o c\'e1i khuy \'e1o l\'f3t cho n\'f3 tu\u7897 t xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1ch h\u7901  h\u7919 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7913 ng \u7903  ph\'eda sau v\'f2ng tay \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i eo nh\u7887  t\'f4i h\'f4n l\'ean c\'e1i c\u7893  m\u7873 m m\u7841 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4m th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y l\u7841 i nh\u7899  ng\'e0y x\u432 a nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ng\u7843  \u273 \u7847 u ra sau n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Em nh\u7899  l\u7855 m..\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i v\u7915 a h\'f4n l\'ean m\'e1i t\'f3c, m\'f9i h\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a, thay v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 m\'f9i \'93son ph\u7845 n b\u7909 i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng\'94.. V\u7915 a h\'f4n v\u7915 a \u273 \u432 a tay g\u7905  c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t r\u7891 i m\'e2n m\'ea l\u7845 y hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 nh\'e3o h\uc0\u7859 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u432  ng\'e0y x\u432 a. V\'ea v\'ea c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i v\'e0o t\uc0\u7855 m \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i c\'f9ng v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m. Qu\u7923 nh nhanh ch\'f3ng c\u7903 i h\u7871 t \u273 \u7891  cho t\'f4i r\u7891 i m\'f3c l\'ean m\'f3c \'e1o m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e0ng ng\'e0y tr\'f4ng n\'f3 c\'e0ng to nh\uc0\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 to. N\'f3 v\uc0\u7851 n th\u7871  ch\u7913  c\'f3 kh\'e1c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em tr\'f4ng n\'f3 to h\uc0\u417 n m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7899 i t\'f4i v\u7915 a t\u7855 m v\u7915 a xoa xoa con c\u7863 c. \u272 \'e1m b\u7885 t tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a l\'e0m \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 enh nh\'e1nh d\'ednh b\u7871 t v\'e0o nhau khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh th\'edch ch\'ed c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7881 a cho n\'f3 ng\u7855 n \u273 i, \u273 \u7875  d\'e0i th\u7871  n\'e0y tr\'f4ng ph\'e1t kinh l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 d\'e0i l\uc0\u7855 m \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7875  anh xem em t\u7881 a th\u7871  n\'e0o nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i th\'f2 tay xu\uc0\u7889 ng m\'e0 xoa xoa c\'e1i mu l\'f4n, kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng c\u7841 o m\'e0 t\u7881 a ng\u7855 n h\u7859 n, ch\u7855 c ch\u7881  d\'e0i ch\u432 a \u273 \u7871 n n\u7917 a ph\'e2n. M\'e2n m\'ea xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n xem th\u7871  n\'e0o th\'ec \'f4i th\'f4i n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n kh\'edt khao nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 \'93c\'e0 v\u7841 t\'94 d\'e0i l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y ng\'f3n tay m\'e2n m\'ea d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y ph\u7843 i t\u7881 a t\'f3t nh\u432  em m\u7899 i th\'edch ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c sao kh\'f4ng t\u7881 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\'e2y th\u417  ch\u432 a bi\u7871 t g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh kh\'fac kh\'edch c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i nhau r\u7891 i x\u7843  s\u7841 ch x\'e0 b\'f4ng tr\u7855 ng ph\u7889 p tr\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i. Qu\u7923 nh ch\u259 m ch\u7881  c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i vu\u7889 t cho nh\'f3 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 l\'e0m cho em \u7845 y t\'ea xu\u7889 ng ng\'e0y \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7889 ng l\'e0m cho em!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng t\u7921  nhi\'ean m\'e0 m\'fat con c\u7863 c m\u7897 t c\'e1ch thu\u7847 n th\u7909 c v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7843 o quanh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c sau \u273 \'f3 d\u7847 n d\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c r\u7891 i l\u7841 i l\'ean ph\'eda tr\'ean. Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m cho c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y l\'ean n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 i \u273 \u7849 y c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c ra ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh h\uc0\u7887 i m\u7897 t c\'e2u nh\u7869  \u273 \u7915 ng gi\u7853 n nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  xem \u273 \'e3 h\'ec h\'ec, m\'e0 th\'f4i anh h\u7887 i \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7915  sau khi ch\'fang ta kh\'f4ng c\'f2n y\'eau nhau n\u7919 a, em \u273 \'e3 th\u7845 y c\'e1i n\'e0o to h\u417 n c\u7911 a anh ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7851 n \'e2u y\u7871 m m\'fat m\'e1t con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Theo anh th\'ec em bi\uc0\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i, anh \u273 o\'e1n l\'e0 bi\u7871 t nhi\u7873 u th\'ec anh m\u7899 i h\u7887 i th\u7871  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\'fat c\'e1i t\u7897 p m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i t\u7911 m t\u7881 m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 to h\uc0\u417 n \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? Th\u7871  c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng? Anh h\u7887 i th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i troll \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7915 ng c\'f3 m\'e0 gi\u7853 n bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i, n\'f3i chung em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng nh\u7899 , m\'e0 to nh\u7845 t kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i Vi\u7879 t, ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n c\'f3 c\uc0\u7843  b\u7891  n\u432 \u7899 c ngo\'e0i n\u7919 a c\u417  \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng, c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e2u. N\'f3i chung l\'e0m m\u7845 y c\'e1i ngh\u7873  ti\u7871 p th\u7883  th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n ph\u7843 i c\'f3 quan h\u7879  n\'e0y kia m\u7899 i b\'e1n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'e0ng ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7841 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng ch\u259 m s\'f3c con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i b\u7857 ng c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7873 m m\u7841 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh. Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n b\u7869 n l\u7869 n ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia n\u7919 a. Qu\u7923 nh li\u7871 m l\'e1p m\'fat m\'e1t m\u7897 t c\'e1ch say m\'ea th\'e8m kh\'e1t.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'fat ch\'e1n th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  th\'ec m\'fat cho em nh\'e9, c\u7911 a em b\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7865 p b\u7857 ng c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau anh \u273 \'e2u nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t kh\'e1c \u273 \'e2u c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o gi\u7889 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o \u273 \'e2u. \u272 \u7875  anh ng\u7855 m xem n\'f3 c\'f3 c\'f2n nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch g\u432 \u7907 ng g\u7841 o n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 b\u7857 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a, n\'f3 t\'e3 l\u7855 m r\u7891 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 kinh nghi\u7879 m l\'e0 h\u417 n th\'f4i h\'ec h\'ec, t\'ed n\u7919 a s\u7869  cho anh bi\u7871 t kinh nghi\u7879 m c\u7911 a em!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  ch\u7913 ! Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i cho anh ng\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i ng\uc0\u7891 i h\u7859 n xu\u7889 ng b\u7871  Qu\u7923 nh l\'ean m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7875  ng\u7855 m ngh\'eda c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n. N\'f3 th\'e2m h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i v\'e0 c\u361 ng x\u7845 u \u273 i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7865 p nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai c\'e1i m\'e9p th\'ec nh\'f4 ra th\uc0\u7853 t nhi\u7879 u. T\'f4i xoa xoa hai c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7913 a ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7885 c m\u7897 t ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o b\'ean trong r\u7891 i ngo\'e1y ngo\'e1y sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7851 n nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 . Ch\u7885 c v\'e0o m\'e0 ngo\'e1y nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng ra n\u432 \u7899 c, kh\'f4ng ra m\u7899 i l\u7841  \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u7873  h\u7873  r\u7891 i b\u7843 o ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c h\u417 n h\u7859 n \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to h\u417 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n h\'ec h\'ec, em c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t v\'ec sao n\u7919 a, c\'e0ng ng\'e0y em c\'e0ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u7885 c ch\u7885 c v\'e0o c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n phun \u7847 m \u7847 m ra \u7845 y.\cb1 \
