\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  kh\'f4ng s\u7907  ai bi\u7871 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0 b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng bi\u7871 t th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 l\'e0m g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u, mi\u7877 n l\'e0 m\'ecnh l\'e0m ch\u7859 ng \u7843 nh h\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n ai l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i h\uc0\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  l\'e0m th\u7871  th\'ec l\'e0m sao m\'e0 c\'f3 s\u7913 c !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\u7913 c, b\u7841 n em c\'f2n c\'f3 \u273 \u7913 a l\'e0m v\u7899 i b\u7889 n n\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\uc0\u7901 i n\'f3i n\'e0o v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh n\u7919 a t\'f4i ng\u7891 i th\u7915  ra th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh tr\u432 \u7901 n l\u7841 i r\u7891 i kh\u7869  \'f4m t\'f4i, tay th\'ec vu\u7889 t ve con c\u7863 c m\u7873 m o\u7863 t m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3i chung l\'e0 d\'f2ng \uc0\u273 \u7901 i x\'f4 \u273 \u7849 y, \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u hay \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7845 y th\'f4i. Th\u7871  bao gi\u7901  anh \u273 \u7883 nh c\u432 \u7899 i em \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i em \u7845 y h\u7885 c xong th\'f4i, em c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i ch\u7885 n ngh\u7873  g\'ec l\'e0m ch\u7913 , \u273 i b\'e1n thu\u7889 c l\'e1 m\'e3i \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\uc0\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7901 i gian r\u7843 nh em \u273 i h\u7885 c l\'e0m t\'f3c.. v\u7899 i g\u7897 i \u273 \u7853 u, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng l\u7845 y ti\u7873 n h\u7885 c t\u7847 m n\u7917 a n\u259 m r\u7891 i em l\'e0m t\'f3c lu\'f4n m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec c\uc0\u7913  n\u7857 m cho Qu\u7923 nh m\'e2n m\'ea hai h\'f2n d\'e1i v\u7899 i c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c. \u272 \u7871 n khi n\'f3 d\u7847 n d\u7847 n c\u7913 ng l\'ean th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 l\'e2u c\u7913 ng ra ph\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n! Gi\u7901  kh\'f4ng nh\u432  ng\'e0y x\u432 a l\'ean nhanh r\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng nhanh \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nheo m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i t\u7921  nhi\'ean c\'fai xu\u7889 ng li\u7871 m l\'e1p ngon l\'e0nh r\u7891 i \u273 \u7843 o v\'f2ng quanh b\u7865 n r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'f9i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a m\'fat r\u7891 i tay x\'f3c x\'f3c con c\u7863 c sau \u273 \'f3 Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913 ng l\'ean r\u7891 i em c\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a cho m\'e0 xem!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u c\u7911 a em c\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a th\'eam t\'ed n\u7919 a c\'f3 m\'e0 ng\'e3 lu\'f4n \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 m\'e0 anh phun \uc0\u273 \u7847 y v\'e0o l\u7891 n em ch\u7913  c\'f2n l\'e2u m\u7899 i c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n em ng\'e3 ng\u7921 a \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  xem!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i bi\uc0\u7871 t th\u7915 a l\'e0 kh\'edch t\u432 \u7899 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng l\'e0m m\u7897 t c\'e1ch nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh. N\'f3i xong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\u7889  g\u7855 ng c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat t\u7891 m t\u7897 p cho con c\u7863 c nhanh ch\'f3ng c\u7913 ng l\'ean r\u7891 i l\u7845 y tay day day c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh sau \u273 \'f3 nh\'e9t v\'e0o m\'e0 nh\'fan th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai b\uc0\u7901  m\'f4ng c\u259 ng tr\'f2n d\u7853 p v\'e0o hai h\'f2n d\'e1i b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i h\u417 i t\u7913 c t\u7913 c nh\u432 ng ch\'ednh v\'ec th\u7871  con c\u7863 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7885  s\'e1t m\u7841 nh v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n n\'ean t\'f4i s\u432 \u7899 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng nh\'fan m\uc0\u7841 nh Qu\u7923 nh c\'e0ng h\u259 ng. \u272 \u432 a tay t\u7921  b\'f3p hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa c\u7911 a m\u7881 nh \u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 s\u7907  em ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u m\uc0\u7899 i c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n s\u7907  em nh\'e9! Th\u7871 .. \u273 \'e3 c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n ch\u432 a.. m\u7899 i nh\'fan c\'f3 v\'e0i c\'e1i m\'e0 nho\'e9t h\u7871 t n\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u m\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \'e3 nh\'e9\'85 c\'e0ng m\u7841 nh c\'e0ng h\u259 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\'fan m\u7897 t h\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n khi th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n v\'ec m\u7879 t th\'ec t\'f4i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u b\u7871  Qu\u7923 nh l\'ean m\'e0 \u273 \u7883 t ki\u7875 u b\u7891 ng em r\u7891 i m\u7845 y ki\u7875 u kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao c\u417 n h\u7913 ng t\'ecnh n\'e0y khi\u7871 n t\'f4i h\'f9ng h\u7909 c th\u7853 t l\'e2u th\'ec m\u7899 i phun \u7847 m \u7847 m tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o l\u7891 n Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh kh\'e9p ch\'e2n c\u7863 p ch\u7863 t l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7847 n hai ra \'edt h\u7859 n h\u417 n l\u7847 n m\u7897 t nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7883  m\'fat h\u7871 t r\u7891 i th\'ec c\'f2n \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'c2n \'e1i xong th\'ec t\'f4i v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh n\u7857 m t\'e2m s\u7921  \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u mu\u7897 n r\u7891 i m\u7899 i chia tay v\u7873 . Tr\u432 \u7899 c khi v\u7873  Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7915 ng cho ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau bi\u7871 t chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i n\'f3i v\u7899 i t\'f4i nh\u432  v\u7853 y. T\'f4i kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i ch\'e0o Qu\u7923 nh sau \u273 \'f3 \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  ch\u7885 n m\u7897 t c\'e1i v\'e1y th\u7853 t \u273 \u7865 p coi nh\u432  t\u7841  l\u7895 i v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n.\
