\cf2 \cb3 Bu\uc0\u7893 i t\u7889 i t\'f4i mang \'e1o cho Huy\u7873 n m\u7863 c th\'ec Huy\u7873 n th\'edch l\u7855 m. C\'e1i v\'e1y ren cao qu\'e1 \u273 \u7847 u g\u7889 i n\'ean khi Huy\u7873 n m\u7863 c v\'e0o \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  c\u7863 p \u273 \'f9i thon nh\u7887  \u273 \u7865 p v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Quay quay tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c g\u432 \u417 ng Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao t\uc0\u7921  d\u432 ng l\u7841 i t\u7863 ng em v\'e1y th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec mu\uc0\u7889 n em \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tin \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y hay l\'e0 \u273 \u7883 nh h\u7889 i l\u7897  em c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7889 i l\u7897  c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \'e2u! Mu\u7889 n cho v\u7907  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  c\u432 \u7899 i xinh h\u417 n ch\u7913  c\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 h\u7889 i l\u7897  c\u417  ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t nghi nghi l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng nh\u7905  em xinh qu\'e1 c\'f3 ai v\u7907 t m\u7845 t em th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  th\u7857 ng n\'e0o m\'e0 v\u7907 t \u259 n \u273 \'f2n ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u7865 p th\u7853 t nh\u432 ng m\'e0 m\u7863 c v\'e0o v\u7851 n ki\u7875 u kh\'eau g\u7907 i th\u7871  n\'e0o \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'eau g\uc0\u7907 i th\'ec nh\'ecn m\u7899 i \u273 \u7865 p ch\u7913 , nh\u432  th\u7871  m\u7899 i cu\u7889 n h\'fat. M\u7863 c th\u7871  n\'e0y th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng kh\'f4ng m\u7863 c \u273 \u7891  b\'ean trong, c\u7913  k\'e9o l\'ean l\'e0 l\'e0m lu\'f4n th\'f4i nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'fang l\'e0 c\'e1i \u273 \u7891  d\'e2m d\'ea ch\u7881  th\u7871  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ai b\u7857 ng th\'f4i. Gh\'e9t c\'e1i m\u7863 t th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i th\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a Huy\u7873 n th\'edch t\'f4i nh\u432  th\u7871 . Huy\u7873 n ng\'fang ngu\u7849 y m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i xoay tr\'f2n tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u432 \u417 ng th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, \'f4m l\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i xoa xoa m\'f4ng sau \u273 \'f3 vu\u7889 t ng\u432 \u7907 c l\'ean c\u7863 p m\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n g\u7841 t nh\u7865  tay t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\'e0m s\u7905  bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng m\'e0 cho anh s\'e0m s\u7905  m\u7897 t t\u7865 o th\'f4i m\'e0 c\'f3 ch\u7871 t ai \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec t\'f4i ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c xoa xoa c\u7863 p m\'f4ng r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n qua h\'e1ng v\'f2ng l\'ean tr\'ean m\'e0 xoa c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n. Huy\u7873 n t\u7915  x\u432 a v\u7851 n th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i s\u7901  m\'f3 nh\u432  v\u7853 y n\'ean khi v\u7915 a lu\u7891 n l\'ean xoa xoa c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t ve m\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y \u273 \u361 ng qu\u7847 n l\'f3t \u273 \'e3 \u7849 m \u7849 m. C\'fai s\'e1t v\'e0o h\'f4n nh\u7865  l\'ean v\'e0nh tai t\u7899 i m\u7845 y l\u7885 n t\'f3c mai m\u7887 ng manh t\'f4i th\u7911  th\u7881  t\u7915 ng l\u7901 i ngon ng\u7885 t:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m r\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Anh th\u7845 y \u432 \u7899 t r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913  s\u7901  m\'f3 th\u7871  em ch\u7883 u l\'e0m sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec, nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 c\'e0ng nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec anh c\'e0ng th\'edch, th\u7871  cho anh m\'fat c\'e1i nh\'e9 c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? N\u432 \u7899 c ra nhi\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'fat s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913  nh\u432 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  t\u7889 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7889 i g\'ec m\'e0 t\u7889 i, anh l\'e0 anh mu\u7889 n ngay b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\u417 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\'f3i kh\'f4ng cho nh\u432 ng t\'f4i bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\'e0 c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat l\'e0 Huy\u7873 n s\u7861 n s\'e0ng banh r\u7897 ng hai ch\'e2n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh th\u7853 t r\u7897 ng lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 p t\u7909 c h\'f4n v\'e0o g\'e1y nh\u432 ng tay kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \'f4m v\u7899 i s\u7903  m\'f3 c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n n\u7919 a, t\'f4i lu\u7891 n v\'e0o c\'e1i c\u7841 p qu\u7847 n r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m \'e0m t\u7909 t xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i. C\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t xu\u7889 ng ngang g\u7889 i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i ra ngo\'e0i \uc0\u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a \u273 i! Nh\u7905  ai nh\'ecn th\u7845 y ng\u7841 i ch\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'ed h\uc0\u7917 ng t\'f4i quay ra \u273 \'f3ng c\u7917 a kh\'e9p lu\'f4n c\u7843  c\'e1i s\u7917 a s\u7893  l\u7841 i, quay l\u7841 i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n v\u7851 n \u273 \u7913 ng, k\u7879  cho c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t l\u417  l\u7917 ng \u7903  g\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng t\'f4i v\u7915 a k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng g\'f3t ch\'e2n v\u7915 a nh\'ecn c\'e1i \u273 \u361 ng qu\u7847 n. N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ch\u7843 y ra \u432 \u7899 t m\u7897 t m\u7843 ng to r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7913 t c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t sang m\u7897 t b\'ean t\'f4i mon men \u273 \u432 a n\u259 m \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay c\u7911 a m\'ecnh vu\u7889 t d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i l\'ean t\u7853 n khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khe l\uc0\u7891 n kh\'edt khao m\'fap m\'e1p nh\u7851 y nh\u7851 y n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'e8m v\'f4 c\'f9ng. M\u7863 c d\'f9 t\'f4i v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m t\'ecnh nhi\u7873 u nh\u432 ng c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng c\u7845 p nh\u432  Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\'e0 nh\uc0\u7865  nh\u7865  tay d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\'ean trong b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ti\u7871 t ra nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n. Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7855 n nh\u7865  v\'e0o c\u7893  r\u7891 i b\u7901  vai m\u7887 ng manh t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch l\uc0\u7855 m \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng v\u7907 .. anh s\u7901  th\u7871  n\'e0y t\'ea l\u7855 m h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n lim dim m\u7855 t ng\u7917 a c\u7893  ra \u273 \u7857 ng sau r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e2ng.. s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng.. em mu\u7889 n anh ch\u7885 c m\u7897 t ng\'f3n v\'e0o.. ki\u7875 u n\'e0y ch\u7885 c m\u7897 t ng\'f3n v\'e0o b\'ean trong m\'f3c m\'f3c th\'edch l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? Ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng ra anh m\'f3c cho nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u432 ng \u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t \u273 en huy\u7873 n v\u7851 n lim dim \u273 \u7875  t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c kho\'e1i l\u7841 c do ng\'f3n tay c\u7911 a t\'f4i mang l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  ng\'f3n tay ng\u7853 p l\'fat v\'e0o t\'f4i day day th\'ec Huy\u7873 n o\u7857 n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 l\u7855 m anh \u417 i.. em th\'edch.\u432 \'85.e..em s\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\u7845 c l\'ean t\u7915 ng ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng cong c\'e1i m\'f4ng ra \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i m\'f3c l\u7891 n. N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n m\u7895 i l\'fac m\u7897 t ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u nh\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u7881  \u273 \'fat hai ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng m\u7897 t l\'fac r\u7891 i quay l\u7841 i \u273 \u7889 i di\u7879 n v\u7899 i t\'f4i v\'e0 \'f4m gh\'ec l\u7845 y c\u7893  t\'f4i m\'e0 n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i, ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a t\'ecnh h\u7915 ng h\u7921 c b\'ean trong th\'e2n th\u7875  n\'f5n n\'e0 c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n b\'f9ng ch\'e1y th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7915 a n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i ch\u7885 c lu\'f4n hai ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t ng\'f3n n\u7919 a, c\u7913  th\u7871  m\'e0 m\'f3c m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng \'f3c \'f3c c\u7911 a n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ch\u7843 y ra h\'f2a c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ti\u7871 ng r\'ean d\'e2m d\'e2t kh\u7869  kh\u7869  vang l\'ean \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 n. \u272 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec t\'f4i nh\u7843  c\'e1i \u273 \'e0u l\u432 \u7905 i m\u7873 m m\u7841 i ng\u7885 t ng\'e0o c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  anh t\u7889 c v\'e1y l\'ean chui v\'e0o m\'e0 m\'fat nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! H\'ec h\'ec, cho anh r\'fac v\'e1y em lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nheo m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i tinh ngh\u7883 ch th\'ec t\'f4i ng\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng, v\'e9n c\'e1i v\'e1y l\'ean r\u7891 i chui v\'e0o. V\'f2ng tay ra ph\'eda sau \'f4m l\u7845 y c\u7863 p m\'f4ng tr\'f2n l\u7859 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u7913  th\u7871  m\'e0 n\'fat li\'ean h\u7891 i c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n m\'fap m\'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n th\u7853 t ro, tay b\u7845 u ch\u7863 t v\'e0o vai t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 qu\'e1.. ch\u7891 ng y\'eau \u417 i.. n\'fat c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a em m\u7841 nh n\u7919 a l\'ean \u273 i n\'e0o.. cho c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m d\u7885 c c\'e1i khe \u7845 y\'85em s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m..\u273 \'e3 l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'fat \uc0\u273 \'e1m n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ng\u7885 t ng\u7885 t v\'e0o mi\'eang t\'f4i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bu\uc0\u7891 n bu\u7891 n kh\'f3 t\u7843 .. nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m anh \u417 i.. em th\'edch li\u7871 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  mu\u7889 n li\u7871 m ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y hay l\'e0 n\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch ki\uc0\u7875 u n\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng h\u417 n v\'ec th\u7871  d\'e3 h\u417 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec n\u7857 m ra \u273 i.. d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra anh n\'fat cho..\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\'ed h\u7917 ng ng\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i v\'e9n c\'e1i v\'e1y c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean ngang b\u7909 ng \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat t\u7891 m t\u7897 p c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a m\'fat v\u7915 a day h\u7897 t le khi\u7871 n Huy\u7873 n kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, l\u259 n l\u7897 n tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f2n n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n th\'ec tu\'f4n ra ph\u7843 i n\'f3i l\'e0 nhi\u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n l\'e0m tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a c\'e1i khe r\u7891 i l\'ean \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u417  th\u417  tr\'ean mu l\u7891 n n\u7919 a. L\'f4ng l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  c\'f3 v\'e0i c\u7897 ng nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\'ednh v\'ec th\u7871  nh\'ecn c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n tr\'f4ng c\'e0ng \u273 \u7865 p v\'e0 g\u7907 i c\u7843 m h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\uc0\u7871 m l\'e1p ch\'e1n ch\'ea th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, t\u7909 t lu\'f4n c\'e1i qu\u7847 n ra \u273 \u7875  con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean lu\'f4n. Huy\u7873 n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y con c\u7863 c t\'f4i th\'ec ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0o xu\uc0\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i em m\'fat c\u7863 c cho.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7857 m m\'fat kh\'f4ng s\u432 \u7899 ng \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'fat c\uc0\u7863 c em th\'edch ki\u7875 u qu\u7923  qu\u7923  m\'fat d\u7877  ch\u7883 u h\u417 n v\u7899 i nh\'ecn ngon l\'e0nh h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec tr\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \'e3 nghi\u7879 n con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a ch\u7891 ng ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i \'e2u y\u7871 m tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7911 a ch\u7891 ng th\'ec nghi\u7879 n l\'e2u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i. Th\u7871  ch\u7891 ng c\'f3 nghi\u7879 n c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a v\u7907  kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd th\'ec Huy\u7873 n tr\u432 \u7901 n nh\u7865  xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432  m\u7897 t con m\'e8o mun r\u7891 i kh\u7869  kh\'e9 n\u7855 m l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c t\'f4i vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c c\u432 ng chi\u7873 u con c\u7863 c kh\'e1c h\u7859 n Qu\u7923 nh chi\u7873 u h\'f4m nay, Qu\u7923 nh chi\u7873 u con c\u7863 c t\'f4i v\u7899 i m\u7897 t c\u7843 m gi\'e1c th\'e8m kh\'e1t c\'f2n Huy\u7873 n v\u7899 i ki\u7875 u c\u432 ng n\u7921 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t d\u7885 c c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c \u273 \u7875  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c l\u7897  r\'f5 ra r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m lu\'f4n m\'e0 m\'fat. Huy\u7873 n th\'ec th\'edch m\'fat lu\'f4n c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng li\u7871 m l\'e1p nh\u432  Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c b\'f3ng \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng th\'ec Huy\u7873 n c\'fai kh\u7869  xu\u7889 ng li\u7871 m ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i li\u7871 m sang hai \u273 \'f9i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e0ng li\uc0\u7871 m th\'ec Huy\u7873 n c\'e0ng th\'edch th\'fa, c\u7889  g\u7855 ng l\'e0m cho con c\u7863 c tr\u417 n nh\u7851 y l\'ean r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean \'e2u y\u7871 m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'e2y gi\u7901  l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em th\'e8m ch\uc0\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Em \u273 ang h\u7887 i anh c\'f2n g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec l\'e0m \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, n\'f3 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean l\'e0 \u273 \'fat v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. V\u7853 y em th\'e8m ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'eau tr\'f4i n\'ean Huy\u7873 n t\u432 ng t\u7917 ng n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\uc0\u7911 a em nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u432  th\u7871  l\'e0 l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i! H\u7887 i l\'e0m g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'fac kh\'edch v\'ec tr\'eau \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i v\u7851 n c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat th\'eam m\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a r\u7891 i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7891 ng \u417 i, v\'e9n v\'e1y l\'ean v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh \u273 \u7883 t nhau nh\'e9! Em th\'edch ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Ch\u7891 ng c\u361 ng th\'edch, m\'e0 d\u7841 o n\'e0y n\'f3i \'93\u273 \u7883 t\'94 tho\u7843 i m\'e1i nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec, hai v\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ph\u7843 i d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng t\'ed ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Huy\uc0\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i ph\'e1i c\u7917 a s\u7893 , tay n\u7855 m nh\u7865  v\'e0o ch\u7845 n xong r\u7891 i ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng l\'ean. Ki\u7875 u n\'e0y th\'ec nh\'ecn qua g\u432 \u417 ng th\u7845 y r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i m\'f4ng tr\'f2n l\u7859 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ra ph\'eda sau t\'f4i t\uc0\u7889 c v\'e1y l\'ean li\u7871 m l\'e1p c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n m\u7845 y c\'e1i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i m\u7899 i ng\u7891 i c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c c\u7885  c\u7885  v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Do chi\uc0\u7873 u nay l\'e0m v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh t\u7853 n hai l\u7847 n n\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0m \u273 \u7871 n n\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i xu\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7913  b\'ecnh t\u297 nh t\'f4i c\u7885  d\'e0i theo c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n th\u7853 t l\'e2u r\u7891 i m\u7899 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  \u7845 n v\'e0o b\'ean trong. Hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n d\u7847 n d\u7847 n t\'e1ch ra \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i. Huy\u7873 n lim dim m\u7855 t r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay sao c\uc0\u7863 c ch\u7891 ng to th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e1p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m n\'e0o m\'e0 ch\uc0\u7859 ng nh\u432  h\'f4m n\'e0o c\'f3 kh\'e1c g\'ec \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t h\'f4m nay l\u7891 n v\u7907  c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n c\u7863 c ch\u7891 ng to l\u7855 m \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 To th\'ec c\'e0ng s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913  sao!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  to th\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng\'85 c\u7855 m s\'e2u v\'e0o \u273 i ch\u7891 ng \u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u7889  g\u7855 ng ng\u7893 ng c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean th\u7853 t cao \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i ch\u7885 c c\'e1i con c\u7863 c v\'e0o th\u7853 t s\'e2u. C\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c banh r\u7897 ng l\u7895  l\u7891 n r\u7891 i chui tu\u7889 t v\'e0o th\u7853 t s\'e2u. Huy\u7873 n kh\u7869  kh\u7869  co b\'f3p c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n cho n\'f3 qu\u7845 n ch\u7863 t c\'e1i con c\u7863 c r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7883 t m\u7841 nh v\'e0o \u273 i anh..em th\'edch l\u7855 m..anh \u7841 .. s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432  ph\'e1t \u273 i\'ean lu\'f4n \u7845 y.. h\'edch h\'edch .. \u273 \'e3 \u417 i l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 lu\'f4n anh \u417 i.a.a. \u273 \u7883 t m\u7841 nh n\u7919 a \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 t v\u7915 a th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh n\u7919 a \u7845 y.. c\u7855 m th\u7853 t s\'e2u con c\u7863 c v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  c\u7911 a em \u7845 y.. nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \'e3 l\u7855 m anh \u7841 .. s\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng ph\'e0nh ph\u7841 ch vang l\'ean th\u7853 t to khi t\'f4i \'f4m ch\u7863 t c\'e1i m\'f4ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7883 t ph\u7847 m ph\u7853 p v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n. Huy\u7873 n o\u7857 n ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng, n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n th\'ec nh\u7887  t\u7887 ng t\u7887 ng xu\u7889 ng b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i v\'ec ch\u7843 y ra qu\'e1 nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Doggy ch\'e1n th\'ec t\'f4i b\uc0\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0o ra gi\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7841 ch c\'e1i v\'e1y l\'ean anh l\'e0m ki\u7875 u truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ra gi\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng m\'e0 l\'e0m ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y th\'ec c\u7903 i lu\'f4n v\'e1y ra ch\u7913 ! M\u7863 c l\'e0m g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7863 c m\u7899 i k\'edch th\'edch.. n\'e0o ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i em!\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe t\'f4i b\uc0\u7843 o th\'ec Huy\u7873 n ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng, n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n c\'e1i g\u7889 i v\'e0o h\'f4ng m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n nh\'f4 l\'ean th\u7853 t cao.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7895  l\u7891 n \u273 \u7887  au b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i banh r\u7897 ng ra ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i chui v\'e0o s\'e2u b\'ean trong. T\'f4i \u7847 m con c\u7863 c \u273 \u7853 p d\u7853 p l\'ean c\'e1i mu r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u7841 o n\'e0y mu cao ph\u7871 t nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Em c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\'f3 cao h\u417 n, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 b\'e9o n\'ean n\'f3 m\u7899 i to nh\u432  th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\'fai xu\u7889 ng li\u7871 m th\'eam v\'e0i c\'e1i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i m\u7905 i kh\u7869  c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c nh\'e9t ti\u7871 p v\'e0o m\'e0 nh\u7853 p. Huy\u7873 n qu\u7863 p ch\'e2n ngang h\'f4ng r\u7891 i tay ch\u7889 ng nh\u7865  v\'e0o ng\u7921 c t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\'e2u c\u361 ng nh\u432  l\'fac n\'e3y \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'e2y gi\u7901  c\'f2n c\u7843 m nh\u7853 n c\u7863 c anh to n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng to n\uc0\u7919 a..h\'ec h\'ec.. ch\u7855 c t\u7841 i em ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c n\'ean kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y to.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7845 p ch\'e1n ch\'ea v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n m\'e0 v\u7851 n ch\u432 a xu\u7845 t v\'ec h\'f4m nay t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m hai l\u7847 n r\u7891 i. Huy\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \'e2u y\u7871 m v\'ec l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c hai l\u7847 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Xoa xoa ng\uc0\u7921 c t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 h\'f4m nay kh\uc0\u7887 e th\u7871 ? H\'f9ng h\u7909 c m\'e3i m\'e0 ch\u432 a ra v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m qu\'e1 n\'ean ch\uc0\u432 a ra ch\u7913  sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i b\uc0\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng l\'e0m ki\u7875 u \'fap th\'eca. Nh\u7845 p nh\u7893 m m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i r\'fat con c\u7863 c ra b\u7855 n h\u7871 t tinh tr\'f9ng l\'ean m\'f4ng Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i n\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\'e9o c\'e1i v\'e1y xu\uc0\u7889 ng lau \u273 \'e1m tinh tr\'f9ng \u432 \u7899 t nh\u7865 p tr\'ean m\'f4ng r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ham h\uc0\u7889  l\u7855 m c\u417 ! B\'e2y gi\u7901  th\'ec th\u7903  kh\'f4ng ra h\u417 i kia k\'eca!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  ch\u7913 \'85 c\'e1i l\u7891 n ngon l\'e0nh th\u7871  kia m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7883 t kh\'f4ng \u259 n th\'ec qu\'e1 ph\'ed \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7911 a anh ch\u7913  c\'f3 c\u7911 a ai \u273 \'e2u, kh\'f4ng h\'f4m nay th\'ec c\'f2n ng\'e0y mai c\u417  m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y h\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nheo m\uc0\u7855 t th\'ec Huy\u7873 n chu m\'f4i l\'e8 l\u432 \u7905 i tr\'eau t\'f4i r\u7891 i v\'e0o trong nh\'e0 t\u7855 m. Hai \u273 \u7913 a \'f4m nhau t\'e2m s\u7921  r\u7891 i ng\u7911  l\'fac n\'e0o kh\'f4ng hay.\
