\cf2 \cb3 M\uc0\u7845 y h\'f4m sau \u273 i l\'e0m t\'f4i th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng nh\u7855 n tin cho Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh h\u7847 u nh\u432  \'edt nh\u7855 n l\u7841 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  s\u7907  ph\'e1 v\u7905  h\u7841 nh ph\'fac c\u7911 a t\'f4i. Cu\u7889 i tu\u7847 n t\u7921  d\u432 ng Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\u7853 p hu\u7845 n n\'ean t\'f4i ph\u7843 i \u7903  nh\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\'ednh chuy\uc0\u7879 n \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7841 c cu\u7889 i n\u259 m c\u432 \u7899 i m\u7845 t m\u7897 t ng\'e0y c\'f2n ng\'e0y ngh\u7881  x\u7843  h\u417 i. G\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i cho Huy\u7873 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n n\u7919 a m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7873 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng bi\uc0\u7871 t l\'e0m g\'ec lang thang ngo\'e0i ph\u7889  th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7855 t g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang \u273 i caf\'e9 v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng, nh\'ecn c\'e1i \u273 i\u7879 u l\u7843  l\u7903 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2m nhi t\'e1ch caf\'e9 r\uc0\u7891 i t\'f4i ch\u417 i ngh\u297  \'93Hay l\'e0 xem Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0m \u259 n th\u7871  n\'e0o v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng n\u7885 \'94.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u7885 n m\u7897 t b\'e0n khu\u7845 t g\u7847 n g\'f3c t\'f4i ng\u7891 i quan s\'e1t. Qu\u7923 nh u\u7889 ng caf\'e9 xong th\'ec ra \'f4 t\'f4 c\'f9ng v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7917 i ti\u7873 n r\u7891 i \u273 i theo sau h\'f3a ra Qu\u7923 nh v\u7899 i hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng v\'e0o nh\'e0 ngh\u7881 . T\'f4i bi\u7871 t r\u7891 i th\'f4i \u273 \'e0nh \u273 \u7907 i \u7903  ngo\'e0i xem l\'fac n\'e0o Qu\u7923 nh ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7871 n h\u417 i hai ti\u7871 ng sau th\'ec hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng ra tr\u432 \u7899 c c\'f2n Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  m\u7879 t m\u7887 i ra sau. Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e0n \'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng g\u7841  g\u7851 m g\'ec v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  l\u432 \u7905 ng l\u7921  r\u7891 i t\u7915  ch\u7889 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 eo c\'e1i t\'fai x\'e1ch, l\u7919 ng th\u7919 ng b\u432 \u7899 c t\u7915 ng b\u432 \u7899 c u\u7875  o\u7843 i tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7845 m m\'e1y g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao l\'fac n\'e0y Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i nh\u7845 c m\'e1y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7903 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y sao m\'e0 \uc0\u273 i th\u7845 y v\u7867  m\u7863 t u\u7875  o\u7843 i th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ti\uc0\u7871 ng th\u7903  d\'e0i c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh kh\u7869  vang l\'ean:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao anh bi\uc0\u7871 t em \u273 ang \u7903  ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u273 ang qu\'e1n caf\'e9 g\u7847 n nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  H\u432 \u417 ng Giang k\'eca.. \u273 ang l\u7919 ng th\u7919 ng \u273 i c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'fac n\'e0y Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7899 i ngo\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i nh\'ecn c\'e1i t\'ean nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  m\'ecnh v\u7915 a v\'e0o r\u7891 i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 v\'e2ng h\'ec h\'ec! Anh ng\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  ch\u7895  cho Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh l\u7919 ng th\u7919 ng sang \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o qu\'e1n. Th\u7845 y t\'f4i Qu\u7923 nh t\u7887  v\u7867  t\u432 \u417 i t\u7881 nh h\u7859 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng \u7911  r\u361  nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7863 t c\'e1i t\'fai x\'e1ch l\'ean b\'e0n Qu\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i h\u7887 i t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 i caf\'e9 v\u7899 i v\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i hay sao m\'e0 \u273 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 th\'ec v\uc0\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i anh ph\u7843 i \u273 i t\u7853 p hu\u7845 n m\u7845 t m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n n\'ean m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 i linh tinh th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'f4i \u7845 y m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 i linh tinh m\'e0 c\'f2n nh\'ecn th\u7845 y em \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nghi theo d\'f5i l\u7855 m nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh b\uc0\u7855 t g\u7863 p v\'f4 t\'ecnh th\u7845 y em v\u7899 i m\u7845 y kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng c\u7911 a em th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'ec m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c m\'e0 anh, gi\u7901  em c\u361 ng \u273 i l\'e0m PG r\u7891 i n\'ean c\u361 ng c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u m\u7889 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, kh\'f4ng \u273 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ti\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  m\u7897 t l\'fac v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh. Nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'e1i b\u7843 n t\'ednh d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3 qu\'e1 hi\u7875 u nhau r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u chuy\uc0\u7879 n loanh quanh m\u7897 t h\u7891 i r\u7891 i c\u361 ng quay l\u7841 i c\'e1i v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  mu\'f4n thu\u7903  \u273 \'f3 l\'e0 t\'ecnh d\u7909 c th\'f4i. V\u7851 n tho\'e1ng v\u7867  m\u7879 t m\u7887 i tr\'ean khu\'f4n m\u7863 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c trang \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7853 m, t\'f4i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 m\u7879 t l\u7855 m h\u7843 ? Li\'ean ti\u7871 p hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i m\'fat nh\u7865  c\u7889 c sinh t\u7889  b\u417  m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n li\'ean ti\u7871 p, hai ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ng\uc0\u7841 c nhi\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i c\'f9ng m\u7897 t l\'fac \'e1.. kh\u7887 e th\u7871  \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng.. n\'f3i chung hai c\'e1i \'f4ng ki ham vui th\'f4i ch\u7913  kh\u7887 e g\'ec, nh\u432 ng b\'e2y gi\u7901  v\u7851 n c\'f2n \'ea \u7849 m \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng kh\uc0\u7887 e m\'e0 \'ea \u7849 m \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! T\u7841 i m\u7845 y \'f4ng \u7845 y u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c r\u7891 i d\'f9ng bao gai n\u7919 a. C\'e1i \u273 \'f3 c\u7911 a m\u7845 y \'f4ng \u7845 y b\'e9 x\'edu nh\u432 ng m\'e0 d\'f9ng bao gai n\'ean \u273 au l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bao th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng h\u417 n ch\u7913  sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng g\'ec m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng\'85 \u273 au b\u7887  x\u7915 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 c\'f2n \u273 au \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c th\'f4i ch\u7913  sau l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a, em ph\u7843 o d\'f9ng gel n\u7919 a \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! H\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c l\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 ph\u7843 i d\'f9ng \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'e1c b\'e2y gi\u7901  kh\'e1c ch\u7913 ! Hai \'f4ng \u7845 y l\'e0m h\'f9ng h\u7909 c \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 h\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c chi\u7873 u m\u7895 i anh c\'f2n gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u nhi\u7875 u nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c kh\'e1c gi\u7901  kh\'e1c ch\u7913 . !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i khu\u7845 y c\u7889 c caf\'e9 ng\u7891 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\'f4m g\'ec l\'e0m xong c\'f3 c\u7843 m x\'fac g\'ec kh\'f4ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe t\'f4i h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 c\uc0\u7843 m x\'fac m\'e0 th\u7871  \'e0? T\'ecnh \u273 \u7847 u c\u7911 a em sao m\'e0 em qu\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\'ec h\'ec. Anh c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng qu\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c em! Em bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  kh\'f4ng qu\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i g\'ec c\u7911 a em?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7847 y c\'e1i! Em bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a.. h\'ec h\'ec nh\u7845 t l\'e0 c\'e1i \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i t\'f4i t\'f2 m\'f2 h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  m\u7845 y \'f4ng \u7845 y d\'f9ng bao gai c\'f3 to l\'ean kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913 , b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f3 h\u417 n ch\u7909 c ph\'e2n chi\u7873 u d\'e0i nh\u432 ng d\'f9ng xong \u273 \u7871 n m\u432 \u7901 i l\u259 m ph\'e2n \u7845 y, c\'f2n to n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh th\uc0\u7845 y trong phim ng\u432 \u7901 i ta th\'edch m\'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Trong phim kh\'e1c ngo\'e0i \uc0\u273 \u7901 i c\'f3 kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng nh\u432  phim \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\'f4m n\'e0o anh th\u7917  c\'e1i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ri\'eang anh kh\'f4ng cho th\uc0\u7917 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng cho th\uc0\u7917 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec em th\'edch ch\'e2n th\uc0\u7853 t h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  m\u7897 t ch\'fat c\u361 ng c\'f3 ch\u7871 t ai \u273 \'e2u c\u417  ch\u7913 . Coi anh nh\u432  m\u7845 y kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng kia c\u7911 a em c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  c\'f3 l\'e0m sao \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Coi l\'e0 coi th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m th\'ec coi l\'e0m sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432  th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i th\'eam c\'e1c ki\u7875 u \'e2n \'e1i r\u7891 i \u273 \'f9 th\u7917  linh tinh n\u7919 a. Qu\u7923 nh t\u432 \u7901 i c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e0 k\u7875  r\u7891 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai trao \u273 \u7893 i v\'f4 t\u432  \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u mu\u7891 n th\'ec t\'f4i r\u7911  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i \u259 n. C\u7843  hai nh\'e2m nhi \u273 \u7871 n mu\u7897 n th\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i nh\'e0 tr\uc0\u7885  \u7903  \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7875  anh \u273 \u432 a v\u7873  n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'f3 h\u417 i mem trong ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'ean n\'e2ng n\'e2ng r\u7891 i. \'d4m l\u7845 y \'f4i r\u7891 i ng\u7843  \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o ng\u7921 c n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i h\'f4m nay cho em ng\uc0\u7911  c\'f9ng anh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? T\u7921  d\u432 ng th\'e8m h\u417 i c\u7911 a anh l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 th\'e8m h\uc0\u417 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t n\u7919 a, nh\u7899  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n t\u7915  khi g\u7863 p anh h\'f4m g\'ec \u7845 y. Quen m\'f9i r\u7891 i h\'ec h\'ec, th\'e8m c\u7843  c\'e1i \u7845 y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7891 n nhi\'ean \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u361 ng qu\'e2n c\u7911 a t\'f4i m\'e0 xoa xoa vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t m\u7863 c k\u7879  trong qu\'e1n nh\u7853 u. \u272 \'e0nh k\u7879  Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i k\'e9o Qu\u7923 nh ra xe r\u7891 i \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n ba sao ven \u273 \'f4 r\u7891 i v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 ngh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 i l\'ean ph\'f2ng th\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'e1i ph\u7883 ch xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 U\uc0\u7889 ng bao nhi\'eau r\u432 \u7907 u r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  c\'e1i r\u432 \u7907 u n\'e0y n\'f3 ng\u7845 m th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y, ph\'ea l\'f2i t\'f2i ph\'f2i lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n! R\u432 \u7907 u x\u7883 n ch\u7913  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i r\u432 \u7907 u \u273 \u7875 u \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng ph\'ea. Nh\'ecn r\u361  r\u432 \u7907 i th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec c\'f2n l\'e0m \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec n\u7919 a nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! \u272 \u7875  xem xem nh\'e9. Em n\'f3ng qu\'e1 \u273 i t\u7855 m \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7891 n nhi\'ean c\u7903 i h\u7871 t qu\u7847 n \'e1o c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra m\'e0 \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m. Hai c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa tr\'f2n nh\u432 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u417 i s\u7879  xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i. C\'e1i mu l\u7891 n cong cong kh\'f4ng c\'f2n m\u7897 t c\u7885 ng l\'f4ng n\'e0o n\u7919 a. Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 t\u7849 y s\u7841 ch r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'ecn c\'e1i mu l\uc0\u7891 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 s\u7907 i l\'f4ng n\'e0o t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7849 y h\u7871 t r\u7891 i \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nh\'ed nh\u7843 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7849 y h\u7871 t cho tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, gi\u7901  l\'e0 em ch\u7881  th\'edch t\u7849 y s\u7841 ch th\'f4i, kh\'f4ng c\'f3 t\u7881 a t\'f3t g\'ec n\u7919 a c\u7843 . \u272 \u7875  th\u7871  n\'e0y th\u7845 y tho\u7843 i m\'e1i h\u417 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7853 t \'e1? Th\u7871  b\u7843 o v\u7907  ch\u432 a c\u432 \u7899 i c\u7911 a anh t\u7849 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec b\uc0\u7843 o \u273 i, kh\'e9o m\'e0 th\u7845 y t\u7849 y l\'f4ng xong c\'fai v\'e0o m\'e0 m\'fat x\'f9m x\u7909 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u7853 t c\u432 \u7901 i v\u7899 i c\'e1i c\'e2u n\'f3i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i c\u7903 i b\u7897  \u273 \u7891  kho\'e1c l\'ean c\'e1i m\'f3c \'e1o sau \u273 \'f3 n\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7845 y chai n\u432 \u7899 c l\u7841 nh tu \u7915 ng \u7921 c v\'ec kh\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c.\
