\cf2 \cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 i v\'e0o ph\'f2ng t\u7855 m x\u7843  n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7897 t h\u7891 i l\'e2u r\u7891 i \u273 i ra v\u7899 i c\'e1i kh\u259 n t\u7855 m qu\u7845 n quanh ng\u432 \u7901 i. Vai v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  c\'e1i h\'ecnh x\u259 m m\'e0 h\'f4m g\'ec t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Xoa xoa m\'e1i t\'f3c nghi\'eang \uc0\u273 \u7847 u Qu\u7923 nh l\'e2u cho kh\'f4 r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh v\'e0o t\uc0\u7855 m \u273 i cho t\u7881 nh r\u432 \u7907 u, t\u7855 m n\u432 \u7899 c n\'f3ng xong t\u7881 nh l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Th\u7871  kh\'f4ng t\u7855 m c\'f9ng anh \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7915 a t\u7855 m xong r\u7891 i c\'f2n t\u7855 m c\'f9ng c\'e1i g\'ec n\u7919 a. Th\'f4i v\'e0o t\u7855 m \u273 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\'e0o t\uc0\u7855 m xong r\u7891 i ra n\u7857 m lu\'f4n v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh. Tay b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u vu\u7889 t ve th\'e2n h\'ecnh m\u7873 m m\u7841 i n\'f5n n\'e0 v\u7899 i c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa.Ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7845 y tu\u7847 n kh\'f4ng g\u7863 p th\'f4i m\'e0 t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\'fa c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh m\u7873 m v\'e0 nh\'e3o l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n s\u259 n ch\u7855 c nh\u432  l\'fac tr\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 G\'e3i g\'e3i c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c v\'fa em t\'e3 l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i m\u7873 m \u273 i t\'ed th\'f4i ch\u7913  l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 t\'e3 l\u7855 m, n\'f3i chung mai kia l\u7845 y ch\u7891 ng th\'ec ch\u7891 ng v\u7851 n s\'e0i t\u7889 t ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ch\'ea \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7903  d\'e0i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c g\'ec \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 ai l\u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nh\'ecn th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\u7889 i anh v\u7851 n c\'f2n m\'ea m\u7849 n l\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y, anh m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 v\u7907  m\u7899 i c\u432 \u7899 i ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng quay l\u7841 i c\u432 \u7899 i em.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7901 i n\'f3i b\u7897 t ph\'e1t c\u7911 a t\'f4i khi\u7871 n Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 v\u7867  th\'e8m kh\'e1t m\u7897 t c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \'f3 l\u7855 m. C\u7863 p m\'f4i h\u7891 ng v\u7851 n c\'f2n son run run l\'ean. Gi\u7885 ng n\'f3i nh\u7887  nh\u7865  r\u432 ng r\u7913 c kh\u7869  vang l\'ean:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  .. sao h\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c..anh kh\'f4ng quay l\u7841 i?\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e2u h\uc0\u7887 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0m t\'f4i b\u7845 t ng\u7901  v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  Qu\u7923 nh s\u7869  h\u7887 i t\'f4i nh\u432  v\u7853 y. Nh\u432 ng c\'f3 l\u7869  l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i ph\u7843 n \u7913 ng nhanh nh\u7841 y v\u7889 n s\u7861 n trong b\u7843 n t\'ednh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh c\'f3 \uc0\u273 \u7907 i nh\u432 ng em \u273 i mi\u7871 t c\'f3 th\'e8m quay l\u7841 i v\u7899 i anh \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u ch\u7843 y m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! C\'f3 l\u7869  do em \u273 i xa qu\'e1 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\u7875  quay l\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a. Nh\u432 ng th\'f4i ch\u7881  c\u7847 n nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y c\u361 ng \u273 \u7911  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y tho\u7843 i m\'e1i r\u7891 i anh nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i xong th\'ec tay \u273 \'e3 lu\u7891 n xu\u7889 ng c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  r\u7891 i. Do c\'f3 r\u432 \u7907 u v\'e0o n\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n Qu\u7923 nh vu\u7889 t vu\u7889 t m\u7845 y c\'e1i l\'e0 c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghi\'eang \uc0\u273 \u7847 u, Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7853 m l\u7845 y n\'fam t\'ed c\u7911 a t\'f4i li\u7871 m li\u7871 m r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i c\u7911 a anh c\'f3 m\'fat t\'ed anh th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng th\'f4i, kh\'e9o ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  anh \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e0o t\u7841 o d\u7847 n \u273 i ch\u7913 , hay h\'f4m n\'e0o em \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o nh\'e9 cho nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i nh\uc0\u432  th\u7871  v\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i c\'f3 m\'e0 c\u7855 t ti\u7871 t anh \'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c li\u7871 p l\'e1p ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i, \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n con c\u7863 c th\'ec t\'f4i ngh\u7875 n c\u7893  d\u7853 y h\u7887 i Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7899 c anh v\u7899 i em kh\'f4ng l\'e0m l\u7895  nh\u7883 , ch\u7855 c sau n\'e0y c\'f3 l\'e0m kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7845 y t\'f4i h\u7887 i th\u7871  th\'ec kh\'fac kh\'edch c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y r\'f5 r\'e0ng kh\'f4ng th\u7917  nh\u7881 , sau n\'e0y th\'ec d\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 em c\'f3 th\u7917  ch\u7913 , l\'e0m l\u7895  nh\u7883  c\u361 ng nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i, m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u \u273 au kh\'f4ng th\u7875  t\u7843  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y nh\u432 ng sau d\u7847 n th\'ec c\u361 ng quen c\u361 ng c\u7843 m th\u7845 y b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i h\uc0\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  s\'e1ng h\'f4m nay c\'f3 l\'e0m kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\'e2n m\'ea con c\u7863 c r\u7891 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 .. h\'f4m nay c\'f3 l\'e0m l\uc0\u7895  nh\u7883  nh\u432 ng m\'e0 em b\u7843 o hai \'f4ng \u7845 y d\'f9ng bao th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'f4i ch\u7913  d\'f9ng bao gai v\u7899 i g\u259 m bi m\'e0 \u273 \'fat v\'e0o th\'ec ch\u7883 u sao th\u7845 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nheo m\uc0\u7855 t c\'e1i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'ed n\uc0\u7919 a cho anh l\'e0m c\'e1i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 l\'e0m ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y ph\u7843 i \u273 i bao \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i m\'e0, ki\u7875 u g\'ec m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 i, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n c\'f3 th\'f4i, em th\u7917  m\u7903  ng\u259 n k\'e9o t\u7911  xem c\'f3 kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7891 m c\u7891 m b\'f2 d\u7853 y k\'e9o c\'e1i ng\u259 n \'e9o r\u7891 i l\u7845 y ba c\'e1i ra r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tho\uc0\u7843 i m\'e1i nh\'e9, trong \u273 \'f3 c\'f2n h\u417 n ch\u7909 c c\'e1i n\u7919 a \u273 \u7845 y. Khi\u7871 p c\'e1i kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n n\'e0y \u273 \u7875  trong \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0m g\'ec m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ph\uc0\u7909 c v\u7909  bao nhi\'eau ng\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  s\u7861 n \u7903  \u273 \u7845 y ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7913 t \u273 \u7889 ng bao cao su l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c li\u7871 m l\'e1p ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i. \u272 \u7871 n g\u7847 n con c\u7863 c th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh th\u7893 i ph\'f9 ph\'f9 v\'e0o hai h\'f2n d\'e1i b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 m t\u7915  d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'f3 l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c li\u7871 m th\u7871  n\'e0y t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m, d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n th\u7853 t to ra m\'e0 \u273 \u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh li\u7871 m l\'e1p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi hai c\'e1i h\'f2n d\'e1i c\'f3 v\uc0\u7867  s\u259 n s\u259 n l\u7841 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m l\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'e2n c\u7863 c m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7881  m\'fat m\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n d\'f9ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i \u273 \u7849 y qua \u273 \u7849 y l\u7841 i cho con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng h\u417 n. M\u7845 y \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng g\'e2n gu\u7889 c n\u7893 i l\'ean v\u7857 n v\u7879 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m ki\uc0\u7875 u 69 \u273 i anh..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! \u272 \u432 a l\u7891 n \u273 \'e2y anh m\'fat n\'e0o.. xem ra n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y nh\'ecn t\'f4i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7889 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  em \u273 \u7889  anh em ra n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u432 a \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y l\'e0 ra n\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i, nhi\u7873 u l\'e0 \u273 \u7857 ng kh\'e1c!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'ec kh\'ec r\u7891 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng hi\u7875 u sao v\u7899 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c em ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c g\'ec, d\'f9 li\u7871 m m\'fat m\'e3i ch\u7881  ra m\u7897 t t\'ed n\u432 \u7899 c th\'f4i, c\u7889  l\u7855 m th\'ec m\u7899 i ra th\'eam ch\u7913  v\u7899 i anh \u273 \u7909 ng v\'e0o l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 d\u7847 m d\u7873  r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 do th\'edch th\'fa. Th\'f4i nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec \u273 \u7875  anh m\'fat n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i r\u7891 i nh\u7887 ng c\'e1i m\'f4ng c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  c\'e1i l\u7891 n s\'e1t v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng t\'f4i. \'c1nh s\'e1nh tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a t\u7915  c\'e1i \u273 \'e8n h\u7855 t xu\u7889 ng l\'e0m t\'f4i nh\'ecn r\'f5 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khe l\uc0\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\'e2m \u273 en l\u7855 m r\u7891 i, nh\u7845 t l\'e0 c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n th\'ec nh\'f4 ra th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'f3 t\'ecnh c\u7843 m s\'e2u n\u7863 ng v\u7899 i t\'f4i n\'ean l\'fac n\'e0y c\'e1i l\u7891 n \u273 \u7847 y n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 r\uc0\u7881  ra l\'e0m hai c\'e1i m\'e9p \u273 en nh\u7851 y b\'f3ng h\u7871 t c\u7843  l\'ean. C\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n m\u7903  r\u7897 ng ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 ang ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\'e9o hai c\'e1i m\'f4ng xu\uc0\u7889 ng t\'f4i m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895  m\'e0 ngo\'e1y. Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec h\'e1 to mi\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m s\'e1t c\u7843  th\'e2n c\u7863 c m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\uc0\u7871 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y c\'e1i t\'f4i \u273 \'fat lu\'f4n hai ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n ngo\'e1y tr\'f2n m\'e0 n\'f3i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\'fat t\u7897 p t\u7897 p con c\u7863 c m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3.. s\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m ch\u7913  anh \u417 i.. \u273 \'e3 l\u7855 m \u7845 y.. h\'edch h\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'ea h\uc0\u7871 t c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i ra \u7845 y.. \u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\'f4n h\'edch h\'edch.. b\u7911 n r\u7911 n c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\u417  \'e0? Th\u7871  v\u7915 a m\'fat v\u7915 a ngo\'e1y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i x\'f5a m\'e1i t\'f3c c\u7911 a m\'ecnh sang m\u7897 t b\'ean ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c ng\u7853 m l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c m\'e0 m\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai li\u7871 m m\'fat ch\'e1n th\'ec thay \u273 \u7893 i t\u432  th\u7871 , t\'f4i n\u7857 m tr\'ean c\'f2n Qu\u7923 nh n\u7857 m d\u432 \u7899 i ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c m\'e0 m\'fat nhau. M\u7897 t l\'fac sau th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh ng\uc0\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\'f2n em n\u7857 m d\u7883 ch l\'ean \u273 \u7875  em m\'fat cho nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch ki\uc0\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec th\'edch ch\uc0\u7913  sao.. ki\u7875 u \u273 \'f3 anh nh\u7845 p v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng em th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u432 \u7901 n l\'ean r\u7891 i t\'f4i ch\u7889 ng tay v\'e0o th\'e0nh gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i nh\u7845 p nh\u7893 m cho con c\u7863 c th\'f2 ra th\u7909 t v\'e0o c\'e1i mi\u7879 ng xinh x\u7855 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh tr\u432 \u7901 n xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i m\u7897 t l\'fac r\u7891 i h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng th\u7853 t to ra \u273 \u7875  cho t\'f4i nh\u7845 p con c\u7863 c v\'e0o \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u432 a tay l\'ean m\'e2n m\'ea xoa b\'f3p c\u7863 p m\'f4ng \u273 ang \u273 ung \u273 \u432 a c\u7911 a t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c v\'e0o ng\u7853 p s\'e2u t\u7853 n h\u7885 ng nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh v\u7851 n say m\'ea m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t. C\'e1i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u7845 m n\'f3ng c\u7911 a \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i ch\'e0 s\'e1t m\u7841 nh l\'ean c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c khi\u7871 n t\'f4i kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 R\'fat con c\uc0\u7863 c ra th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n t\'f4i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a kh\'e9o b\u7855 n ra m\u7845 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7855 n ra th\'ec em u\u7889 ng ch\u7913  c\'f3 sao \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i anh l\'e0 anh kh\'f4ng th\'edch xu\uc0\u7845 t ngay h\'ec h\'ec, mu\u7889 n xu\u7845 t th\'ec xu\u7845 t lu\'f4n v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895  n\'e0y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  lu\'f4n v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh. Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec th\'e8m con c\u7863 c t\'f4i l\u7855 m, tuy r\'fat ra kh\u7887 i mi\u7879 ng r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n ch\u7891 m l\u7845 y m\'e0 li\u7871 p l\'e1p hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'fd n\uc0\u7919 a ki\u7875 u g\'ec em ch\u7859 ng cho, c\u7913  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 anh th\'edch!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch c\uc0\u361 ng ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7875  cho em li\u7871 m n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \'e0nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y cho Qu\u7923 nh m\'e2n m\'ea li\u7871 m l\'e1p con c\u7863 c m\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra \u273 \u7875  t\'f4i \u273 \'fat con c\u7863 c v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao, c\u7843 m x\'fac mu\u7889 n s\u7903  h\u7919 u c\'e1i th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh tr\u7895 i d\u7853 y. N\'f3 khi\u7871 n t\'f4i h\u7915 ng h\u7921 c kh\'ed th\u7871 , nh\u7845 p ph\'e1t n\'e0o l\'e0 con c\u7863 c c\u7855 m ng\u7853 p v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ph\'e1t \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\uc0\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra r\u7891 i qu\u7863 p hai khu\u7927 u ch\'e2n v\'e0o \u273 \'f9i t\'f4i Qu\u7923 nh c\u7889  \u432 \u7905 n l\'ean cho c\'e1i con c\u7863 c v\'e0o \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\'e2u h\u417 n r\u7891 i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i vu\u7889 t ve m\'e1 t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y.. v\'e0o s\'e2u nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 anh \u417 i\'85 l\u7891 n em nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a \u273 \u7883 t v\u7915 a th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n v\u7915 a tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 .. nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.. c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng d\'e2m nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'e2m th\'ec m\uc0\u7899 i s\u432 \u7899 ng ..l\u7891 n em ch\u7855 c l\'e0 r\u7897 ng l\u7855 m r\u7891 i h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng.. \u273 \u7883 t v\u7851 n s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng th\'ec anh l\'e0m m\u7841 nh \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7841 nh th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a\'85 em c\'f3 s\u432 \u7899 ng kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913 ..n\u432 \u7899 c nhi\u7873 u m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u r\'ean v\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c ra nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m r\u7891 i. \u272 \u7883 t ki\u7875 u truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng th\'eam m\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a th\'ec t\'f4i ch\u7891 m ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean, v\u7855 t hai ch\'e2n l\'ean c\u7893  r\u7891 i \u273 u ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7873  ph\'eda tr\u432 \u7899 c.\
