\cf2 \cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1, h\'e1 h\u7889 c m\u7891 m th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh \uc0\u417 i..ki\u7875 u n\'e0y th\'ec anh.. nh\u7845 p t\u7915  t\u7915  th\'f4i nh\'e9.. r\'fat g\u7847 n ra r\u7891 i c\u7855 m v\'e0o.. nh\u432  th\u7871  s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m anh \u7841 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 L\'e0m y nh\uc0\u432  l\u7901 i c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh tu\'f4n ra tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a. \u272 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh ph\'eda d\u432 \u7899 i con c\u7863 c b\u7871 t l\u7841 i v\u7899 i nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng t\'f4i th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'ean \uc0\u273 \u7881 nh r\u7891 i h\u7843  em y\'eau?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'edch.. l\'ean hai l\uc0\u7847 n r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y.. t\u7841 i anh \u7845 y.. c\u7913  l\'e0m em s\u432 \u7899 ng th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? D\u7841 o n\'e0y m\'ecnh c\u361 ng kh\u7887 e ph\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 , l\'e0m cho em ra hai l\u7847 n r\u7891 i m\'e0 ch\u432 a xu\u7845 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  kh\u7887 e th\u7853 t, kh\'e9o \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7855 c l\'e0 qu\u7847 n v\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i kh\'f4ng \u273 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\'f4n nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m g\'ec \uc0\u273 \u7871 n n\u7895 i \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai \uc0\u273 \u7913 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n, t\'f4i v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  con c\u7863 c c\u7855 m s\'e2u v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n ch\u432 a th\'e8m r\'fat ra. \u272 \u7907 i m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng l\u7841 i \u273 \u7875  doggy r\u7891 i t\'f4i phun \u7847 m \u7847 m tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o l\u7895  l\u7891 n sau \u273 \'f3i \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y ra gh\u7871  m\'e0 th\u7903 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng, day day c\'e1i h\u7897 t le r\u7891 i banh c\'e1i m\'e9p th\u7891 n th\'e2m \u273 en c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra cho tinh tr\'f9ng trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n nh\u7887  t\u7887 ng t\u7887 ng xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 xu\u7845 t v\'e0o th\'ec d\u7877  c\'f3 b\u7847 u l\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? T\'ednh xin anh m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  ! Bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i d\u7841 i c\u7843  m\u7863 t \u273 i b\u7843 o;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Xin anh c\'f3 m\'e0 anh ch\uc0\u7871 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! M\u7899 i n\'f3i th\u7871  th\'f4i m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 s\u7907  r\u7891 i. Y\'ean t\'e2m \u273 i, em ch\u432 a mu\u7889 n c\'f3 con \u273 \'e2u, m\'e0 xin c\u7911 a anh xong th\'ec em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7875  cho anh bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  \'e1? Bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c mai kia h\u7913 ng l\u7841 i v\u7873  v\u7913 t cho anh b\u7843 o. Con anh \u273 \u7845 y anh nu\'f4i \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'fac kh\'edch r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n b\'ean ng\u7891 i l\'ean \u273 \'f9i t\'f4i, c\u7843  hai l\u7841 i n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i nhau v\'e0 n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n v\u7873  v\u7845 n \u273 \u7873  l\'e0m t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n t\'f4i v\u7915 a v\'ea v\'ea c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y th\uc0\u7871  m\u7845 y \'f4ng h\'f4m nay c\'f3 xu\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng? Anh b\u7855 t g\u7863 p l\'e2u th\u7871  m\'e0 m\u7895 i \'f4ng c\'f3 hai l\u7847 n th\'f4i \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec hai l\uc0\u7847 n th\'f4i ch\u7913  c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, \u273 \u7845 y l\'e0 u\u7889 ng thu\u7889 c v\'e0o r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y, c\'e1i ki\u7875 u s\u7871 p v\u259 n ph\'f2ng th\u7871 , th\u7875  thao th\'ec \'edt l\'e0m sao m\'e0 nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng b\uc0\u7857 ng anh h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7857 ng l\'e0m sao \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, v\u7915 a kh\'f4ng tr\u7867  b\u7857 ng l\u7841 i c\'f2n y\u7871 u h\u417 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Th\u7871  th\'edch kh\u7887 e hay th\'edch y\u7871 u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh h\uc0\u7887 i bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i th\u7853 t, ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 ai th\'edch y\u7871 u c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n v\u7899 i nhau th\'eam m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh k\u7875  hai \'f4ng \u7845 y l\'e0m v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh th\u7871  n\'e0o. L\'fac \u7903  trong \'f4 t\'f4 th\'ec m\u7897 t trong hai \'f4ng \u273 \'e3 th\'f2 tay v\'e0o trong v\'e1y Qu\u7923 nh m\'e0 m\'f3c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 K\uc0\u7875  h\u7871 t v\u7873  hai c\'e1i \'f4ng s\u7871 p \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh k\u7875  ti\u7871 p v\u7873  nh\u7919 ng l\u7847 n th\'e1c lo\u7841 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh. T\'f4i kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  l\'e0 sau m\u7845 y n\u259 m kh\'f4ng c\'f2n y\'eau t\'f4i Qu\u7923 nh c\'f2n th\'e1c lo\u7841 n \u273 \u7871 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n g\u7847 n n\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a tay xu\u7889 ng m\'e2n m\'ea con c\u7863 c. T\'f4i th\'ec vu\u7889 t ve c\'e1i l\u7891 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\u7841 i th\'e8m r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh th\'ec kh\'e1c g\'ec em m\'e0 c\'f2n b\uc0\u7843 o em!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec t\'ed n\u7919 a cho anh l\'e0m v\u7899 i l\u7895  nh\u7883  nh\'e9. \'c0 hai \'f4ng \u7845 y c\u361 ng l\'e0m v\u7899 i l\u7895  nh\u7883  \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\uc0\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 c\u7843  hai ch\u7913 , c\'f2n tranh nhau \u7845 y, em th\u7889 n nh\u7845 t l\'e0 qu\u7843  m\u7897 t \'f4ng c\u7855 m v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n m\u7897 t \'f4ng c\u7855 m v\'e0o l\u7895  nh\u7883  \u7845 y, t\'ea kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\'f4n. N\'f3 th\u7889 n th\u7889 n n\u7919 a kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u417 i l\'e0 kh\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t g\'f9 th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  ch\u432 a g\u7841  v\u7907  s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i l\'e0m ki\u7875 u \u273 \'f3 bao gi\u7901  \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a! Ngoan l\u7855 m, bi\u7871 t g\'ec \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh th\u7845 y t\'f4i b\u7843 o ngoan th\'ec ngu\'fdt d\'e0i m\u7897 t c\'e1i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Em n\'e0o \u7903  trong tay anh m\'e0 anh ch\u7859 ng \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o \u273 \u7871 n n\u417 i \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7889 n c\'f2n b\'e0y \u273 \u7863 t l\'e0 ngoan l\u7855 m v\u7899 i ch\u7843  ngoan v\u7915 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec anh c\'f3 \uc0\u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o em \u273 \u7871 n th\u7871  n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y! Y\'eau nhau c\'f3 hai n\u259 m th\'f4i m\'e0 c\'f2n th\u7871  n\u7919 a c\'f2n g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i lu\'f4n xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t vu\u7889 t ve r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'fat con c\u7863 c v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng m\'fat v\'e0 chi\u7873 u chu\u7897 ng t\'f4i nh\u432  m\u7897 t \'f4ng ho\'e0ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7891 m m\'f4ng quay l\u7841 i ng\u7891 i l\'ean nh\'fan nh\'fan m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em th\'edch c\uc0\u432 \u7905 i ng\u7921 a ki\u7875 u n\'e0y m\u7897 t l\'fac r\u7891 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng anh doggy em nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7915 a doggy c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m v\uc0\u7899 i l\u7895  nh\u7883  \u7845 y! Em th\'edch l\'e0m th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u k\u7879  cho Qu\u7923 nh nh\'fan ph\u7847 m ph\u7853 p xu\u7889 ng con c\u7863 c, t\'f4i ch\u7881  v\'f2ng tay ra m\'e0 \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa xoa xoa b\'f3p b\'f3p.\cb1 \
\cb3 Khi n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n tu\'f4n ra ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt th\'e2m \u273 en \u7903  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng ng\u7891 i ch\u7891 m h\u7895 m r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a tay banh c\'e1i khe m\'f4ng cho l\u7895  \u273 \'edt l\u7897  ra m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'fat v\'e0o \u273 i anh..em th\'e8m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  anh \u273 i bao \u273 \'e3 ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! \u272 \u7875  em \u273 eo bao cho.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh x\'e9 c\'e1i bao r\u7891 i cho v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng m\'ecnh. T\'f4i th\u7845 y th\u7871  h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ph\uc0\u7843 i k\u7865 o cao su \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 \u259 n!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! \uc0\u272 \u7875  em \u273 eo bao b\u7857 ng mi\u7879 ng cho anh xem.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh l\u7841 i ch\'fai \u273 \u7871 n, ng\u7853 m con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i kh\'e9o l\'e9o cho c\'e1i bao v\'e0o \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c r\u7891 i d\'f9ng m\'f4i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7875  tu\u7889 t cho n\'f3 \'f4m kh\'edt l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c. C\'f4ng nh\u7853 n v\u7899 i nh\u7919 ng k\u297  thu\u7853 t th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec kh\u7889 i anh m\'ea m\u7879 t v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng \u273 \'fang.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 eo bao xong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh quay l\u7841 i, s\u7861 n s\'e0ng \u273 \u7875  cho t\'f4i \u273 \'fat con c\u7863 c v\'e0o l\u7895  \u273 \'edt. Nh\'ecn c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt m\u7899 i ch\u7881  c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n th\'f4i n\'ean t\'f4i nh\u7893  lu\'f4n \'edt n\u432 \u7899 c b\u7885 t v\'e0o \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c ch\'e0 ch\'e0 m\'e0 \u273 \'fat v\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7895  \u273 \'edt c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh qu\'e1 quen thu\u7897 c v\u7899 i ki\u7875 u l\'e0m n\'e0y r\u7891 i n\'ean ch\u7859 ng kh\'f3 kh\u259 n g\'ec \u273 \u7875  c\'e1i con c\u7863 c chui v\'e0o c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7851 n s\u7907  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 au n\'ean c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c t\'e1ch ra chui v\'e0o b\'ean trong th\'ec t\'f4i d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 \uc0\u273 au kh\'f4ng em?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh cong c\'e1i h\'f4ng ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng l\'ean cao h\u417 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng.. em quen r\uc0\u7891 i m\'e0.. \u7845 n m\u7841 nh s\'e2u n\u7919 a \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh n\'f3i quen nh\u432 ng t\'f4i v\u7851 n ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u7845 n m\u7841 nh v\'e0o. C\u7913  t\u7915  t\u7915  cho con c\u7863 c v\'e0o th\u7853 t s\'e2u, \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nahsnh ch\u7841 m v\'e0o m\'f4ng r\u7891 i t\'f4i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7895  \u273 \'edt em kh\'edt qu\'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ngo\'e1i l\u7841 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7895  \u273 \'edt ai m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng kh\'edt.. ki\u7875 u n\'e0y ch\u7855 c nh\u7845 p m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i \'e0o \'e0o phun ra..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec ch\uc0\u7855 c v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7851 n s\u7907  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 au n\'ean nh\u7845 p nh\u7865  nh\u7865  cho \u273 \u7871 n Khi qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o t\'f4i nh\u7845 p m\u7841 nh l\'ean th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\'e0 h\'ec h\u7909 c \u273 \u7849 y cho con c\u7863 c th\u7909 t s\'e2u v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  th\'e2m \u273 en.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7847 n \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m v\u7899 i c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y t\'f4i s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m. C\'e0ng nh\u7845 p th\'ec n\'f3 c\'e0ng th\'edt l\u7841 i th\u7853 t s\'e2u. T\'f4i v\u7895  nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'ean c\'e1i b\u7901  m\'f4ng tr\'f2n l\u7859 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i x\u432 a sao kh\'f4ng cho anh l\'e0m ki\u7875 u n\'e0y nh\u7881 ? L\'e0m\'85 ki\u7875 u n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 c\'f2n s\u432 \u7899 ng ph\'e1t \u273 i\'ean l\'ean \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec! Em c\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t.. nh\u432 ng ki\u7875 u n\'e0y \u273 \'e3 \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? H\u7891 i x\u432 a em s\u7907  v\u7899 i c\'f3 bi\u7871 t l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ki\u7875 u n\'e0y \u273 \'e2u.. m\u7841 nh m\u7841 nh n\u7919 a l\'ean \u273 i anh ..em s\u432 \u7899 ng anh \u417 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7841 nh th\'eam m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u7919 a nh\u432 ng do c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt n\'f3 kh\'edt n\'ean t\'f4i s\u7889  g\u7855 ng nh\u7845 p m\'e0 kh\'f4ng nh\u7845 p nhanh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7891  h\'f4i m\u7891  k\'ea b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7913 a ra nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i t\'f4i phun \u7847 m \u7847 m tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o trong c\'e1i bao r\u7891 i m\u7899 i r\'fat kh\u7887 i c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 n\u7857 m \u432 \u7901 n xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng, c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i gi\u7853 t gi\u7853 t l\'ean t\'ea d\u7841 i v\'ec \u273 \'e3 r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1 anh \u417 i..em l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh\'85 l\u7891 n em l\u7841 i ra n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng nh\'ecn c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh c\'f4ng nh\u7853 n l\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n l\u7841 i ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n. R\'fat c\'e1i bao ra r\u7891 i v\u7913 t v\'e0o b\u7891 n c\u7847 u sau \u273 \'f3 ra ng\u7891 i ngh\u7881 . Qu\u7923 nh n\u7857 m c\u7841 nh t\'f4i th\u7903  nh\u7865  nh\u7865  r\u7891 i quay sang ngh\u7883 ch ng\u7907 m con c\u259 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  c\u361 ng mu\u7897 n r\u7891 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2y ng\u7911  v\u7899 i em lu\'f4n mai tr\u7843  ph\'f2ng nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! C\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i nhau. Qu\u7923 nh k\u7875  nhi\u7873 u chuy\u7879 n l\u7855 m, c\'f3 l\u7869  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m g\'e1i bao r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  ho\'e0n c\u7843 nh thay \u273 \u7893 i nhanh \u273 \u7871 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y, t\u7915  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i con g\'e1i ngoan ngo\'e3n hi\u7873 n hi\u7873 n m\'e0 gi\u7901  \u273 \'e2y Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i th\'e0nh nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y.\
