\cf2 \cb3 T\'e2m s\uc0\u7921  \u273 \u7871 n mu\u7897 n th\'ec c\u7843  hai ng\u7911 . S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau t\'f4i chia tay Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i \u273 i l\'e0m c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c. M\u7897 t tu\u7847 n sau \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i ch\u7859 ng g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh n\u7919 a v\'ec c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c kh\'e1 nhi\u7873 u v\'e0 c\u361 ng h\u7889 i h\u7853 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 n\'ean g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n quan t\'e2m Huy\u7873 n nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Cu\uc0\u7889 i tu\u7847 n Huy\u7873 n v\u7873  t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7863 t s\u7861 n m\u7897 t b\'e0n ti\u7879 c cho Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i. C\u7843  hai ng\u7891 i c\'f9ng \u259 n u\u7889 ng n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n. Huy\u7873 n tr\'f4ng \u273 \'e3 tr\u7867  d\u432 \u7899 i \'e1nh n\u7871 n lung linh Huy\u7873 n c\'e0ng tr\u7867  h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nh\'e2m nhi ch\'fat r\uc0\u432 \u7907 u vang Huy\u7873 n h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7855 ng v\u7907  \u7903  nh\'e0 c\'f3 l\'e9ng ph\'e9ng v\u7899 i ai kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c b\'f9 \u273 \u7847 u c\'f2n l\'e9ng ph\'e9ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i ai1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nghi l\uc0\u7855 m nh\'e9, c\'e1i m\u7863 t th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng tin \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng tin \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7903  nh\'e0 m\'e0 gi\u7919  nh\'e9 xem c\'f3 ph\u7843 i kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i k\u7875  chuy\u7879 n chuy\u7871 n \u273 i t\u7853 p hu\u7845 n. Tr\'ean tr\u7901 i d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7845 t, Huy\u7873 n h\'f2a \u273 \u7891 ng n\'ean nhi\u7873 u ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7881  d\u7851 n l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u258 n u\u7889 ng \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u t\u7889 i th\'ec t\'f4i nh\'e1y m\u7855 t b\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y t\uc0\u7889 i ph\u7843 i \u273 \u7873 n b\'f9 cho anh \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nheo m\u7855 t r\u7891 i c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7891 ng th\u7901 i \u273 \u432 a tay l\'ean v\'e9o nh\u7865  nh\u7865  m\'e1 r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7873 n c\'e1i g\'ec n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \u7873 n c\'e1i g\'ec r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec. H\u417 n m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai v\'e3 l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'ecn c\'e1i v\u7867  m\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea c\u7911 a t\'f4i th\'ec mu\u7889 n tr\'eau l\u7855 m. V\'e9n m\u7845 y l\u7885 n t\'f3c t\u417  l\'ean r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \u7873 n cho ch\u7891 ng l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng m\'e0 h\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ph\uc0\u7909 ng ph\u7883 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c, c\u7843  tu\u7847 n r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'ecn v\u7867  m\u7863 t c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\'e0ng c\u432 \u7901 i to h\u417 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  ch\u7891 ng c\'f3 mu\u7889 n v\u432 \u7907 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7887  kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u th\'edch v\u432 \u7907 t th\'ec v\u7907  cho v\u432 \u7907 t tho\u7843 i m\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o th\u7871  t\'f4i xua tay n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec th\'f4i, h\'ec h\'ec.. v\u432 \u7907 t \u273 \'e8n \u273 \u7887  l\'e0 d\u7877  b\u7883  ph\u7841 t l\u7855 m, m\'e0 kinh ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u7845 y, th\'f4i nh\u7883 n m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n n\u7919 a h\'ec h\'ec. C\u7889  g\u7855 ng v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'fac kh\'edch n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f3 ph\u7843 i ngoan kh\'f4ng nh\u432 ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng c\u7847 n ph\u7843 i m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u, ba b\u7889 n ng\'e0y n\u7919 a l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  th\'ec ba b\u7889 n ng\'e0y n\u7919 a nh\u432 ng m\'e0 l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y th\'ec l\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u ra n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7881 . Kh\'e9o h\u7841 n h\'e1n m\u7845 t th\'f4i m\'e0 mu\u7889 n c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c th\'ec ph\u7843 i t\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i tr\'eau Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec Huy\u7873 n nh\'e9o t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\'f5 \u273 au r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u m\uc0\u7899 i c\'f3 kh\'e1i ni\u7879 m kh\'f4ng c\'f3 n\u432 \u7899 c nh\'e9. Th\u7871  nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7875  l\'e0m g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  u\u7889 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7913  c\'e1i m\u361 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\'ean r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i m\uc0\u7863 t d\'e2m \u273 \'ea kh\'f4ng l\u7851 n v\'e0o \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai v\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng s\u7855 p c\u432 \u7899 i c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'f9a v\u7899 i nhau r\u7891 i \u273 i xem phim. T\u7889 i v\u7873  t\'f4i \'f4m l\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  chuy\u7879 n c\u432 \u7899 i h\u7887 i n\'e0y n\u7885  \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n khuya th\'ec c\u417 n d\u7909 c v\u7885 ng n\u7893 i l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i c\'f3 v\u7867  n\'f3ng n\'f3ng th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7847 n v\u7907  l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec kh\'f4ng ch\uc0\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y, ng\u7917 i c\'e1i m\'f9i da th\u7883 t c\u7911 a v\u7907  l\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u273 \'e8 v\u7907  ra r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 th\uc0\u7853 t kh\'f4ng hay l\'e0 c\u7913  ng\u7917 i m\'f9i em n\'e0o c\u361 ng mu\u7889 n \u273 \'e8 em \u7845 y ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \'f3 th\'ec c\u361 ng c\'f3 nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 \'e8 v\u7907  ra l\'e0 th\'edch nh\u7845 t h\'ec h\'ec. Ti\u7871 c l\'e0 ph\u7843 i nh\u7883 n \u273 \'f3i th\'eam v\'e0i bu\u7893 i n\u7919 a r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u7883 n \u273 \'f3i r\u7891 i \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7899 i s\u432 \u7899 ng ch\u7913 , c\u7913  ph\u7843 i th\'e8m thu\u7891 ng \u259 n m\u7899 i ngon nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 s\u7901  m\'f3 con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i, mi\u7879 ng th\'ec kh\u7869  kh\u7869  h\'f4n l\'ean m\'e1 t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Xem n\'f3 c\uc0\u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 b\u7843 o l\'e0 th\'e8m n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\'e1 c\uc0\u7913 ng \u7845 y ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n vu\u7889 t nh\u7865  nh\u7865  cho c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c l\u7897  ra c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c r\u7891 i l\u7845 y ng\'f3n c\'e1i v\'ea v\'ea l\'ean m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n l\'e0 c\u7913 ng th\u7853 t, ch\u7855 c l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ch\u7885 c v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i v\u7907  l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea qu\'e1 \u273 i m\u7845 t th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7883 nh n\'f3i l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ch\u7885 c l\u7855 m th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u7871  v\u7907  gi\'fap ch\u7891 ng gi\u7843 i t\u7887 a nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\u7857 ng quy t\u7855 c b\'e0n tay ph\u7843 i hay quy t\u7855 c b\'e0n tay tr\'e1i th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7843  hai h\'ec h\'ec, th\u7871  b\u7857 ng mi\u7879 ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng? \u272 \u7875  em c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat cho nh\'e9. M\'e0 m\u7845 y h\'f4m \u273 i th\u7921 c t\u7853 p to\'e0n th\u7845 y m\u7845 y b\'e0 ch\u7883  b\u7843 o BJ n\'e0y n\u7885  m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng hi\u7875 u g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0 h\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 BJ l\'e0 d\'f9ng mi\uc0\u7879 ng \u7845 y, em m\'fat ch\'e1n cho anh r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec l\'fac \uc0\u273 \u7847 u kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u m\'e3i v\u7873  sau m\u7899 i hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. M\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y d\'e2m ng\u7847 m ra ph\u7871 t, h\u7847 u nh\u432  b\'e0 n\'e0o c\u361 ng l\'e9ng ph\'e9ng kh\'f4ng ch\u7881  v\u7899 i ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? Th\u7871  em c\'f3 h\u7885 c m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i xin ki\uc0\u7871 u, kh\'f4ng quen h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong r\uc0\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m c\'fai xu\u7889 ng v\u7841 ch con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i ra. T\'f4i nh\u7845 c nh\u7865  m\'f4ng l\'ean \u273 \u7875  Huy\u7873 n k\'e9o qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng cho d\u7877 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean th\'ec Huy\u7873 n tr\u432 \u7901 n nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng xu\u7889 ng g\u7889 i \u273 \u7847 u tr\'ean b\u7909 ng r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\'f9ng l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh m\'e0 li\u7871 m l\'e1p v\'f2ng quanh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n d\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 kh\'f4ng thu\u7847 n th\u7909 c chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p nh\u432  Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng ch\'ednh v\'ec th\u7871  l\'e0m cho t\'f4i th\u7845 y th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7843 o c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n d\u7885 c t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c xu\u7889 ng t\u7853 n b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i g\u7847 n hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n m\u7899 i ng\u7853 m v\'e0o m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lim dim \uc0\u273 \'f4i m\u7855 t t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng t\u7915 ng h\u417 i th\u7903  \u7845 m \'e1p ph\u7843  v\'e0o g\u7889 c c\u7863 c t\'f4i cong ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean v\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng. Huy\u7873 n v\u7915 a m\'fat v\u7915 a s\u7909 c con c\u7863 c m\u7841 nh h\u417 n r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 qu\'e1 h\u7843  ch\u7891 ng y\'eau? N\'f3 c\u7913 ng h\u7871 t c\u7905  r\u7891 i n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 S\uc0\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m v\u7907  \u7841 .. v\u7907  m\'fat th\'edch th\u7871 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i m\'e3n nguy\u7879 n v\'ec l\'e0m cho t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y th\u7887 a m\'e3n. C\'fai xu\u7889 ng li\u7871 m l\'e1m ch\'e1n ch\'ea r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n ti\u7871 n l\'ean b\'fa l\u7845 y \u273 \u7847 u t\'ed c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i l\u7841 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat hai h\'f2n d\'e1i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao l\'fac n\'e0y t\'f4i th\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p h\u7859 n n\'ean h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ai ch\uc0\u7881  v\u7907  m\'e0 v\u7907  li\u7871 m gi\u7887 i th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ng\u7849 ng l\'ean tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec m\uc0\u7845 y ch\u7883  \u273 i t\u7853 p hu\u7845 n c\'f9ng em th\'f4i, m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y n\'f3i em \u7903  ngo\'e0i h\'f3ng h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y c\'f2n ch\u7881  g\'ec n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7881  nhi\u7873 u c\'e1i l\u7855 m..nh\u432 ng nh\u7899  \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \'e2u em l\'e0m \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7845 y cho ch\u7891 ng s\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i xong Huy\u7873 n ti\u7871 p t\u7909 c c\'fai xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 a d\u7885 c c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh t\u7915  \u7903  hai h\'f2n d\'e1i l\'ean c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c r\u7891 i l\u7841 i qu\'e9t nh\u7865  sang hai \u273 \'f9i.\cb1 \
\cb3 L\'e0m \uc0\u273 i l\'e0m l\u7841 i \u273 \u7871 n khi con c\u7863 c tr\u417 n nh\u7851 y th\'ec Huy\u7873 n ng\u7853 m c\u7843  th\'e2n c\u7863 c m\'e0 m\'fat. T\'f4i run run kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e8n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7907 ..\u417 i..t\'ed n\u7919 a\'85 ch\u7891 ng xu\u7845 t ra \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ng\u7849 ng l\'ean b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec v\uc0\u7907  u\u7889 ng lu\'f4n cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng v\u7907  kinh c\'e1i ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y l\u7855 m m\'e0? Sao h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i th\'edch u\u7889 ng v\u7853 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7845 y b\'e0 ch\u7883  \u7845 y b\u7843 o u\u7889 ng \u273 \u7865 p da.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f3 tay v\uc0\u7899 i m\u7845 y b\'e0 c\'f3 ch\u7891 ng s\u7891 n s\u7891 n \u7903  ch\u7895  l\'e0m c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n, t\'f4i \u273 \'e0nh \u273 \u7875  cho Huy\u7873 n m\'fat r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n khi kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a th\'ec b\u7855 n \'e0o \'e0o v\'e0o c\'e1i mi\u7879 ng xinh x\u7855 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n chu m\'f4i l\u7841 i m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t r\u7891 i \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m v\'f2ng quanh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c n\u7919 a. V\u7915 a li\u7871 m xong t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\'f3 c\'f2n kinh n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7843 m th\u7845 y v\u7851 n kinh nh\u432 ng d\u7847 n d\u7847 n quen h\'ec h\'ec. Kh\'e9o m\'e0 em nghi\u7879 n l\'e0 em u\u7889 ng su\u7889 t ng\'e0y \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 U\uc0\u7889 ng su\u7889 t ng\'e0y sao m\'e0 s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t k\u7883 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec em b\uc0\u7891 i b\u7893  cho s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t k\u7883 p ch\u7913  sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n \'e2u y\u7871 m nh\'ecn t\'f4i r\u7891 i c\u7913  m\'fat con c\u7863 c cho \u273 \u7871 n khi n\'f3 m\u7873 m o\u7863 t sang m\u7897 t b\'ean. Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y r\u7891 i kh\u7869  v\'e0o nh\'e0 v\u7873  sinh r\u7917 a c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a m\'ecnh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho h\uc0\u7871 t n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n \u273 i t\'ed n\u7919 a anh ph\u7843 i cho n\'f3 ch\u7843 y ra \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7845 y th\'ec c\'f2n ph\u7843 i xem c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u kh\'f4ng n\u7919 a ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\'e1 nhi\uc0\u7873 u h\u417 n, d\u7847 n d\u7847 n em h\u417 i b\u7883  d\'e2m \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7907 i m\u7897 t l\'fac sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i \u273 \'e8 Huy\u7873 n ra li\u7871 m l\u7891 n v\'e0 hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng l\u7841 i qu\u7879 n v\'e0o nhau. \'c2n \'e1i \u273 \u7871 n mu\u7897 n th\'ec t\'f4i xu\u7845 t h\u7871 t tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n th\'eam m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a r\u7891 i c\u7843  hai \u273 i ng\u7911 .\
