\cf2 \cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t th\'e1ng sau\'85\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Hai ch\'fang t\'f4i chu\uc0\u7849 n b\u7883  l\u7877  c\u432 \u7899 i r\u7891 i t\u7893  ch\u7913 c m\u7901 i b\u7841 n b\'e8. T\'f4i ph\'e2n v\'e2n kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t c\'f3 n\'ean m\u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng b\'e8n h\u7887 i Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y l\uc0\u7877  c\u432 \u7899 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh c\'f3 m\u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n vui v\u7867  nh\'ed nh\u7843 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, n\'ean m\u7901 i ch\u7913 . Cho ch\u7883  \u7845 y b\u7887  l\u7905  m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7891 ng th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec b\u7843 o l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! C\'f2n anh th\'ec cho xem c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f2n xinh h\u417 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'f4m t\uc0\u7893  ch\u7913 c \u273 \'e1m c\u432 \u7899 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng \u273 \u7871 n, c\u7863 p k\'e8 v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0 m\u7897 t c\u7853 u thanh ni\'ean kh\'e1 tr\u7867 . T\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c k\'e9m ch\'fang t\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n g\u7847 n ch\u7909 c tu\u7893 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ch\'fac ph\'fac cho v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i ra b\'e0n ti\u7879 c. B\u7889  m\u7865  t\'f4i d\u297  nhi\'ean bi\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean c\u361 ng m\u7901 i ch\'e0o nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7899 i xong hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng \u273 i tr\u259 ng m\u7853 t, \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 chu\u7895 i ng\'e0y c\'f3 th\u7875  n\'f3i l\'e0 t\'f4i v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m t\'ecnh hoang d\u7841 i v\u7899 i nhau nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7915  \u273 \u7891 i th\'f4ng xanh m\u432 \u7899 t tr\'ean \u272 \'e0 L\u7841 t r\u7891 i b\'e3i c\'e1t tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a \u7903  Nha Trang. Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i \u273 \'e0o t\u7841 o n\'ean c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng bi\u7871 t chi\u7873 u ch\u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\'fac c\u7843  hai \u273 i t\u7855 m bi\u7875 n v\u7873  l\'e0 Huy\u7873 n k\'e9o lu\'f4n c\'e1i qu\u7847 n c\u7911 a t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 m\'fat con c\u7863 c v\'ec th\'e8m thu\u7891 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 i tr\u259 ng m\u7853 t v\u7873  t\'f4i \'edt khi g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n h\u7887 i th\u259 m Qu\u7923 nh l\u7855 m. Cho \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t h\'f4m \u273 i ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  cho Huy\u7873 n th\'ec g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i mua \u273 \u7891 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh trang \u273 i\u7875 m \u273 \u7853 m h\u417 n, t\u7887  v\u7867  b\u7845 t c\u7847 n \u273 \u7901 i h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c. C\'f3 l\u7869  do t\'f4i m\u7901 i \u273 i \u273 \'e1m c\u432 \u7899 i n\'ean Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 \u273 \'f4i ch\'fat th\u7845 t v\u7885 ng. H\'f4m \u273 \'f3 t\'f4i g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh v\u7899 i c\'e1i v\'e1y ng\u7855 n qu\'e1 g\u7889 i, n\u7871 u c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 nh\u7863 t \u273 \u7891  l\'e0 l\u7897  c\u7843  c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t ph\'eda b\'ean trong.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ch\uc0\u259 m t\'ednh ti\u7873 n xong m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  cho Huy\u7873 n th\'ec th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh mang hai b\u7897  v\'e1y \u273 \u7871 n. T\'f4i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i;\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7885 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  \u273 \u7865 p nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ng\u432 \u7899 c m\u7855 t l\'ean, th\u7845 y t\'f4i th\'ec nho\u7867 n mi\u7879 ng c\u432 \u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh Minh c\uc0\u361 ng \u273 i mua \u273 \u7891  \'e0? Ch\u7855 c t\u7863 ng Huy\u7873 n h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 G\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec l\'e2u l\'e2u mua t\uc0\u7863 ng v\u7907  \'edt \u273 \u7891 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m \uc0\u273 \'e1m c\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'f3, ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i c\'f9ng anh kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 Huy\u7873 n m\'e0 l\'e0 em th\'ec ch\u7855 c l\'e0 em c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh mua \u273 \u7891  th\u7871  n\'e0y nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec kh\'f4ng c\uc0\u7847 n \u273 i c\'f9ng anh mua t\u7863 ng em c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913  sao!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m th\uc0\u7871  Huy\u7873 n gi\u7853 n \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 g\'ec m\'e0 gi\uc0\u7853 n c\u417  ch\u7913 ! Coi nh\u432  b\u7841 n b\'e8 t\u7863 ng nhau m\'f3n \u273 \u7891  th\'f4i m\'e0. \u272 \u7875  anh t\'ednh ti\u7873 n cho.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'ednh ti\uc0\u7873 n xong th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7901 i t\'f4i \u273 i caf\'e9. H\u7887 i han \u273 \u7911  th\u7913  chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh h\u7887 i bao gi\u7901  ch\'fang t\'f4i \u273 \u7883 nh c\'f3 baby.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7897 t ng\u7909 m caf\'e9 r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c m\u7897 t hai n\u259 m n\u7919 a, c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c ch\u432 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u7893 n \u273 \u7883 nh l\u7855 m, m\'e0 em c\u361 ng c\u432 \u7899 i ch\u7891 ng \u273 i. Tu\u7893 i c\u361 ng ch\'edn r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'fac kh\'edch n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a l\u7915 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh n\'e0o anh \u7841 ! Ph\u7843 i l\u7915 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh n\'e0o nh\u432  anh ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m \u273 \u7847 y ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u417 n anh c\'f3 ph\u7843 i anh l\'e0 nh\u7845 t \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng v\u7899 i em l\'e0 nh\u7845 t r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 ang n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 m\'e1y kh\'e1ch g\u7885 i, t\'f4i nghe qua cu\u7897 c n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n th\'ec nh\u7853 n th\u7845 y Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7855 c c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t m\'e1 m\'ec r\u7891 i. Kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  Qu\u7923 nh l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7907 t d\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n m\u7913 c n\'e0y, t\'f4i \u273 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh nghe m\'e1y xong th\'ec n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n l\'e0 em kh\'e1c xa v\u7899 i l\'fac chia tay. Th\u7871  h\'f4m nay l\u7841 i g\u7863 p kh\'e1ch \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em ch\uc0\u7881  s\u7855 p x\u7871 p cho m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a em \u273 i th\'f4i ch\u7913  gi\'e0 r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7899 i c\'f3 hai t\'e1m.. ch\'edn m\'f9i th\'f4i ch\u7913  ch\u432 a gi\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. L\'e0m th\u7871  c\'f4ng an t\'f3m th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i gi\uc0\u7901 i.. k\u7875  c\u7843  t\'f3m cho \'edt ti\u7873 n l\'e0 l\u7841 i ra th\'f4i \u7845 y m\'e0 anh.. c\'f3 g\'ec \u273 \'e2u, th\u7871  anh c\'f3 nhu c\u7847 u kh\'f4ng em b\u7843 o m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a em \u273 \u7871 n ph\u7909 c v\u7909  nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u ch\'e1n ng\'e1n v\'ec kh\'f4ng ngh\u297  ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh t\u7915 ng y\'eau l\u7841 i th\u7871  n\'e0y. \u272 ang \u273 \u7883 nh tr\u7843  l\u7901 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 nh\uc0\u7847 m, Huy\u7873 n xinh nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec \u7903  nh\'e0 ch\u7913  l\'e0m sao m\'e0 c\'f3 h\u7913 ng \u273 i v\u7899 i em n\'e0o n\u7919 a nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u7853 t c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7875  nh\u432 ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y l\u7841 i c\'f3 h\u7913 ng \u273 i v\u7899 i em th\'ec sao.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i m\'fat nh\u7865  ly sinh t\u7889  r\u7891 i tr\u7843  l\u7901 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u297  thu\u7853 t th\'ec \u273 i\'eau luy\u7879 n r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng m\'e0 em gi\'e0 r\u7891 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n sung s\u7913 c nh\u432  m\u7845 y em kia n\u7919 a. Tu\u7893 i tr\u7867  b\'e2y gi\u7901  gi\u7887 i l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i c\uc0\u7847 n l\'e0 chuy\u7879 n nghi\u7879 p v\u7899 i t\'ecnh c\u7843 m ch\u7913  c\'e1i \u7845 y th\'ec quan tr\u7885 ng g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe \uc0\u273 \u7871 n hai ch\u7919  \'93T\'ecnh c\u7843 m\'94 th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nho\u7867 n m\u7897 t n\u7909  c\u432 \u7901 i g\u432 \u7907 ng g\u7841 o n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? Em h\u7887 i th\u7853 t anh c\'f2n t\'ecnh c\u7843 m v\u7899 i em kh\'f4ng? \'c0 m\'e0 \u273 \u7875  em t\u7921  tr\u7843  l\u7901 i nh\'e9. B\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\u7855 c ch\u7881  c\'f2n t\'ecnh c\u7843 m th\u432 \u417 ng th\u432 \u417 ng ki\u7875 u th\u432 \u417 ng h\u7841 i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n l\'e0 t\'ecnh y\'eau nh\u432  tr\u432 \u7899 c kia n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng kh\'f4ng h\u7859 n nh\u432  th\u7871  \u273 \'e2u, ch\u7919  t\'ecnh c\u7843 m n\'e0y kh\'f3 n\'f3i l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh xin ph\'e9p t\'f4i \u273 i tr\u432 \u7899 c, t\'f4i \u7903  l\u7841 i v\u7899 i n\u7895 i tr\u7889 ng v\u7855 ng trong l\'f2ng. Mang \u273 \u7891  v\u7873  t\u7863 ng Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i l\u7841 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\'e0o c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c.\
