\cf2 \cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t th\u7901 i gian sau\'85\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7873  b\u7841 t l\'ean ch\u7913 c to h\u417 n v\'e0 c\u361 ng l\'e0 l\'fac ph\u7843 i ti\u7871 p kh\'e1ch nhi\u7873 u h\u417 n, cho \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t h\'f4m c\'f3 m\u7897 t kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng k\'ed xong h\u7907 p \u273 \u7891 ng th\'ec \u273 i gi\u7843 i tr\'ed.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4ng kh\'e1ch n\'e0y h\uc0\u7887 i d\'f2 t\'f4i xem c\'f3 m\u7845 y em n\'e0o ph\u7909 c v\u7909  kh\'f4ng. T\'f4i ngh\u297  m\'e3i r\u7891 i cu\u7889 i c\'f9ng g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng ng\uc0\u7901  trong chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y Qu\u7923 nh s\'e0nh s\u7887 i l\u7855 m. L\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4i nh\u7901  v\u7843  th\u7871  n\'ean c\'f3 ph\u7847 n mu\u7889 n gi\'fap t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\'f9ng v\u7899 i m\u7845 y em \u7845 y \u273 \u7871 n cho Kh\'e1nh ch\u7885 n th\u7853 t kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  \'f4ng kh\'e1ch \u7845 y l\u7841 i k\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh. Kh\'f4ng ng\u7901  ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  t\'f4i l\u7841 i ph\u7843 i l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o l\'fac n\'e0y. Suy ngh\u297  m\u7897 t l\'fac th\u432 \u417 ng Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng t\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i \'93Th\'f4i k\u7879 , c\'f4 \u7845 y ch\u7885 n ngh\u7873  n\'e0y\'94.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7899 i v\u7883  kh\'e1ch h\'e0ng h\u7865 n \u273 i nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  th\'ec t\'f4i h\u417 i bu\u7891 n r\u7891 i l\'e1i xe v\u7873 . Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u7907 i t\'f4i \u7903  nh\'e0, th\u7845 y t\'f4i v\u7867  m\u7863 t c\'f3 v\u7867  bu\u7891 n th\'ec h\u7887 i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay \'f4ng x\'e3 c\'f3 vi\uc0\u7879 c g\'ec m\'e0 bu\u7891 n th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 m\uc0\u7845 y chuy\u7879 n \u7903  c\'f4ng ty \u7845 y m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n g\'ec kh\'f3 kh\u259 n \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng c\'f3 g\'ec kh\'f3 kh\u259 n \u273 \'e2u, n\'f3i chung h\'f4m nay k\'ed \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i h\u7907 p \u273 \u7891 ng kh\'e1 l\'e0 l\u7899 n, ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'f4ng ty th\u432 \u7903 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'f4i m\'e0 c\u361 ng x\u7883  c\'e1i m\u7863 t ra l\'e0 l\'e0m sao. Th\'f4i \u273 i t\u7855 m \u273 i em pha cho c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c cam.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i \u273 i t\u7855 m r\u7891 i ra ng\u7891 i xem ti vi v\'e0 u\u7889 ng c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c cam Huy\u7873 n pha s\u7861 n. H\'f4m nay Huy\u7873 n m\u7863 c c\'e1i \'e1o ng\u7911  m\u7887 ng tang nh\u432 ng b\'ean trong kh\'f4ng c\'f3 m\u7897 t ch\'fat \u273 \u7891  l\'f3t n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 D\'f9i d\uc0\u7909 i nh\u7865  v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y h\'f4m nay c\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 bu\u7891 n thiu th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay anh g\uc0\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u432 \u7901 m y\'eau t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  l\'e0 ai \u273 \u7845 y? Ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7863 p ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  m\'e0 bu\u7891 n th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\u7855 c l\'e0 mu\u7889 n \u7903  c\'f9ng v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i y\'eau c\u361  ch\u7913  g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i chuy\u7879 n l\'e0 th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i k\uc0\u7875  lu\'f4n cho Huy\u7873 n nghe nh\u432  v\u7853 y Huy\u7873 n h\u417 i ng\u7905  ng\'e0ng m\u7897 t l\'fac sau \u273 \'f3 r\u7891 i m\u7899 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh gi\u7901  l\'e0m th\u7871  \'e1?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Anh bi\u7871 t l\'e2u r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng c\'f3 khuy\'ean b\u7843 o nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec l\u7841 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 mu\u7889 n ch\u7891 ng em c\u432 \u7899 i l\u7841 i \u273 \'e2y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec tr\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  n\u7871 u ch\u7891 ng em m\'e0 c\u432 \u7899 i th\'ec sao n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! L\'fac \u273 \u7845 y c\u7855 t lu\'f4n, cho h\u7887 i \u273 i, l\u7845 y v\u7873  r\u7891 i ch\u7859 ng l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec n\u7919 a. Ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh m\'e0 l\'e0m th\u7871  ch\u7855 c l\'e0 nhu c\u7847 u cao l\u7855 m nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i tr\'eau Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao bi\uc0\u7871 t nhu c\u7847 u cao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec ph\uc0\u7843 i c\'f3 nh\u432  c\u7847 u cao th\'ec m\u7899 i l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 . Nhu c\u7847 u \'edt th\'ec l\'e0m \u259 n ki\u7875 u g\'ec, \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o m\'e0 kh\'f4 nh\u432  ng\'f3i th\'ec ch\u7871 t \'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  v\u7907  c\'f3 nh\u432  c\u7847 u cao kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7847 n ch\u7891 ng l\'e0 nhu c\u7847 u cao h\u7871 t. H\'f4m nay th\'e8m l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y.. kh\'f4ng chi\u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7907  l\'e0 v\u7907  d\u7895 i \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chi\uc0\u7873 u th\u7871  n\'e0o n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho v\uc0\u7907  th\u7887 a m\'e3n cho v\u7907  ra nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a. H\'f4m nay kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao th\'e8m l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m l\'e0 th\'e8m th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'e9o t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'e8m l\'e0 th\'e8m ch\uc0\u7913  c\'f2n th\'e8m th\u7871  n\'e0o n\u7919 a. Gh\'e9t ch\u7891 ng!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Huy\uc0\u7873 n \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, nh\'ecn c\'e1i d\'e1ng ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c t\'f4 \u273 i\u7875 m b\u7903 i b\u7897  qu\u7847 n \'e1o ng\u7911  b\u7857 ng l\'f9a m\u7887 ng tang khi\u7871 n Huy\u7873 n c\'e0ng kh\'eau g\u7907 i h\u417 n. Bi\u7871 t ch\u7891 ng h\'f4m nay v\u7873  n\'ean Huy\u7873 n d\'f9ng lo\u7841 i n\u432 \u7899 c hoa g\'ec \u273 \'f3 m\'e0 t\'f4i m\u7899 i ng\u7917 i tho\'e1ng qua th\'f4i \u273 \'e3 m\'ea m\u7879 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n b\u432 \u7899 c kh\u7869  v\'e0o trong ph\'f2ng ng\u7911  th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 i theo r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y th\'ec ch\uc0\u7891 ng l\'e0m cho \u273 \'e3 th\'e8m n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 V\'f2ng tay t\uc0\u7915  ph\'eda sau \'f4m l\u7845 y c\'e1i eo nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i h\'f4n l\'ean t\'f3c Huy\u7873 n sau \u273 \'f3 xu\u7889 ng c\'e1i c\u7893  hon d\'e0i. Do Huy\u7873 n th\u7845 p h\u417 n t\'f4i n\'ean mu\u7889 n h\'f4n v\'e0o c\u7893  v\'e0 vai t\'f4i ph\u7843 i c\'fai th\u7845 p h\u417 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat. Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 a m\u7845 y ng\'f3n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i n\u7855 m nh\u7865  l\u7845 y b\'e0n tay t\'f4i m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  h\u7871 t th\'e8m r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Nh\'ecn m\u7863 t th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 h\u7871 t th\'e8m \'e1? Kh\'f4ng tin \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, xem h\u7871 t th\'e8m th\u7871  n\'e0o n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai b\'e0n tay \'f4m \uc0\u7903  eo t\'f4i l\u7847 n l\u432 \u7907 t di chuy\u7875 n, ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m \u273 \u432 a xu\u7889 ng mu l\u7891 n t\'f4i day nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'f2n m\u7897 t tay th\'ec \u273 \u432 a l\'ean b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i n\'e2ng n\'e2ng n\'f3 m\'e0 ngh\u7883 ch.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\u7855 m ch\u7863 t hai tay t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ngh\uc0\u7883 ch linh tinh, b\u7843 o h\u7871 t th\'e8m r\u7891 i c\u417  m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 i\'eau! S\u7901  h\u7859 n xu\u7889 ng th\'ec m\u7899 i bi\u7871 t h\u7871 t hay kh\'f4ng ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u432 \u7901 m m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i d\u7847 n d\u7847 n bu\'f4ng th\'f5ng hai tay m\'ecnh ra, t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7875  lu\u7891 n v\'e0o trong qu\u7847 n m\'e0 vu\u7889 t ve m\u417 n tr\u7899 n c\'e1i l\u7891 n. G\u7847 n nh\u432  h\u417 n m\u7897 t tu\u7847 n nay th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7897 ng v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7891 n \u7845 m \'e1p c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t nh\u7865  hai \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay tr\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n m\'fap m\'e1p t\'f4i nh\u7853 n th\u7845 n kh\'f4ng c\'f2n m\u7897 t s\u7907 i l\'f4ng t\u417  n\'e0o n\u7919 a n\'ean \'f4m l\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n m\'fat nh\u7865  v\'e0nh tai m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7849 y h\u7871 t l\'f4ng r\u7891 i h\u7843  v\u7907  y\'eau?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ng\u7917 a \u273 \u7847 u ra m\'e0 n\'f3i kh\u7869 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7849 y h\u7871 t l\'f4ng \u273 i th\u7845 y tho\u7843 i m\'e1i, v\u7899 i l\u7841 i l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y th\'ec li\u7871 m s\u432 \u7899 ng h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'fat th\uc0\u7853 t m\u7841 nh c\'e1i d\'e1i tai th\'eam m\u7897 t ph\'e1t t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'edch li\u7871 m l\u7855 m \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m ng\u432 \u7907 ng ng\'f9ng g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e2ng! C\uc0\u361 ng t\u7841 i m\u7845 y ch\u7883  ch\u7895  em c\u7913  n\'f3i nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i g\u7841  em th\u7917 . C\'e1c ch\u7883  \u7845 y c\'f2n mi\'eau t\u7843  c\u7909  th\u7875  l\'e0 li\u7871 m th\u7871  n\'e0o r\u7891 i l\'e0m ki\u7875 u g\'ec n\u7919 a \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 ung \u273 \u432 a ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m ki\uc0\u7875 u g\'ec l\'e0 l\'e0m ki\u7875 u g\'ec?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec ki\uc0\u7875 u \u7903  ngo\'e0i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng n\'e0y, ch\u7895  v\u7855 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7901  bi\u7875 n c\'e1c ki\u7875 u n\u7919 a. H\'f4m \u273 i tr\u259 ng m\u7853 t v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh ch\u7881  l\'e0m trong kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n th\'f4i nh\u7881 , \u273 \'e1ng nh\u7869  ph\u7843 i th\u7917  nhi\u7873 u ch\u7895  kh\'e1c!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Eo c\'e0ng ng\'e0y c\'e0ng d\'e2m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879  h\'ec h\'ec..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  li\u7871 m th\'ec v\u7907  th\'edch li\u7871 m ch\u7895  n\'e0o, h\'f4m nay ch\u7891 ng li\u7871 m cho kh\'f4ng c\'f2n m\u7897 t t\'ed n\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0o lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7895  n\'e0o c\u361 ng th\'edch nh\u432 ng m\'e0 th\'edch nh\u7845 t l\'e0 li\u7871 m c\'e1i h\u7897 t le \u7845 y.. n\'f3 bu\u7891 n bu\u7891 n t\'ea t\'ea.. c\u7913  \u273 \u7897 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 th\'ec em l\u7841 i ra n\u432 \u7899 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec t\u7909 t qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng li\u7871 m lu\'f4n!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i b\uc0\u7871  th\u7889 c Huy\u7873 n l\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7875  Huy\u7873 n n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng r\u7891 i k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n xu\u7889 ng v\u7913 t sang m\u7897 t b\'ean. Mu l\u7891 n c\u259 ng m\u7885 ng, l\u7845 m t\u7845 m v\'e0i c\'e1i g\u7889 c l\'f4ng tr\'f4ng kh\'eau g\u7907 i v\'f4 c\'f9ng. Nh\u7845 t l\'e0 c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n kh\'edt kh\'ecn kh\u7883 t \u273 \u7887  au b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7891 i ch\u7891 m h\u7895 m r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u th\u7893 i nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Mu c\uc0\u7911 a em c\'f3 c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 th\u7893 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng chi\'eau k\'edch th\'edch h\u417 i b\u7883  hay \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.. n\'e0o d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra \u273 i, d\u7841 o n\'e0y t\u259 ng c\'e2n hay sao m\'e0 mu m\'fap th\u7871  kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em t\uc0\u259 ng c\'e2n nh\u432 ng m\'e0 nh\'ecn n\'f3 c\u361 ng c\'f3 m\'fap m\u7845 y \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 kh\'f4ng m\'fap th\'ec th\u7871  n\'e0o m\u7899 i l\'e0 m\'fap n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i ch\'e0m ch\uc0\u7853 m th\u7893 i nh\u7865  nhe sang hai b\'ean b\u7865 n. Huy\u7873 n ch\u7855 c nh\u7897 t n\'ean d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n ra \u273 \u7875  c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n m\u7903  ra \u273 \'f4i ch\'fat. T\'f4i m\u7899 i kh\u7869  kh\u7869  d\'f9ng hai ng\'f3n tay k\'e9o hai c\'e1i m\'e9p th\u7883 t cho h\u7897 t le h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng l\u7897  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i l\uc0\u7895  l\u7891 n nh\u7887  nh\u7855 n b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e3 ti\u7871 t ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7909 c \u273 \u7909 c r\u7891 i. Ch\u432 a v\u7897 i li\u7871 m m\'e0 t\'f4i ch\u7881  h\'f4n v\'e0o c\'e1i khe m\'e0 th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u432 \u7905 n cong ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7915 a m\'fat v\u7915 a c\u7855 n nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 nh\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i anh nh\'e9, anh c\u7855 n v\'e0o hai c\'e1i m\'e9p \u7845 y..em th\'edch day day c\'e1i m\'e9p..h\u417 i \u273 au nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\u7899 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 m l\'e1p c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n. \u272 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i ch\u7841 m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  v\'e0o c\'e1i h\u7897 t le c\u259 ng m\u7885 ng tr\'f2n vo th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\u7843 y ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7849 ng l\'ean nh\'ecn Huy\u7873 n th\'ec th\u7845 y Huy\u7873 n lim dim m\u7855 t t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7891 ng y\'eau th\u432 \u417 ng m\'ecnh r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngo\'e1y tr\'f2n c\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i quanh h\u7897 t le r\u7891 i t\'f4i ch\u7885 c c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  th\'ec Huy\u7873 n o\u7857 n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean. T\'f4i m\'fat c\'e1i ch\u7909 t th\'ec d\'f2ng n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7909 c \u273 \u7909 c \u273 \'f3 chui kh\u7869  v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 n\uc0\u7891 ng n\u7891 ng th\'f4i nh\u432 ng l\'e0m t\'f4i th\'edch l\u7855 m. C\'f4ng nh\u7853 n l\'e0 c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n li\u7871 m tho\u7843 i m\'e1i h\u417 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh r\u7845 t nhi\u7873 u. c\'e0ng li\u7871 m t\'f4i c\'e0ng th\'edch.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'e1 to mi\uc0\u7879 ng ng\u7853 m c\u7843  c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n r\u7891 i t\'f4i c\u7855 n, Huy\u7873 n b\u7845 u ch\u7863 t v\'e0o c\'e1i g\u7889 i r\u7891 i r\'ean l\'ean th\u7853 t to:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 A..a.a.a.a anh \uc0\u417 i.. ch\u7891 ng \u417 i..em \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1.. s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'e1i l\u7891 n qu\'e1 anh \u417 i..em th\'edch ch\u7891 ng ch\u7885 c v\'e0o c\'e1i l\u7895  .. ch\u7885 c m\u7841 nh v\'e0o \u273 i.. em s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1..a.a \u273 \'e3 qu\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7849 ng l\'ean t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7885 c v\'e0o s\'e2u hay th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7885 c.. v\'e0o s\'e2u n\u7919 a \u273 i.. em th\'edch.. s\u432 \u7899 ng l\u7855 m, anh n\'fat h\u7897 t le em \u273 i..c\u7855 n hai b\'ean c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n n\u7919 a \u7845 y..em th\'edch c\u7855 n..\
