\cf2 \cb3 L\'e0m theo l\uc0\u7901 i Huy\u7873 n th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\'ean trong c\'e0ng ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u, xu\u7889 ng t\u7853 n c\'e1i l\u7895  \u273 \'edt th\'e2m \u273 en b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i. M\'fat th\u7853 t l\'e2u th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a hai ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o m\'e0 m\'f3c. D\'f9 l\'e0 v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng v\'e0 \'e2n \'e1i nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng l\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n kh\'edt l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Hai ng\'f3n tay ngo\'e1y m\uc0\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n m\u7899 i r\u7897 ng ra th\'eam, ch\u7885 c s\'e2u ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o r\u7891 i t\'f4i h\u7887 i Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  m\u7845 y b\'e0 ch\u7883  c\u7911 a em \u7903  c\'f4ng ty c\'f3 b\u7843 o l\'e0 m\'f3c cua th\u7871  n\'e0o kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7893 n h\u7875 n r\u7891 i m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\'f3c th\'ec nh\uc0\u7865  nh\u7865  th\'f4i,.h\'ec h\'ec..m\'e0 m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y b\u7853 y l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i v\u7915 a m\'f3c v\u7915 a li\u7871 m r\u7891 i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7853 y th\'ec b\u7853 y th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec b\uc0\u7853 y c\u7913  ki\u7875 u m\'f3c l\u7891 n m\u7841 nh l\'ean.. m\'f3c banh l\u7891 n ra \u7845 y.. m\'e0 kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y \u273 \u7867  l\u7891 n l\u7891 n to ra hay sao \u7845 y, c\'f3 b\'e0 c\'f2n b\u7843 o ch\u7891 ng ho\u7863 c b\u7891  cho c\u7843  b\u7889 n \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o b\'ean trong l\u7891 n m\'e0 m\'f3c n\u7919 a c\u417 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u7873  h\u7873  b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 \u273 \u7867  r\u7891 i n\'f3 m\u7899 i th\u7871  ch\u7913 , b\'e9 t\'ed th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 c\u7889  nh\'e9t th\'eam th\'ec c\u361 ng ch\u7883 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i kh\'f4ng li\uc0\u7871 m n\u7919 a, n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng c\u7841 nh Huy\u7873 n nh\u432 ng hai ng\'f3n tay th\'ec v\u7851 n m\'f3c nh\u7865  nh\u7865  r\u7891 i m\'e2n m\'ea c\'e1i h\u7897 t le.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n quay sang n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh r\u7891 i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y c\u361 ng nhi\u7873 u \u273 \u7891  ch\u417 i l\u7855 m ch\u7891 ng \u7841 ? C\'f3 b\'e0 mang cho em xem c\'e1i c\u7863 c gi\u7843  to \u417 i l\'e0 to.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ph\'ec c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 To th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 To g\uc0\u7845 p \u273 \'f4i c\u7911 a ch\u7891 ng l\'e0 \'edt, m\'e0 n\'f3 d\'e0i c\u7905  g\u7847 n hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'e2n \u7845 y, \u273 en x\'ec b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y lu\'f4n \u7845 y. Nh\'ecn ki\u7875 u ki\u7875 u nh\u432  c\u7911 a m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng t\'e2y \u273 en \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7891 n m\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y r\u7897 ng th\u7871  th\'ec ch\u7881  c\'f3 lo\u7841 i \u7845 y m\u7899 i \u273 \'e1p \u7913 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! To nh\u432  c\u7911 a ch\u7891 ng nhi\u7873 u l\'fac \u273 \'fat v\'e0o c\u361 ng \u273 au l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y l\u7841 i c\'f2n v\u7915 a d\'e0i v\u7915 a to n\u7919 a ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i tr\'eau Huy\uc0\u7873 n n\'ean h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  v\u7907  c\'f3 th\'edch kh\'f4ng ch\u7891 ng mua cho m\u7897 t c\'e1i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i! \uc0\u272 \u7891  th\u7853 t c\'f2n d\'f9ng kh\'f4ng h\u7871 t th\'ec d\'f9ng \u273 \u7891  gi\u7843  l\'e0m g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\'f3i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o qu\u7847 n m\'e0 m\u417 n tr\u7899 n con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i. X\'f3c x\'f3c n\'f3 m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n kh\u7869  b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y ch\uc0\u7891 ng \u417 i, tr\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 hay vu\u7889 t th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i tr\u432 \u7899 c y\'eau th\'ec ph\u7843 i vu\u7889 t ch\u7913 , m\'e0 vu\u7889 t th\'ec m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u7913 , n\'f3 m\'e0 m\u7873 m nh\u432  c\u7885 ng b\'fan th\'ec l\'e0m \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n b\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Nh\'ecn c\'e1i m\u7863 t nh\u432  th\u7871  kia, m\u7899 i ng\u7917 i h\u417 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ta l\'e0 \u273 \'e3 c\u7913 ng nh\u432  kh\'fac g\u7895  r\u7891 i c\'f2n b\'e0y \u273 \u7863 t, c\'e1i m\u7863 t d\'e2m d\'ea th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec kh\'f4ng l\u7851 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  c\u417  \'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  ch\u7883  \u7845 y m\'fat c\'f3 hay kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3! H\'f4m nay sao t\uc0\u7921  nhi\'ean to\'e0n h\u7887 i chuy\u7879 n c\u361  th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'edch th\'ec h\uc0\u7887 i th\'f4i h\'ec h\'ec, m\'e0 v\u7907  n\'f3i th\u7853 t n\'e0y, ch\u7859 ng hi\u7875 u sao h\u7887 i chuy\u7879 n \u7845 y v\u7907  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y n\u7913 ng n\u7913 ng mu\u7891 n \u273 \'e8 ch\u7891 ng ra ngay \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? T\u432 \u7903 ng ghen ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879 ! Ghen th\'ec c\u361 ng ghen nh\u432 ng m\'e0 ki\u7875 u v\u7851 n th\'edch th\'edch..\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec Huy\u7873 n ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m c\'fai xu\u7889 ng k\'e9o c\'e1i l\u7899 p da xung quanh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c r\u7891 i kh\u7869  \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i li\u7871 m v\'f2ng quang.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y l\u7847 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 b\'e0 \uc0\u7903  ch\u7895  em k\u7875  bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7921 c, b\u7855 t ch\u7891 ng c\u7855 m c\u7863 c v\'e0o h\u7897 p s\u7919 a chua sau \u273 \'f3 m\'fat m\'fat nh\u432  \u259 n kem \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0 h\'e0 r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  v\u7907  c\'f3 mu\u7889 n \u259 n s\u7919 a chua ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7845 y kh\'f4ng? N\u7871 u mu\u7889 n \u259 n ch\u7891 ng cho \u259 n th\u7917 \cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i t\u7911 m t\u7881 m n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7871 u m\'e0 \u259 n th\u7871  th\'ec c\u7843  hai c\'f9ng \u259 n nh\'e9, kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\u7855 t em \u259 n m\u7897 t m\'ecnh \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng chuy\u7879 n g\'ec ch\u7913  anh \u259 n tho\u7843 i m\'e1i ha ha, l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y ch\u7891 ng \u259 n l\u7841 i b\u7843 o k\'eau b\u7849 n l\u7855 m kh\'f4ng cho ch\u7891 ng \u259 n n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Kh\'f4ng c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 \u273 \'e2u nh\'e9, b\u7849 n c\u361 ng \u259 n \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u432 \u7907 c ch\u417 i lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i h\'ed h\uc0\u7917 ng ch\u7841 y ra t\u7911  l\u7841 nh l\u7845 y hai h\u7897 p s\u7919 a chua r\u7891 i ch\u7841 y v\'e0o n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7895 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t h\u7897 p, b\u7855 t ph\u7843 i \u259 n h\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9. B\'e2y gi\u7901  ai \u259 n tr\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh ch\uc0\u7913  c\'f2n ai n\u7919 a, c\'f3 th\u7871  m\'e0 c\u361 ng h\u7887 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7857 m \u273 \'e0ng ho\'e0ng ngay ng\u7855 n n\'e0o, ch\u417 i lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n h\'ed h\u7917 ng n\u7857 m th\u7859 ng ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i du\u7895 i th\u7859 ng ch\'e2n nh\u432 ng h\u417 i d\u7841 ng r\u7897 ng ra m\u7897 t ch\'fat. T\'f4i b\'f3c h\u7897 p s\u7919 a chua r\u7891 i l\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'eca qu\'e9t m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7889 ng s\u7919 a chua v\u7915 a m\u7899 i ch\u7841 m v\'e0o c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u7841 o s\u7841 ch s\u7869  th\'ec Huy\u7873 n gi\u7853 t b\u7855 n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ng\uc0\u7849 ng \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao th\uc0\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7841 nh l\u7855 m..\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0 h\'e0 t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7841 nh th\u7871  n\'e0y t\'ed m\'fat m\u7899 i s\u432 \u7899 ng, kh\'e9o t\'ea h\u7871 t c\u7843  ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'ean \u7845 y ch\u7913 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u7889  ch\u7883 u m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'ec t\'f4i \u273 \'e3 qu\u7871 t n\u7917 a h\u7897 p s\u7919 a chua l\'ean c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 m. M\'f9i v\u7883  s\u7919 a chua th\u417 m ngon l\'e0m t\'f4i li\u7871 m h\u259 ng say l\u7855 m. Huy\u7873 n th\'edch n\'ean lim dim m\u7855 t ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a t\'f4i khua kho\u7855 ng c\'e1i l\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Li\uc0\u7871 m ch\'e1n mu th\'ec t\'f4i g\u7849 y \u273 \'fang v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n r\u7891 i ch\u7885 c ch\u7885 c h\u7897 t le m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\'e9t ti\uc0\u7871 p v\'e0o \u273 \'e2y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 qu\'e9t xong l\'e0 li\u7871 m \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9, n\'f3 ch\u7843 y xu\u7889 ng gi\u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0 ph\u7843 i gi\u7863 t ga \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh bi\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7893  m\u7897 t \'edt s\u7919 a chua l\'ean h\u7897 t le r\u7891 i t\'f4i chu m\'f4i m\'fai ch\u7909 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i. M\'f9i v\u7883  c\u7911 a s\u7919 a \'e1t h\u7871 t m\'f9i c\u7911 a n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n ch\'ednh v\'ec th\u7871  t\'f4i m\'fat m\u7841 nh h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n o\u7857 n ng\u432 \u7901 i, b\u7845 u ch\u7863 t tay v\'e0o g\u7889 i cong c\'f4ng l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i t\'ea l\uc0\u7891 n qu\'e1 ch\u7891 ng \u417 i.. th\'edch qu\'e1 \u273 i m\u7845 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u7913  m\'fat s\u7897 p so\u7841 p cho Huy\u7873 n mu\u7889 n r\'ean th\u7871  n\'e0o th\'ec r\'ean, nho\u7857 ng c\'e1i \u273 \'e3 h\u7871 t h\u7897 p s\u7919 a chua t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y ti\uc0\u7871 p h\u7897 p n\u7919 a nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7912 ! Th\'f4i.. kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a \u273 \'e2u\'85 em l\'ean \u273 \u7881 nh r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y! N\u432 \u7899 c n\'f4i ch\u7843 y t\'f9m lum r\u7891 i h\'edch h\'edch ..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7859 ng th\u7845 y t\'ed n\u432 \u7899 c n\'e0o ch\u7843 y ra c\u7843 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh m\'fat h\uc0\u7871 t r\u7891 i c\'f2n \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7843 y ra n\u7919 a ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\'f3i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec b\'e2y gi\u7901  \u273 \u7871 n l\u432 \u7907 t v\u7907  \u259 n xem n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n th\u7903  m\u7841 nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i v\u432 \u417 n vai ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\'f3 l\u7869  c\'e1i c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u273 \'ea m\'ea n\'e2ng n\'e2ng t\u7915  c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n ch\u7841 y kh\u7855 p c\u417  th\u7875  v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 \u7897 ng l\u7841 i nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng th\'ec em m\u7899 i qu\'e9t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'ean ch\u7913 , \u273 \u7913 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  l\'e0m sao m\'e0 em qu\'e9t l\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u d\'f9ng s\u7919 a chua qu\'e9t l\'ean c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i b\u7909 ng sau \u273 \'f3 c\'fai xu\u7889 ng m\'fat. S\u7919 a chua l\u7841 nh l\'e0m con c\u7863 c t\'f4i h\u417 i co l\u7841 i m\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u432 ng Huy\u7873 n li\u7871 m m\u7845 y c\'e1i th\'ec n\'f3 d\u7847 n d\u7847 n l\u7841 i c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u7875 n \u273 \u7847 u l\'ean t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u258 n s\u7919 a chua ki\u7875 u n\'e0y c\'f3 ngon h\u417 n kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i h\u7887 i l\u7841 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  l\'fac n\'e3y \u259 n c\'f3 ngon kh\'f4ng m\'e0 c\'f2n h\u7887 i em?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913  h\'ec h\'ec .. ngon l\u7855 m \u7845 y.. v\u7915 a n\'f3ng v\u7915 a l\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i n\'f3i xong th\'ec Huy\uc0\u7873 n kh\'fac kh\'edch c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i c\u7913  th\u7871  say m\'ea m\'fat con c\u7863 c, h\u7871 t l\u7899 p s\u7919 a chua n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n l\u7899 p s\u7919 a chua kh\'e1c.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\'f4i h\uc0\u7871 t con c\u7863 c th\'ec Huy\u7873 n b\'f4i c\u7889  m\u7897 t \'edt s\u7919 a chua c\'f2n x\'f3t l\u7841 i l\'ean hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i ng\u7853 m c\u7843  hai h\'f2n d\'e1i m\'e0 m\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i ki\uc0\u7875 u say m\'ea m\'fat th\u7873  n\'e0y l\'e0 t\'f4i bi\u7871 t Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7845 y b\'e0 d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng \u7903  ch\u7895  l\'e0m ch\u7881  cho r\u7891 i ch\u7913  t\'f4i ch\u7881  m\'e3i Huy\u7873 n c\u361 ng ch\u432 a thu\u7847 n th\u7909 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7871  n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Con c\uc0\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c \u273 ung \u273 \u432 a khi Huy\u7873 n l\u7845 y tay g\u7849 y g\u7849 y r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y gi\uc0\u7901  l\'e0m nh\'e9! Ch\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! C\u7889  g\u7855 ng l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y, t\'ed n\u7919 a th\'ec cho em \u259 n s\u7919 a chua n\'f3ng \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng h\u7843 ? D\u7841 o n\'e0y ai ch\u7881  d\u7841 y m\'e0 m\'fat kinh th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec m\uc0\u7845 y b\'e0 \u7845 y c\u7913  n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n n\'ean em h\'f3ng h\u7885 c theo th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Tr\uc0\u7843  l\u7901 i t\'f4i xong th\'ec Huy\u7873 n n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng, lu\u7891 n tay v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n day day \u273 \u7875  k\'edch th\'edch. \u272 \u7843 o c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tay quanh h\u7897 t le m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 s\uc0\u7919 a chua d\'ednh qu\'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'ednh m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i, t\'ed n\u432 \u7899 c ra kh\'e9o m\'e0 tr\u417 n nh\u7851 y lu\'f4n \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i banh c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n ra ch\u7901  \u273 \u7907 i con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\u7855 m v\'e0o. Qu\u7923  xu\u7889 ng c\u7847 m con c\u7863 c qu\'e9t d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y n\'f3 d\'ednh th\u7853 t nh\u432 ng th\'f4i k\u7879 . L\'e0m m\u7897 t t\'ed l\'e0 c\u7843  hai s\u7869  tho\u7843 i m\'e1i ngay th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7875  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c \u273 \'fang c\'e1i l\u7895  r\u7891 i t\'f4i \u7845 n v\'e0o ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m cho c\u7843  hai c\'f9ng s\u432 \u7899 ng. C\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n \u7845 m n\'f3ng c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n banh ra \'f4m l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c m\u7897 t c\'e1ch kh\'edt khao. Huy\u7873 n h\u417 i nh\u259 n m\u7863 t m\u7897 t c\'e1i r\u7891 i day h\u7897 t le m\'e0 r\'ean \u432  \u7917 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\uc0\u7845 y th\u7871  h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay m\'e0 l\uc0\u7841 i \u273 au \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n l\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u nh\u7865  nh\u7865  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 au \u273 \'e2u anh.. s\u432 \u7899 ng s\u432 \u7899 ng h\'ec h\'ec.. \u273 \'e3 l\u7855 m \u7845 y\'85.\u7845 n s\'e2u v\'e0o \u273 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 ang v\'e0o r\u7891 i n\'e0y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u7844 n cho c\'e1i \u273 \'e1m l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh \u7903  g\u7889 c c\u7863 c ch\u7841 m v\'e0o c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n th\'ec t\'f4i r\'fat ra l\'e0m l\u7841 i v\'e0i l\u7847 n nh\u432  th\u7871 . N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n \u7845 y v\u7853 y m\'e0 tu\'f4n ra nhi\u7873 u v\'f4 c\'f9ng, n\'f3 l\'e0m cho c\u7843  c\'e1i g\u7889 c c\u7863 c b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y l\'ean \u273 \u7863 c qu\'e1nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7897 t tay t\'f4i xoa xoa c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n, m\u7897 t tay t\'f4i b\'f3p c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh nh\uc0\u7845 p m\u7841 nh nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i \'f4m t\'f4i. C\u7843  hai th\'e2n th\u7875  n\'f3ng b\u7887 ng b\u7903 i ng\u7885 n l\u7917 a d\u7909 c t\'ecnh qu\u7845 n l\u7845 y nhau. Ti\u7871 ng ph\'e0nh ph\u7841 ch \u273 \u7873 u \u273 \u7863 n vang l\'ean m\u7895 i khi con c\u7863 c t\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7849 y s\'e2u v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n. H\u7871 t ki\u7875 u truy\u7873 n th\u7889 ng th\'ec \u273 \u7871 n ki\u7875 u \'fap th\'eca r\u7891 i m\u7897 t s\u7889  ki\u7875 u kh\'e1c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai v\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng th\u7845 m m\u7879 t th\'ec t\'f4i c\u361 ng phun \u273 \u7911  hai l\u7847 n tinh tr\'f9ng n\'f3ng h\u7893 i v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n kh\'edt khao c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7857 m trong v\'f2ng tay t\'f4i Huy\u7873 n n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\uc0\u7845 y r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  h\u7891 i x\u432 a nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'edch \u273 \u432 \u7907 c l\'e0m nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  h\u7891 i x\u432 a \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n t\u7911 m t\u7881 m g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\'fac \u7903  ch\u7895  l\'e0m \u7845 y, m\u7845 y b\'e0 ch\u7883  c\u7913  n\'f3i \u273 \u7871 n chuy\u7879 n n\'e0y kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u sao l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y em th\'e8m \u417 i l\'e0 th\'e8m \u7845 y, n\u432 \u7899 c ra \u432 \u7899 t \u273 \u7851 m qu\u7847 n lu\'f4n !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7907  g\'ec m\'e0 d\'e2m th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 K\uc0\u7879 , em c\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t sao nh\u432  v\u7853 y nh\u432 ng m\'e0 l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y ph\u7843 i c\'f3 b\u259 ng v\u7879  sinh \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh n\u432 \u7899 c ra \u7845 y, nhi\u7873 u n\u432 \u7899 c l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  sao kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i anh \u273 \u7871 n m\'fat cho!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Th\u7871  h\'f4m n\'e0o em g\u7885 i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec Huy\u7873 n l\u7841 i h\u7887 i t\'f4i v\u7873  chuy\u7879 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh ti\u7871 p. N\'f3i chung l\'e0 nh\u7919 ng k\u7881  ni\u7879 m x\u432 a r\u7891 i nh\u7919 ng ki\u7875 u l\'e0m t\'ecnh c\u7911 a t\'f4i v\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i k\uc0\u7875  d\u297  nhi\'ean l\'e0 gi\u7845 u m\u7897 t ph\u7847 n ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng k\u7875  cho Huy\u7873 n bi\u7871 t. N\'f3i chuy\u7879 n \u273 \u7871 n khuya th\'ec hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ng\u7911  lu\'f4n.\
