\cf2 \cb3 S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau d\uc0\u7853 y c\u7843  hai t\u7845 t b\u7853 t \u273 i l\'e0m th\'ec t\'f4i tr\'eau Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay m\'e0 c\'f2n ra n\uc0\u432 \u7899 c n\u7919 a th\'ec b\u7843 o ch\u7891 ng nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! H\'ec h\'ec!\cb1 \
\
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai l\u7841 i b\u7883  cu\u7889 n v\'e0o c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u t\u7889 i, t\'f4i \u273 \u432 a Huy\u7873 n \u273 i \u259 n th\'ec b\u7855 t g\u7863 p Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i v\u7899 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u7919 a, n\'f3i chung to\'e0n d\u7841 ng ch\u417 i b\u7901 i ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7855 n nh\u432  hai ng\u432 \u7901 i h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nh\'e1y m\uc0\u7855 t b\u7843 o Huy\u7873 n:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kia k\'eca!\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n quay l\u7841 i nh\'ecn r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i sao tr\'f4ng kh\'e1c th\uc0\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'e1c l\'e0 kh\'e1c th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'f4ng gi\'e0 \uc0\u273 i v\'e0 x\u7845 u \u273 i nhanh ch\'f3ng \u7845 y, kh\'f4ng c\'f2n nh\u432  c\'e1i h\'f4m c\u432 \u7899 i m\'ecnh n\u7919 a, m\'e0 c\'e1ch \u273 \'e2y c\'f3 m\u7845 y th\'e1ng \u7845 y nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec gi\'e0 \uc0\u273 i th\'f4i v\u7899 i l\u7841 i \u259 n nh\u7853 u th\'e1c lo\u7841 n th\u7871  kh\'f4ng gi\'e0 \u273 i m\u7899 i l\u7841 . M\'e0 th\'f4i \u273 \u7875  \'fd l\'e0m g\'ec em, h\u7885  c\'f3 con \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng s\u7889 ng c\u7911 a h\u7885  th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u nh\u432 ng v\u7851 n \u273 \u7875  \'fd \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i ch\u7895  m\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ang ng\u7891 i, \u259 n u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh v\u7899 i m\u7845 y ng\u432 \u7901 i kia \u273 i, t\'f4i nh\'ecn th\u7845 y c\'f3 b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nam gi\u7899 i , t\u7909 i n\'f3 ch\u7855 c d\'e2n x\'e3 h\u7897 i n\'ean x\u259 m tr\u7893  c\u361 ng nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m. T\'f4i th\u7847 m ngh\u297  \'93C\'e1i l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh h\'f4m nay ch\u7855 c n\'e1t v\u7899 i b\u7889 n con c\u7863 c kia r\u7891 i\'94.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7907 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i khu\u7845 t h\u7859 n th\'ec Huy\u7873 n h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'e0 n\'e0y gi\uc0\u7901  ch\u417 i v\u7899 i c\u7843  d\'e2n x\'e3 h\u7897 i anh nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng c\'f3 th\u7873  m\'e0 c\u361 ng bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u l\'e0 kh\'e1ch th\'ec sao. M\u7889 i l\'e0m \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n ngh\u297  ngh\u297  m\u7845 t m\u7845 y gi\'e2y r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i d\'e2n l\'e0m \u259 n \u273 \'e2u, b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng k\u7875  c\u7843  x\u259 m m\'ecnh nh\u432 ng khi b\'e0n chuy\u7879 n c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\'e1c ki\u7875 u c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng \u259 n m\u7863 c th\u7871  kia.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u7853 m \u7915  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u h\u432 \u7903 ng \u7913 ng l\u7901 i n\'f3i c\u7911 a Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i vi\uc0\u7879 c ai ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7845 y l\'e0m, v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng m\'ecnh \u273 i si\'eau th\u7883  \u273 i\u7879 n m\'e1y s\u7855 m m\u7845 y \u273 \u7891  \u273 i, anh m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u432 \u7903 ng \'edt ti\u7873 n, v\u7899 i l\u7841 i \u273 \u7891  nh\'e0 m\'ecnh c\u361  r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ed h\'ed! Th\uc0\u7871  t\u7863 ng v\u7907  c\'e1i g\'ec kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec t\uc0\u7863 ng v\u7907  \u273 \u7891  c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7845 y kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i t\u7863 ng m\'e0 l\'e0 d\'f9ng chung nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i tr\u7843  ti\u7873 n n\u432 \u7899 c sau \u273 \'f3 hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng \u273 i, v\u7915 a ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7891  v\u7915 a nghe t\u432  v\u7845 n nh\u432 ng h\'ecnh \u7843 nh l\'fac n\'e3y c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \'e1m \u7843 nh v\'e0o t\'e2m tr\'ed t\'f4i r\u7891 i. T\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh li\u7879 u c\'f3 ch\u7883 u \u273 \u7921 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\u7899 i b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i l\u7921 c l\u432 \u7905 ng kia kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f4ng lung m\'e3i, t\'f4i l\uc0\u7841 i ch\u7907 t ngh\u297  \u273 \u7871 n Huy\u7873 n \u273 ang \u273 i b\'ean c\u7841 nh b\'e8n l\u7845 y l\u7841 i v\u7867  b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng r\u7891 i g\u7841  Huy\u7873 n \u273 i mua n\u432 \u7899 c hoa, sau \u273 \'f3 t\u7863 ng Huy\u7873 n m\u7897 t l\u7885 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai v\uc0\u7907  ch\u7891 ng vui v\u7867  \u273 \u7871 n t\u7889 i, \u273 i ng\u7911  Huy\u7873 n d\u7909 i nh\u7865  v\'e0o ng\u7921 c t\'f4i kh\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u7855 c l\'e0 v\u7851 n c\'f2n t\u417  t\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n ch\u7883  Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngu\'fdt d\'e0i t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u417  t\u432 \u7903 ng c\'e1i g\'ec c\u417  ch\u7913 , v\u7907  y\'eau ghen \u273 \u7845 y \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ghen l\uc0\u7855 m nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7843 m th\u7845 y ch\u7891 ng kh\'f3 x\u7917  ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y \u273 \'fang kh\'f4ng? N\'f3i v\u7907  nghe xem n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\uc0\u7869  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i t\u417  t\u432 \u7903 ng \u273 \u7871 n hay kh\'f4ng, s\u7907  h\'f4m nay \u273 i v\u7899 i m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u273 \u7845 y n\'f3 hi\u7871 p \u273 \'e1p g\'ec th\'f4i ch\u7913  t\'ecnh c\u7843 m th\'ec l\'e0m g\'ec c\'f2n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ? Th\u7871  h\'f4m n\'e0o m\'e0 t\'ecm g\u7863 p ch\u7883  \u7845 y khuy\'ean ch\u7883  \u7845 y l\'e0m m\u7897 t c\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y, hay xin v\'e0o c\'f4ng ty n\'e0o \u273 \'f3 l\'e0m, ch\u7883  \u7845 y h\u7885 c h\'e0nh c\u361 ng c\'f3 b\u7857 ng c\u7845 p m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  \u273 \u7875  anh t\'ednh xem. Ch\u7855 c khuy\'ean nh\u7911  n\u7871 u thi\u7871 u ti\u7873 n th\'ec m\'ecnh gi\'fap m\u7897 t \'edt ti\u7873 n l\'e0 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Huy\uc0\u7873 n kh\u7869  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i \'f4m t\'f4i, hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng ng\u7911  l\'fac n\'e0o kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t. \u272 \u7871 n v\'e0i tu\u7847 n sau th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 A l\'f4 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7843 ? R\u7843 nh kh\'f4ng anh v\u7899 i em caf\'e9 m\u7897 t ch\'fat?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Gi\uc0\u7901  th\'ec em kh\'f4ng r\u7843 nh l\u7855 m.. \u273 \u7875  chi\u7873 u t\u7847 m hai gi\u7901  anh nh\'e9. V\u7851 n c\'e1i qu\'e1n h\'f4m tr\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 anh g\u7863 p em lu\'f4n \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! V\u7853 y c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fap m\'e1y xong t\'f4i \uc0\u273 i r\'fat th\'eam m\u7897 t \'edt ti\u7873 n m\u7863 t r\u7891 i chi\u7873 u mang \u273 \u7871 n c\'f3 v\u7867  Qu\u7923 nh c\u7847 n gi\'fap \u273 \u7905 . Hai gi\u7901  chi\u7873 u, t\'f4i qua c\'e1i qu\'e1n caf\'e9 l\u7847 n tr\u432 \u7899 c ng\u7891 i \u273 \u7907 i th\'ec hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'fat sau Qu\u7923 nh m\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7871 n.Th\u7845 y t\'f4i ng\u7891 i m\u7897 t m\'ecnh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao h\'f4m nay r\uc0\u7843 nh vi\u7879 c th\u7871  \'e0 m\'e0 m\u7901 i em caf\'e9 th\u7871  n\'e0y. \u272 i th\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f3 s\u7907  v\u7907  kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0 kh\'f4ng! Ng\uc0\u7891 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n t\'ed th\'f4i, ch\u7855 c anh g\u7885 i th\u7871  n\'e0y l\'e0m l\u7905  m\u7845 t c\'f4ng vi\u7879 c c\u7911 a em nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng, t\'ecnh c\uc0\u361  r\u7911  m\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 i th\'ec m\u7899 i l\'e0 l\u7905 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nheo m\u7855 t c\u432 \u7901 i tr\'eau t\'f4i. N\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m g\'ec c\'f3 m\uc0\u7845 y anh \u273 i c\'f9ng tr\'f4ng cao to l\u7921 c l\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m n\'e0o nh\uc0\u7881 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1ch \uc0\u273 \'e2y h\u417 n tu\u7847 n \u7903  qu\'e1n caf\'e9 Bi\u7875 n Kh\'e1t \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'c0.. h\'ec h\'ec, n\'f3i chung m\uc0\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u7845 t \u417  \u7845 y m\'e0. M\u7865  h\'f4m n\'f3 em v\u7915 a t\u7913 c v\u7915 a b\u7883  \u273 \'e1nh n\u7919 a ch\u7913  nh\u432 ng n\'f3i chung sau \u273 \'f3 th\'ec t\u7909 i n\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 th\u7857 ng n\'e0o c\'f2n l\'e0nh l\u7863 n c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 chuy\uc0\u7879 n g\'ec m\'e0 kinh th\u7871 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n d\'e0i d\'f2ng l\u7855 m \u273 \u7875  em k\u7875  d\u7847 n d\u7847 n cho m\'e0 nghe.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u b\u7857 ng m\u7897 t gi\u7885 ng v\u7851 n t\u7913 c t\u7889 i Qu\u7923 nh n\'f3i. H\'f4m \u273 \u7845 y u\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c xong th\'ec m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i nh\'e0 ngh\u7881 . T\u432 \u7903 ng kh\'e1ch b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i\u7873 u th\'eam m\u7897 t em n\u7919 a r\u7891 i hai ch\u7883  em \u273 i nh\u432 ng t\u7909 i n\'f3 v\'e0o trong \u273 \'f3 th\'ec \u273 \u7853 p \u273 \'e1 \u273 \u7911 ng r\u7891 i \u273 \'e8 Qu\u7923 nh ra v\u7899 i m\u7897 t em n\u7919 a m\'e0 l\'e0m t\u7853 p th\u7875 . R\u7891 i ki\u7875 u b\u7841 o d\'e2m.\cb1 \
\cb3 Nghe Qu\uc0\u7923 nh k\u7875  m\u7897 t th\'f4i m\u7897 t h\u7891 i t\'f4i bu\u7891 n c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m l\'fac \u273 \u7845 y s\u432 \u7899 ng c\'f2n k\'eau g\'ec n\u7919 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! S\u432 \u7899 ng g\'ec m\'e0 s\u432 \u7899 ng \u273 au ch\u7871 t cha ch\u7871 t m\u7865  lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng s\u432 \u7899 ng, b\u7889 n anh cao to l\u7921 c l\u432 \u7905 ng th\u7871  ph\u7909 c v\u7909  c\'f2n g\'ec. Th\u7871  sao kh\'f4ng s\u432 \u7899 ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\'ecnh th\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng th\'ec c\'f2n s\u432 \u7899 ng, \u273 \u7857 ng n\'e0y c\u7913  h\'f9ng h\u7909 c h\'f9ng h\u7909 c th\'ec ai m\'e0 ch\u7883 u n\u7893 i cho \u273 \u432 \u7907 c! T\u7909 i n\'f3 c\'f2n b\u7841 o d\'e2m n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh t\u7881 nh b\u417  g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i ch\'fai ng\u432 \u7901 i xu\u7889 ng th\u7911  th\u7881  n\'f3i nh\u7887  v\u7899 i t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7909 i n\'f3 \u273 eo bao gai g\u7911 ng \u273 \'f4n l\'ean d\'e0i \u273 \u7871 n hai m\u432 \u417 i ph\'e2n th\'ec l\'e0m sao ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, em c\u361 ng quen quen r\u7891 i nh\u432 ng em kia ch\u7843 y c\u7843  m\'e1u ra, g\'e0o kh\'f3c gh\'ea l\u7855 m\'85 gi\u7901  v\u7851 n c\'f2n \u273 au, ch\u7855 c n\u7917 a th\'e1ng n\u7919 a m\u7899 i kh\u7887 i \u7845 y. Ti\'ean s\u7921  b\u7885 n b\u7879 n ho\u7841 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nghe m\'e0 r\'f9ng m\'ecnh n\'ean h\uc0\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7853 y sau \u273 \'f3 th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7909 i n\'f3 qu\u7847 n em v\u7899 i con em em \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau, m\u7865  t\u7909 i ch\'f3 ch\u7871 t, Sau \u273 \'f3 th\'ec tr\u7843  m\u7897 t \u273 \u7889 ng ti\u7873 n nh\u432 ng m\'e0 em gh\'e9t c\'e1i th\'e1i \u273 \u7897  n\'ean v\u7873  t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng em x\'e3 h\u7897 i. M\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 nh\u7915  t\u7917  lu\'f4n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i l\u7841 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n b\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng, k\u7875  v\u7873  th\u7901 i h\u7885 c c\u7845 p ba r\u7891 i quen \u273 \u7913 a n\'e0y quen \u273 \u7913 a kh\'e1c l\'e2u r\u7891 i h\u7885 p l\u7899 p c\'f3 v\u7873  kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch chau ch\'e1t n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\uc0\u7873  c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\u7909 i n\'f3 l\u7841 i ngh\u297  m\'ecnh th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'ecnh th\u7871  kh\'e1c, \u7903  qu\'ea th\'ec bi\u7871 t th\u7915 a r\u7891 i c\'f2n g\'ec! Th\u7871  n\'ean em c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng th\'edch. Th\u7871  h\u7885 p l\u7899 p sao anh kh\'f4ng v\u7873 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 v\uc0\u7873  m\u7897 t hai l\u7847 n nh\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 b\u7853 n vi\u7879 c n\'ean ch\u7883 u kh\'f4ng v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n tr\u432 \u7901 ng l\u7899 p m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec l\u7841 i sang chuy\u7879 n gia \u273 \'ecnh. Qu\u7923 nh h\'ed h\u7917 ng b\u7843 o t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  Huy\u7873 n c\'f3 b\u7847 u ch\u432 a?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a! Ch\u7855 c sang n\u259 m th\'ec c\'f3!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i h\'edp m\u7855 t b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7889  g\u7855 ng m\'e0 nhanh nhanh l\'ean ch\u7913 , \u273 \u7847 y ng\u432 \u7901 i mong l\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i tr\'eau Qu\uc0\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  em c\'f3 mong kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3.. cho em l\'e0m m\uc0\u7865  \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u7847 u nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\uc0\u7869  m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u432 \u7903 ng m\u7865  ru\u7897 t th\u7853 t th\'ec h\u417 i kh\'f3 ch\u7913  m\u7865  \u273 \u7905  \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec \u273 \u417 n gi\u7843 n kh\'f4ng \u7845 y m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Th\u7871  xin m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a th\'ec c\'f3 cho kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i kh\'f4ng cho \uc0\u273 \'e2u, Huy\u7873 n n\'f3 c\u7855 t th\'ec h\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\'e0m \u259 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Cho th\'ec em c\u361 ng c\'f3 n\'f3i g\'ec v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e2u, coi nh\u432  c\u7911 a \u273 \u7875  d\'e0nh th\'f4i m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh chuy\u7875 n gh\u7871  sang ng\u7891 i c\u7841 nh t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y th\uc0\u7871  h\'f4m n\'e0o cho em \u273 \u7913 a \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i nheo m\uc0\u7855 t n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7875  xem c\'f2n m\'e0 cho kh\'f4ng \u273 \'e3 ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai c\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0n huy\'ean th\'eam ch\'fat n\u7919 a th\'ec t\'f4i l\u7845 y ti\u7873 n ra b\u7843 o cho Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh t\u7915  ch\u7889 i nh\u432 ng r\u7891 i Qu\u7923 nh c\u361 ng nh\u7853 n coi nh\u432  b\u7841 n b\'e8 gi\'fap \u273 \u7905  nhau.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i chuy\uc0\u7879 n th\'eam m\u7897 t l\'fac n\u7919 a th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh xin ph\'e9p t\'f4i v\u7873  tr\u432 \u7899 c v\'ec c\'f3 con em g\u7885 i, t\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c l\u7841 i c\'f3 kh\'e1ch n\'ean m\u7899 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i v\u7873  t\'f4i t\'e2m s\u7921  v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n tuy nhi\'ean c\'e1i chuy\u7879 n xin \u273 \u7913 a con th\'ec gi\u7845 u nh\u7865 m \u273 i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec c\u7843 . Huy\u7873 n th\u7845 y t\'f4i th\u7871  th\'ecm \u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i th\'edch l\u7855 m v\'ec hi\u7875 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \'fd t\'f4i.\
