\cf2 \cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian th\u7845 m tho\'e1t tr\'f4i \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n v\'e0i th\'e1ng sau t\'f4i ch\u7859 ng li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh n\u7919 a. \u272 \'fang l\'fac Huy\u7873 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 i c\'f4ng t\'e1c b\'ean Singapore hai tu\u7847 n th\'ec \u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean Qu\u7923 nh g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho t\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y v\'e0i th\'e1ng m\'e0 kh\'f4ng g\uc0\u7885 i em \u273 \u7871 n m\u7897 t cu\u7897 c \u273 i\u7879 n tho\u7841 i \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec sau h\'f4m g\uc0\u7863 p em anh b\u7853 n qu\'e1, li\'ean mi\'ean \u273 i h\u7871 t t\u7881 nh n\'e0y \u273 \u7871 n t\u7881 nh kh\'e1c l\'e0m th\u7883  tr\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 \u7847 u t\u7855 t m\u7863 t t\u7889 i lu\'f4n, v\u7907  c\u361 ng gi\u7853 n \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? C\u7853 n th\u7853 n kh\'f4ng th\'ec v\u7907  b\u7887  \u273 i \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7887  l\'e0 b\u7887  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \u7883 nh b\u7843 o b\u7887  l\'e0 b\u7887  th\u7871  n\'e0o, c\'f3 nh\u432  em \u273 \'e2u, nh\u432 ng t\'f4i ch\u7881  n\'f3i v\u7853 y th\'f4i. Qu\u7923 nh v\u7899 i t\'f4i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7889 i nay r\u7843 nh kh\'f4ng \u273 i nh\u7853 u \u273 \'eam v\u7899 i em. R\u7911  c\u7843  Huy\u7873 n \u273 i nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Huy\uc0\u7873 n nh\'e0 anh sang Singapore c\'f4ng t\'e1c r\u7891 i ch\u7855 c ph\u7843 i tu\u7847 n n\u7919 a m\u7899 i v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u417 . Mu\u7889 n nh\u7853 u th\'ec t\u7889 i h\u7865 n em \u7903  \u273 \'e2u n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'ec h\'ec qua nh\'e0 anh \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qua nh\'e0 anh r\u7891 i \u273 i nh\u7853 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i l\'e0m vi\uc0\u7879 c \u273 \u7871 n chi\u7873 u r\u7891 i v\u7873  nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  ng\u417 i sau \u273 \'f3 qua shop ng\u7855 m m\u7897 t b\u7897  v\'e1y m\'e0 t\'f4i c\u7843 m th\u7845 y h\u7907 p v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i mua g\'f3i c\u7849 n th\u7853 n \u273 \u7875  t\u7863 ng Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\uc0\u7889 i mu\u7897 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh m\u7899 i g\u7885 i b\u7855 t taxi \u273 \u7871 n nh\'e0 t\'f4i r\u7891 i t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i nh\u7853 u. V\u7851 n son ph\u7845 n th\u7853 t \u273 \u7853 m nh\u432 ng Qu\u7923 nh tr\'f4ng kh\'e1c h\u7859 n, \u273 \'e3 t\u432 \u417 i t\u7855 n h\u417 n v\'e0 c\'f3 v\u7867  \u273 i th\u7849 m m\u297  vi\u7879 n n\'ean c\'e1i m\u361 i cao h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a l\'e1i xe v\u7915 a n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n t\'f4i h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Tr\'f4ng d\uc0\u7841 o n\'e0y xinh v\u7899 i t\u432 \u417 i h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 c\'f4ng vi\uc0\u7879 c m\u7899 i m\'e0, em m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\'e1i salon t\'f3c r\u7891 i, h\'f4m n\'e0o qua ch\u7895  em ch\u417 i, em g\u7897 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u7855 t t\'f3c mi\u7877 n ph\'ed cho.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  \'e0? Ch\'fac m\u7915 ng nh\'e9, th\u7871  m\'e0 h\'f4m khai tr\u432 \u417 ng kh\'f4ng g\u7885 i anh!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! G\u7885 i c\'f3 th\'e8m nghe m\'e1y \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Hai ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t l\'fac r\u7891 i \u273 i \u259 n, v\u7915 a u\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u v\u7915 a t\'e2m s\u7921 , th\'ec ra Qu\u7923 nh d\'e0nh d\u7909 m \u273 \u432 \u7907 c ti\u7873 n v\'e0 th\'eam \'edt ti\u7873 n t\'f4i cho n\u7919 a n\'ean m\u7903  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c salon v\'e0 thu\'ea th\'eam ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m. Th\u7845 y g\'f3i qu\'e0 tr\'ean b\'e0n Qu\u7923 nh h\u7887 i t\'f4i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'eam r\u7891 i c\'f2n \u273 \u7883 nh \u273 i t\'e1n t\u7881 nh em n\'e0o m\'e0 qu\'e0 c\'e1p kinh th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'e1n t\uc0\u7881 nh em n\'e0o \u273 \'e2u, qu\'e0 anh t\u7863 ng em \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ? C\'e1i g\'ec \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'ed v\uc0\u7873  th\'ec bi\u7871 t. T\'f2 m\'f2 th\u7871  l\'e0 kh\'f4ng hay.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 i c\u7843  \u273 \'eam th\'ec t\'ed v\u7873  g\'ec m\'e0 v\u7873 ..\u259 n xong m\u7903  ra xem lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Xem lu\'f4n ch\uc0\u7913  t\'ed n\u7919 a m\u7903  ra c\'f2n h\u7913 ng th\'fa g\'ec n\u7919 a. T\u7863 ng em l\'e0 em m\u7903  lu\'f4n nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\uc0\u7863 c l\u432 \u7905 i c\'e1i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec m\u7903  lu\'f4n c\u361 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\'ed h\u7917 ng b\'f3c c\'e1i h\u7897 p qu\'e0 ra th\'ec th\u7845 y c\'e1i v\'e1y r\u7845 t l\'e0 \u273 \u7865 p v\'e0 h\u7907 p v\u7899 i n\u432 \u7899 c da c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh th\'edch l\u7855 m, m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean nh\'ecn t\'f4i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch \'e2u y\u7871 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e2u l\uc0\u7855 m r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai t\u7863 ng qu\'e0 cho em \u273 \u7845 y, m\'e0 \u273 \'fang l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'ecnh c\u361  c\'f3 kh\'e1c, ch\u7885 n c\'e1i n\'e0o chu\u7849 n c\'e1i \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Theo th\'f3i quen th\'f4i, m\'e0 theo th\'f3i quen th\'ec qu\'e1 chu\uc0\u7849 n \u273 i ch\u7913  l\u7841 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i c\u7847 m lu\'f4n \u432 \u7899 m \u432 \u7899 m v\'e0o ng\u7921 c m\'ecnh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y! Th\uc0\u7871  mua cho em th\u7871  n\'e0y Huy\u7873 n c\'f3 bi\u7871 t kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y? N\'f3 bi\u7871 t m\'e0 \u273 \'e1nh em l\'e0 em b\u7855 t \u273 \u7873 n anh \u273 \u7845 y bi\u7871 t ch\u432 a!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'f3i chung c\'f3 m\uc0\u7895 i c\'e1i v\'e1y m\'e0 \u273 \'e1nh ghen th\'ec c\u361 ng h\u417 i ph\'ed \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Bi\uc0\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e0n b\'e0 ghen th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7845 t c\'e1i v\'e1y v\'e0o h\u7897 p qu\'e0 r\u7891 i t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh nh\u7853 u ti\u7871 p \u273 \u7871 n h\u417 n m\u7897 t gi\u7901  \u273 \'eam th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o t\'f4i \u273 i nh\'e0 ngh\u7881  lu\'f4n. C\'f3 t\'ed r\u432 \u7907 u v\'e0o ng\u432 \u7901 i t\'f4i c\u361 ng ph\'ea ph\'ea r\u7891 i n\'ean g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. C\u7843  hai l\u7919 ng th\u7919 ng l\u7853 t \u273 \u7853 t d\'ecu nhau v\'e0o trong kh\'e1ch s\u7841 n r\u7891 i l\u259 n lu\'f4n ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 chu\u7849 n b\u7883  s\u7861 n \u273 \u7891  gi\u7843 i r\u432 \u7907 u r\u7891 i, v\u7855 t b\u7889 n n\u259 m \u7911 a chanh l\'e0m hai c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c, cho th\'eam m\u7897 t \'edt \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng v\'e0o r\u7891 i l\u7845 y \u273 \'e1 trong t\u7911  l\u7841 nh b\u7887  th\u7853 t nhi\u7873 u v\'e0o, Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 a cho t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y u\uc0\u7889 ng \u273 i anh! U\u7889 ng cho \u273 \u7905  kh\'e1t n\u432 \u7899 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7847 m l\u7845 y c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c t\'f4i u\u7889 ng m\u7897 t ph\'e1t h\u7871 t lu\'f4n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e2u l\uc0\u7855 m r\u7891 i kh\'f4ng ph\'ea nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0y, r\u432 \u7907 u n\'e0y n\'f3 chu\u7849 n ph\u7871 t \u273 \u7845 y, u\u7889 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y m\'e0 ch\u432 a th\u7845 y \u273 au \u273 \u7847 u g\'ec c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i u\u7889 ng h\u7871 t c\u7889 c n\u432 \u7899 c sau \u273 \'f3 tr\u432 \u7901 n ra, \'f4m nh\u7865  l\u7845 y t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ph\'ea th\uc0\u7871  n\'e0y c\'f3 c\'f2n l\'e0m \u259 n tr\'f2 tr\u7889 ng g\'ec \u273 \u432 \u7907 c kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 R\uc0\u432 \u7907 u v\'e0o c\'e0ng h\u259 ng ch\u7913  sao, ch\u7881  s\u7907  em kh\'f4ng h\u259 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'f4i !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! Em l\'e0 em h\u417 i b\u7883  h\u259 ng h\u417 n \u273 \u7845 y, quan tr\u7885 ng l\'e0 anh c\'f3 d\'e1m kh\'f4ng th\'f4i. Huy\u7873 n m\'e0 bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec c\'f3 m\'e0 n\'f3 c\u7855 t ti\u7871 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 G\uc0\u7899 m! Th\u7871  th\'f4i anh v\u7873  \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Chu\uc0\u7849 n b\u7883  \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 a b\'e0n tay m\u7873 m m\u7841 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c s\u417 n m\'f3ng t\u7881  m\u7849 n k\'e9o t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 M\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \'f9a c\'e1i th\'f4i m\'e0 \u273 \'e3 gi\u7853 n r\u7891 i \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 L\uc0\u7855 c \u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ph\uc0\u7843 i gi\u7853 n m\'e0 l\'e0 s\u7907 , nh\u7905  Huy\u7873 n bi\u7871 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec l\u7841 i bu\u7891 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ha ha! Em \uc0\u273 \'f9a \u273 \u7845 y, kh\'f4ng ph\'e1 v\u7905  h\u7841 nh ph\'fac c\u7911 a anh \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 V\uc0\u7915 a n\u7857 m xu\u7889 ng th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 tr\u432 \u7901 n l\'ean \'f4m l\u7845 y t\'f4i r\u7891 i \u273 \'e8 t\'f4i ra ng\u7845 u nghi\u7871 n m\'e0 h\'f4n r\u7891 i. T\'f4i \u273 o\'e1n ch\u7855 c c\u417 n kh\'e1t t\'ecnh c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u tr\u7895 i d\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'f9i r\uc0\u432 \u7907 u, m\'f9i n\u432 \u7899 c chanh r\u7891 i m\'f9i th\'e2n th\u7875  c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh qu\u7879 n v\'e0o nhau t\u7841 o ra m\u7897 t m\'f9i kh\'f3 t\u7843  l\u7855 m. Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u432 a h\u7859 n l\u432 \u7905 i v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i t\'f4i th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \'e0nh n\'fat l\u432 \u7905 i Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i t\'f4i m\u7899 i kh\u7869  xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e8 l\'ean ng\u432 \u7901 i Qu\u7923 nh tay xoa xoa c\'e1i b\u7847 u v\'fa trong c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t c\'e1ch \u273 i\u7879 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7917  v\'e1y anh xem n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, c\u7903 i c\'e1i v\'e1y ngo\'e0i ra r\u7891 i thay v\'e1y. So v\u7899 i l\'fac m\u7845 y th\'e1ng tr\u432 \u7899 c g\u7863 p t\'f4i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\'e9o h\u417 n h\u7859 n nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng x\u7891  x\u7873  m\'e0 \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\uc0\u7869  h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em l\'ean c\'e2n \uc0\u273 \u7845 y \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 V\'e2ng! B\'e9o l\'ean nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\u7855 m \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng b\'e9o l\'ean m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n, g\u7847 y \u7889 m y\u7871 u nh\u432  c\'e1ch \u273 \'e2y m\u7845 y th\'e1ng m\u7899 i khi\u7871 p.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n l\'fac \u273 \'f3 g\u7847 y th\u7853 t. Gi\u7901  \u273 \u7905  h\u417 n r\u7891 i, l\'e0m salon t\'f3c ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng l\'e0m th\u7871  kia n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i b\uc0\u297 u m\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng l\'e0m th\uc0\u7871  kia ch\u7855 c kinh nghi\u7879 m qu\'ean h\u7871 t nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n l\'e2u m\uc0\u7899 i c\'f3 chuy\u7879 n qu\'ean nghe ch\u432 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\uc0\u7863 c xong c\'e1i v\'e1y Qu\u7923 nh \u273 ong \u273 \u432 a tr\u432 \u7899 c m\u7863 t t\'f4i m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i kh\u7869  b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y mang v\u7873  c\u7845 t t\u7911 , th\u7881 nh tho\u7843 ng mang ra m\u7863 c th\'f4i ch\u7913  m\u7863 c r\'e1ch l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ai mua ti\u7871 p cho n\u7919 a nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914  \u273 \'fang r\u7891 i \u273 \u7845 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh h\u7913  m\u7897 t ti\u7871 ng r\u7891 i l\u7841 i tr\u432 \u7901 n ra r\u7891 i xoa xoa l\'ean ng\u7921 c \'e1o t\'f4i, m\u7845 y ng\'f3n tay nhanh tho\u259 n tho\u7855 t \u273 \'e3 bung h\u7871 t c\'fac \'e1o l\'fac n\'e0o kh\'f4ng hay.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lu\uc0\u7891 n n\u259 m \u273 \u7847 u ngon tay v\'e0o, Qu\u7923 nh g\'e3i nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i n\'fam t\'ed nh\u7887  x\'edu c\u7911 a t\'f4i r\u7891 i v\'e2n v\'ea n\'f3 m\'e0 n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'f4m nay cho em xin \uc0\u273 \u7913 a \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9, xin xong l\'e0 em v\'e0o S\'e0i G\'f2n lu\'f4n kh\'f4ng \u7903  \u273 \'e2y n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'d4m kh\uc0\u7869  Qu\u7923 nh r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Xin nh\uc0\u7905  kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng \uc0\u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\'ec th\'f4i. Nh\u432 ng m\'e0 c\u7913  xin, m\u7845 t g\'ec \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 kh\'f4ng xin nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh nghi\'eang ng\u432 \u7901 i, x\'f5a m\'e1i t\'f3c ra r\u7891 i c\'fai xu\u7889 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u li\u7871 m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'ean ng\u7921 c r\u7891 i ng\u7853 m c\'e1i n\'fam ti m\'e0 m\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 B\uc0\u7843 n n\u259 ng l\'e0m t\'ecnh chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 hi\u7879 n ra. Qu\u7923 nh say m\'ea li\u7871 m m\'fat r\u7891 i lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng c\u7903 i c\'e1i th\u7855 t l\u432 ng r\u7891 i c\'fac qu\u7847 n ra lu\u7891 n tay xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u xoa xoa con c\u7863 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 U\uc0\u7889 ng r\u432 \u7907 u v\'e0o r\u7891 i n\'ean ch\u7881  c\u7847 n Qu\u7923 nh xoa xao m\u7845 y c\'e1i l\'e0 n\'f3 d\u7921 ng \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean. T\'f4i m\u7899 i \u273 \u7847 u c\u7913  \u273 \u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh mu\u7889 n l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec l\'e0m nh\u432 ng sau \u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng k\'ecm ch\u7871  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, tay b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u v\'e9n c\'e1i v\'e1y l\'ean r\u7891 i xoa xoa c\'e1i b\u7901  m\'f4ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 Vu\uc0\u7889 t nh\u7865  d\u7885 c theo c\'e1i khe m\'f4ng xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'fang c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n th\'ec t\'f4i th\u7845 y \u273 \u361 ng qu\u7847 n l\'f3t \u432 \u7899 t \u432 \u7899 t r\u7891 i. Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'fang l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i ph\u7909  n\u7919  thu\u7897 c h\'e0ng d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng.\
