\cf2 \cb3 L\uc0\u7845 y ng\'f3n tr\u7887  t\'f4i ch\u7885 c ch\u7885 c m\u7845 y c\'e1i v\'e0o c\'e1i khe r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c ra nhi\u7873 u r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y! Th\u7871  c\'e1i l\u7847 n g\u7863 p anh v\u7899 i b\u7889 n th\u7857 ng x\u259 m tr\u7893  \u7845 y th\'ec ch\'fang n\'f3 l\'e0m nh\u432  th\u7871  n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ng\u7849 ng l\'ean m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i n\u7857 m sang b\'ean c\u7841 nh, tay n\u7855 m con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i x\u7909 c x\u7909 c r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u k\u7875 :\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \'f3 th\'ec ngh\u297  t\u7909 i n\'e0y th\'e1c lo\u7841 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i, m\u7895 i th\u7857 ng gi\u7887 i l\u7855 m l\'e0m hai c\'e1i r\u7891 i th\'f4i nh\u432 ng ai ng\u7901  t\u7909 i n\'f3 \u273 \u7853 p \u273 \'e1 n\'ean qu\u7845 t nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec em c\u361 ng ch\u417 i v\'e0o m\'e0 qu\u7845 t l\u7841 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em kh\'f4ng d\'ednh v\'e0o m\uc0\u7845 y th\u7913  \u273 \'f3, k\u7879  th\'f4i. Em c\'f2n ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng con b\'e9 \u273 i c\'f9ng th\'ec kh\'f4ng quen, m\'e0 con b\'e9 \u7845 y h\'e0ng h\u7885  xinh h\u417 n n\'ean m\u7845 y th\u7857 ng \u273 \'f3 nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh h\u417 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\u7873  h\u7873  n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'e0ng h\uc0\u7885  c\'f3 to kh\'f4ng m\'e0 s\u7907  th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! To l\'e0m sao b\u7857 ng c\u7911 a anh \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nh\u432 ng m\'e0 t\u7909 i n\'f3 to\'e0n d\'f9ng bao gai th\'f4i, \u273 \'e2m ph\'e1t n\'e0o t\'ea ph\'e1t \u273 \u7845 y, l\'fac \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec s\u432 \u7899 ng nh\u432 ng m\'e0 sau th\'ec r\'e1t kh\'f4ng th\u7875  n\'e0o ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  l\'fac \u273 \'f3 r\'e1t nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec ph\u7843 i l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 D\'f9ng gel ch\uc0\u7913  l\'e0m th\u7871  n\'e0o n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i t\'f2 m\'f2 h\uc0\u7887 i th\'eam:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\u7889 n ng\u432 \u7901 i nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'ec ch\u7855 c ch\u417 i c\u7843  l\u7895  nh\u7883  ch\u7913  nh\u7881 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i k\u7875  ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec d\uc0\u297  nhi\'ean t\u7909 i n\'f3 c\'f3 c\'e1i l\u7895  n\'e0o \u273 \'fat \u273 \u432 \u7907 c v\'e0o th\'ec ch\'fang n\'f3 \u273 \'fat th\'f4i. Em kia ch\u432 a ch\u417 i ki\u7875 u \u273 \'f3 bao gi\u7901  n\'ean g\'e0o \u7847 m l\'ean t\u7909 i n\'f3 c\u361 ng kh\'f4ng c\'f3 tha. B\'ecnh th\u432 \u7901 ng th\'ec ai c\u361 ng l\'e0m nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng nh\u432 ng h\'f4m \u273 \'f3 b\u7889 n th\u7857 ng ch\'f3 ch\u7871 t l\'e0m nh\u432  ki\u7875 u hi\u7871 p d\'e2m t\u7909 i em v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  sao kh\'f4ng c\u7847 m k\'e9o c\u7855 t lu\'f4n \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7889 n th\u7857 ng nh\u432  th\u7871  th\'ec c\u7847 m k\'e9o ki\u7875 u g\'ec m\'e0 c\u7855 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, h\'ec h\'ec.. nh\u432 ng th\'f4i chuy\u7879 n c\u361  r\u7891 i nh\u7855 c l\u7841 i l\'e0m g\'ec!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh h\uc0\u7887 i th\'eam ch\'fat n\u7919 a th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\'f2 m\'f2 th\uc0\u7871  h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec t\'f2 m\'f2 m\uc0\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u \u273 \'e2u, th\u7871  em ch\u7881  b\u7883  hai th\u7857 ng \u7845 n v\'e0o th\'f4i h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng, l\'fac nhi\uc0\u7873 u nh\u7845 t l\'e0 ba th\u7857 ng, m\u7897 t th\u7857 ng doggy em b\u7857 ng l\u7895  nh\u7883 , th\u7857 ng \u7903  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i \u7845 n v\'e0o l\u7891 n c\'f2n m\u7897 t th\u7857 ng b\u7855 t em BJ.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u432 \u7901 ng t\u432 \u7907 ng ra c\'e1c c\u7843 nh trong nh\u7919 ng b\u7897  phim sex t\'f4i xem n\'f3 ch\u7859 ng kh\'e1c so v\u7899 i l\u7901 i mi\'eau t\u7843  c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh l\'e0 m\u7845 y. T\'f4i th\u7847 m ngh\u297  \'93 b\u7883  bao nhi\'eau th\u7857 ng \u273 \u7883 t th\u7871  ch\u7855 c b\'e2y gi\u7901  to\'e1c ra r\u7891 i, m\'ecnh \u273 \u7883 t ch\u7855 c ki\u7875 u \u273 u\'f4i chu\u7897 t ngo\'e1y l\u7885  m\u7905 \'94.\cb1 \
\cb3 Ngh\uc0\u297  nh\u432  v\u7853 y th\'f4i nh\u432 ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m n\'f3i v\u7853 y m\'e0 ch\u7881  k\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7897 i em qu\'e1 nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y t\u7897 i em th\'ec ph\u7843 i cho em m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i m\uc0\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Cho em m\uc0\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a \'e1? L\u7845 y ch\u7891 ng th\'ec em xin ch\u7891 ng em bao nhi\'eau \u273 \u7913 a m\'e0 ch\u7859 ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Quan tr\uc0\u7885 ng l\'e0 em kh\'f4ng mu\u7889 n l\u7845 y ch\u7891 ng, ch\u7881  c\'f3 mu\u7889 n m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a con l\'e0 \u273 \u7911  th\'f4i h\'ec h\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec th\'ec Qu\uc0\u7923 nh x\'f3c cho con c\u7863 c c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y ch\u7855 c ch\u7855 n c\'f3 \u273 \u7913 a \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7845 y anh \u7841 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Ch\uc0\u432 a k\u7883 p tr\u7843  l\u7901 i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'fai ngay xu\u7889 ng h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng ra m\'e0 m\'fat ch\u7909 t ch\u7909 t l\u7845 y con c\u7863 c m\u7897 t c\'e1ch ngon l\'e0nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u7847 n m\u7851 n li\u7871 m l\'e1m t\u7915  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u kh\u7845 c xu\u7889 ng d\u7847 n c\'e1i g\u7889 c c\u7863 c sau \u273 \'f3 li\u7871 m l\'e1p l\'ean tr\'ean ch\u259 m ch\u7881  nh\u432  m\u7897 t con ong h\'fat m\u7853 t v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Lim dim m\uc0\u7855 t t\'f4i t\u7853 n h\u432 \u7903 ng c\u7843 m gi\'e1c \u7845 m \'e1m m\u7873 m m\u7841 i \u432 \u7899 t \'e1t t\u7915  \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i truy\u7873 n sang. M\'fat cho con c\u7863 c b\'f3ng nh\u7851 y th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh xoay ng\u432 \u7901 i, k\'e9o c\u7843  c\'e1i qu\u7847 n t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng m\'e0 li\u7871 m l\'e1m \u273 \u7871 n hai h\'f2n d\'e1i r\u7891 i \u273 \u7871 n c\'e1i \u273 \'f9i sau \u273 \'f3 l\u7841 i l\'ean ng\u7921 c m\'e0 h\'f4n n\'fam ti.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u417 n n\u7917 a ti\u7871 ng sau th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh d\u7915 ng l\u7841 i, ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m c\u7903 i c\'e1i v\'e1y c\u7911 a minh sang m\u7897 t b\'ean r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 B\uc0\u7887  ra kh\'f4ng nh\'e0u h\u7871 t!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i ch\uc0\u7881  c\u432 \u7901 i r\u7891 i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y, \u273 \u432 a tay xoa xoa l\u7845 y l\u7845 y b\u7847 u v\'fa th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\u7903 i c\'e1i \'e1o l\'f3t m\u7887 ng tang b\u7857 ng ren ra, c\'e1i n\'fam v\'fa t\u7921  nhi\'ean h\u7891 ng r\u7921 c l\'ean t\'f4i th\u7845 y v\u7853 y h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao l\uc0\u7841 i h\u7891 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i h\'edp m\u7855 t n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em phun l\uc0\u7841 i cho h\u7891 ng \u7845 y m\'e0.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec t\'f4i h\u7887 i ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i c\'f3 l\'e0m l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7845 y?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 L\'e0m l\'e0 l\'e0m l\uc0\u7841 i h\u7871 t ch\u7913 , l\'e0m l\u7841 i r\u7891 i th\u7871  n\'ean anh ph\u7843 i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i h\'e0 h\'e0 ki\u7875 u th\'edch ch\'ed r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'e3 bao gi\u7901  anh l\'e0m m\u7841 nh \u273 \'e2u, to\'e0n y\'eau chi\u7873 u t\u7915  tr\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \u7871 n gi\u7901  v\u7851 n th\u7871  c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. N\'e0o c\u7903 i ra xem s\u7917 a th\u7871  n\'e0o n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn b\'ean ngo\'e0i th\'ec bi\uc0\u7871 t m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i, quan tr\u7885 ng l\'e0 b\'ean trong c\u417 . Ki\u7875 u g\'ec c\u361 ng th\u7845 y kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4 th\uc0\u7853 t \'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Chuy\uc0\u7879 n, m\u7845 t g\u7847 n ch\u7909 c tri\u7879 u c\u7911 a em \u273 \u7845 y \'edt \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\'ed h\uc0\u7917 ng t\'f4i ng\u7891 i d\u7853 y s\'e1t m\'e9p gi\u432 \u7901 ng. Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng l\'ean r\u7891 i kh\u7869  \u273 \u7863 t nh\u7865  tay l\'ean vai t\'f4i. Nh\'ecn c\'e1i b\u7909 ng thon nh\u7887  v\'e0 mu l\u7891 n c\u259 ng m\u7885 ng th\u7845 p tho\'e1ng trong c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t khi\u7871 n t\'f4i ch\u7881  mu\u7889 n k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n th\u7853 t nhanh xu\u7889 ng \u7845 n v\'e0o m\'e0 nh\u7845 p th\'f4i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'fai xu\uc0\u7889 ng h\'f4n l\'ean c\'e1i mu r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m k\'e9o c\'e1i qu\u7847 n l\'f3t xu\u7889 ng m\u7897 t c\'e1ch t\u7915  t\u7889 n. C\'e1i mu l\u7891 n m\'fap r\u7909 p d\u7847 n d\u7847 n hi\u7879 n ra. Qu\u7923 nh t\u7849 y h\u7871 t l\'f4ng ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\u7841 o n\u7919 a n\'ean n\'f3 tr\u7855 ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng, so v\u7899 i Huy\u7873 n th\'ec tr\u7855 ng h\u417 n nhi\u7873 u.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\'e9o h\u417 n m\u7845 y c\'e2n n\'ean c\'e1i mu c\'e0ng m\u7885 ng, c\'e1i khe kh\'edt khao ch\u7841 y d\u7885 c t\'e1ch c\'e1i mu m\'fap m\u7909 p th\'e0nh hai n\u7917 a t\'f4ng nh\u432  hai m\'fai m\'edt v\u7853 y.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7845 y t\'f4i ch\u7857 m ch\u7857 m nh\'ecn v\'e0o c\'e1i mu th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7845 y c\'f3 kh\'e1c kh\'f4ng n\'e0o?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\'ecn th\uc0\u7871  ki\u7875 u n\'e0y th\'ec ch\u432 a th\u7845 y kh\'e1c l\u7855 m, em b\'e9o l\'ean c\'e1i mu m\'fap ra th\'f4i\'85 nh\u432 ng c\'f3 v\u7867  kh\'edt h\u417 n \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u th\'ec t\'f4i nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i c\u7911 a m\'ecnh ra r\u7891 i ch\u7847 m ch\u7853 m li\u7871 m nh\u7865  nh\u7865  t\u7915  c\'e1i b\u7909 ng xu\u7889 ng kh\u7869  c\'e1i mu.\cb1 \
\cb3 H\uc0\u432 \u417 ng th\u417 m nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng len l\u7887 i v\'e0o m\u361 i t\'f4i l\'e0m t\'f4i h\u7913 ng l\'ean b\'e8n b\u7843 o Qu\u7923 nh:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i n\uc0\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i anh m\'fat c\'e1i n\'e0o, n\'f3 m\u7885 ng qu\'e1.. mu\u7889 n c\u7855 n l\u7855 m r\u7891 i \u273 \'e2y n\'e0y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7912 ! Em mu\u7889 n anh li\u7871 m ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7913 ng n\'e0y m\u7897 t t\'ed n\u7919 a c\u417 ..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 T\uc0\u7915  l\'fac n\'e0o l\u7841 i th\'edch ki\u7875 u \u273 \u7913 ng n\'e0y th\u7871 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Em c\uc0\u361 ng ch\u7859 ng bi\u7871 t, c\u7913  g\u7847 n anh l\'e0 em th\'edch ki\u7875 u n\'e0y, h\'ec h\'ec. N\'f3i chung l\'e0 l\'e0m v\u7899 i anh th\'edch ki\u7875 u nh\u7865  nh\'e0ng l\u7855 m.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u432 \u7901 i m\u7897 t c\'e1ch th\'edch th\'fa r\u7891 i t\'f4i k\'e9o s\'e1t Qu\u7923 nh v\'e0o h\u417 n r\u7891 i ch\'fa m\'f4i ra h\'f4n nh\u7865  l\'ean c\'e1i mu r\u7891 i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i nh\u7865  nh\u7865 .\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u432 \u7899 c mi\u7871 ng ch\u7843 y ra tr\'ean c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i khi\u7871 n cho c\'e1i mu l\u7891 n \u432 \u7899 t h\u7859 n. C\u7889  g\u7855 ng \u273 \u432 a \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i xu\u7889 ng d\u432 \u7899 i c\'e1i khe th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i th\u7845 y n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n b\'ean trong r\u7881  ra.\cb1 \
\cb3 Kh\'f4ng nhi\uc0\u7873 u l\u7855 m nh\u432 ng \u273 \u7911  l\'e0m cho c\'e1i khe \u432 \u7899 t \u432 \u7899 t. Ch\u7885 c nh\u7865  nh\u7865  c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i gi\u7919 a c\'e1i khe th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh run l\'ean k\'eau:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i th\'edch qu\'e1\'85 \uc0\u273 \'e3 kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c n\u7919 a anh \u417 i\'85 em th\'edch l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.. n\u7857 m ra anh li\u7871 m cho em nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao v\uc0\u7915 a b\u7843 o th\'edch \u273 \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y cho anh li\u7871 m gi\u7901  l\u7841 i n\u7857 m l\'e0 sao?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\'edch.. \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng th\u7871  n\'e0y m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'f4i ch\u7913  th\'e8m\'85l\u7855 m kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900  th\'ec n\u7857 m ra \u273 i anh coi xem s\u7917 a th\u7871  n\'e0o n\'e0o, xem c\'f3 \u273 \'e1ng ti\u7873 n kh\'f4ng n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u417 i b\u7883  \u273 \'e1ng \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  \'e1? C\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o d\'f9ng r\u7891 i v\'e0 \u273 \'e1nh gi\'e1 hay sao m\'e0 ph\'e1t bi\u7875 u chu\u7849 n th\u7871  ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ch\uc0\u432 a c\'f3 ai c\u7843  nh\u432 ng \u273 o\'e1n th\u7871  h\'ec h\'ec. T\u7915  l\'fac l\'e0m xong c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c quan h\u7879  \u273 \'e2u, ki\'eang h\u417 i b\u7883  l\'e2u \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9, nhi\u7873 u l\'fac h\u7913 ng l\u7855 m \u273 \u7845 y nh\u432 ng ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t t\u7921  x\u7917 !\cb1 \
\cb3 Mu\uc0\u7889 n tr\'eau Qu\u7923 nh n\'ean t\'f4i n\'f3i \u273 \'f9a:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  th\'ec l\u7845 y d\u432 a chu\u7897 t hay c\'e0 t\'edm th\u7871  ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 H\uc0\u7913 ! L\u7841 i tr\'eau em r\u7891 i. D\'f9ng tay th\'f4i ch\u7913  c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c d\'f9ng m\u7845 y c\'e1i linh tinh \u273 \'e2u. C\'f3 th\'ec d\'f9ng c\'e1i kh\'e1c ch\u7913  d\u432 a leo c\'e0 t\'edm c\'e1i g\'ec.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7875  cho Qu\u7923 nh n\u7857 m ra gi\u432 \u7901 ng c\'f2n t\'f4i ng\u7855 m c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n kh\'edt khao th\u7871  n\'e0o. C\'f4ng nh\u7853 n l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u273 i s\u7917 a l\u7841 i kh\'e1c h\u7859 n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n th\'e2m \uc0\u273 en n\u7919 a m\'e0 h\u7891 ng h\'e0o l\'ean h\u7859 n, hai c\'e1i m\'e9p b\'ean d\u432 \u7899 i kh\'edt l\u7841 i kh\'f4ng c\'f2n n\u7871 p th\u7883 t th\u7915 a n\'e0o c\u7843 .\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u432 a ng\'f3n tay l\'ean day day c\'e1i mu r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t xu\u7889 ng banh hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n ra th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng hi\uc0\u7875 u sao t\u7915  l\'fac l\'e0m l\u7841 i, em xoa xoa c\'e1i h\u7897 t le c\u7911 a em c\'f3 m\u7897 t t\u7865 o th\'f4i m\'e0 n\u432 \u7899 c ch\u7843 y ra bao nhi\'eau \u7845 y, ch\u7881  \u273 \u7897 ng m\u7897 t ch\'fat th\'f4i l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ha ha! C\uc0\u7843 m gi\'e1c kh\'e1c bi\u7879 t \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh m\u7881 m c\u432 \u7901 i th\'ec t\'f4i v\u7895  nh\u7865  nh\u7865  l\'ean c\'e1i mu m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t d\u7885 c c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ng\'f3n tr\u7887  xu\u7889 ng \u273 \'fang c\'e1i h\u7897 t le xoay tr\'f2n, c\'e0ng xoay th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n c\'e0ng ch\u7843 y ra nhi\u7873 u, n\'f3 tr\u7855 ng x\'f3a hai c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n th\'ec t\'f4i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh li\uc0\u7871 m nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i n\'f3i th\'eam:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh v\uc0\u7915 a li\u7871 m v\u7915 a ch\u7885 c m\u7897 t ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o m\'f3c m\'f3c cho em nh\'e9! Em th\'edch v\u7915 a m\'f3c v\u7915 a li\u7871 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7900 ! \u272 \u432 \u7907 c r\u7891 i, l\'e0m nh\u432  ki\u7875 u em th\'edch lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 N\'f3i xong t\'f4i b\uc0\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i qu\'e9t d\u7885 c theo hai c\'e1i m\'e9p th\u7883 t h\u7891 ng h\u7891 ng thu h\u7871 t \u273 \'e1m n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n tr\u7855 ng \u273 \u7909 c v\'e0o trong mi\u7879 ng.\cb1 \
\cb3 \uc0\u272 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i cu\u7889 n l\u7845 y c\'e1i m\'e9p l\u7891 n th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh th\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \'d4i \uc0\u273 \'e3 anh \u417 i.. th\'edch qu\'e1.. l\'e2u l\u7855 m m\u7899 i c\'f3 c\u7843 m gi\'e1c n\'e0y.. m\u7845 y th\'e1ng r\u7891 i.. n\'fat m\u7841 nh c\'e1i m\'e9p c\u7911 a em \u273 i anh..em th\'edch n\'fat l\u7891 n qu\'e1 anh \u417 i.\u432 ..\u432 .\u432  \u432 .\u432 .a.a. s\u432 \u7899 ng.\u432 .. anh n\'fat l\u7891 n em s\u432 \u7899 ng qu\'e1.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh r\'ean nh\u432  v\u7853 y t\'f4i n\'fat m\u7841 nh h\u417 n r\u7891 i ng\u7849 ng l\'ean b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f4ng nh\uc0\u7853 n l\'e0 n\'f3 h\u7891 ng th\u7853 t th\u7853 t \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u431 \'85th\u7871  h\u7843  anh..em c\u361 ng c\'f3 nh\'ecn \u273 \u432 \u7907 c k\u297  \u273 \'e2u.. ch\u7881  c\u7843 m th\u7845 y l\'e0 n\'f3 \u273 \u7865 p h\u417 n tr\u432 \u7899 c th\'f4i \u432 ..\u432 ..\u432  n\'fat c\'e1i m\'e9p c\u7911 a em r\u7891 i li\u7871 m h\u7897 t le..n\'fat lu\'f4n n\'f3 n\u7919 a anh nhe..em th\'e8m qu\'e1..\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nghi\uc0\u7879 n m\u7845 y th\'e1ng gi\u7901  m\u7899 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7887 a m\'e3n \u273 \u7845 y h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh lim dim g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u r\u7891 i c\u7889  g\u7855 ng d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra h\u417 n v\'e0 \u7845 n c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u t\'f4i xu\u7889 ng. C\u7889  g\u7855 ng li\u7871 m th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u432 a m\u7897 t ng\'f3n tay v\'e0o b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  m\'e0 m\'f3c.\
