\cb3 \'96 H\'f4 h\'f4.. ph\uc0\u7843 i v\u7855 t th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec m\u7899 i c\'f3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a ch\u7913 ! \u272 ang \u273 i xin m\'e0!\cb1 \
