\cb3 Th\uc0\u7903  h\u7893 n h\u7875 n t\'f4i nh\'ecn b\u7901  m\'f4ng c\u259 ng m\u7885 ng \u273 \u7887  n\u7921 ng l\'ean khi t\'f4i v\u7895  v\'e0o th\'ec t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \u7845 y th\u7887 a m\'e3n r\u7891 i nh\'e9, nh\u432 ng m\'e0 xin \u273 \u7913 a con l\'e0 kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u273 \'e2u \u273 \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh quay \u273 \u7847 u l\u7841 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Sao m\'e0 kh\'f4ng? K\uc0\u7879  ch\u7913  em kh\'f4ng n\'f3i th\'ec c\'f3 ai bi\u7871 t \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nh\uc0\u432 ng m\'e0 th\u7845 y ki\u7875 u ki\u7875 u g\'ec \u7845 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u g\'ec l\'e0 ki\u7875 u g\'ec\'85 v\'f4 t\u432  \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 N\uc0\u7857 m m\u7897 t l\'fac th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh mon men \u273 \u7871 n \'f4m t\'f4i r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y kh\'e9o mai kia c\'f3 th\'ec ph\uc0\u7843 i b\u7843 o con anh v\u7899 i con em kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c c\u432 \u7899 i nhau \u273 \u7845 y nh\u7881 , n\'f3 m\'e0 c\u432 \u7899 i lo\u7841 n lu\'e2n lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec \uc0\u273 \'f3 kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\'e0 t\u7889 t nh\u7845 t.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3i g\'ec m\'e0 x\u7883  c\'e1i m\u7863 t c\u7911 a m\'ecnh l\u7841 i, c\'f3 l\u7869  Qu\u7923 nh khao kh\'e1t c\'f3 m\u7897 t \u273 \u7913 a con v\u7899 i t\'f4i th\u7853 t. \u272 \'e0nh xoa xoa c\'e1i m\'f4ng t\'f4i d\u7895  d\'e0nh Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7875  m\u7863 c k\u7879  r\u7891 i t\'e2m s\u7921  ti\u7871 p. N\u7857 m n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n nh\u432 ng b\'e0n tay Qu\u7923 nh ch\u7859 ng th\u7875  n\'e0o d\u7901 i \u273 \u432 \u7907 c con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i m\u7863 c d\'f9 n\'f3 m\u7873 m nh\u361 n r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 M\'e2n m\'ea t\uc0\u7915 ng c\u7885 ng l\'f4ng \u273 en nh\'e1nh r\u7891 i vu\u7889 t hai h\'f2n d\'e1i Qu\u7923 nh kh\u7869  h\u7887 i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7902  nh\'e0 em Huy\u7873 n c\'f3 chi\u7873 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c anh th\u7871  n\'e0y kh\'f4ng?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f3 ch\uc0\u7913 ! K\u297  thu\u7853 t kh\'f4ng b\u7857 ng em nh\u432 ng m\'e0 \u273 am m\'ea c\'f3 nhi\u7873 u l\u7855 m.. nhi\u7879 t t\'ecnh lu\'f4n\'85 ch\u7891 ng m\'e0!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh c\u432 \u7901 i h\'ec h\'ec r\u7891 i b\u7843 o ti\u7871 p:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7871  theo anh ngo\'e0i ch\u7891 ng ra Huy\u7873 n \u273 \'e3 \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u7843 i nghi\u7879 m con c\u7863 c n\'e0o kh\'e1c ch\u432 a? \u272 \u7845 y l\'e0 em h\u7887 i \u273 \u7845 y nh\'e9 ch\u7913  kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i l\'e0 \u273 \u7863 t nghi v\u7845 n cho anh \u273 \'e2u.\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i ph\'e1 l\'ean n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'e1i n\'e0y th\'ec anh ngh\uc0\u297  ch\u7855 c l\'e0 ch\u432 a, Huy\u7873 n tr\'f4ng th\u7871  th\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  th\'e1c lo\u7841 n, d\'e2m \u273 \'e3ng v\'f4 c\'f9ng tr\'ean gi\u432 \u7901 ng nh\u432 ng chuy\u7879 n \u273 \'f3 ch\u7855 c l\'e0 kh\'f4ng d\'e1m \u273 \'e2u!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\uc0\u7853 t \'e1!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Anh ngh\uc0\u297  v\u7853 y!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh g\u7853 t g\'f9 r\u7891 i m\'e2n m\'ea ti\u7871 p con c\u7863 c m\u7897 t l\'fac l\'e2u r\u7891 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 N\'e0y anh v\uc0\u7899 i em ra ban c\'f4ng ng\u7855 m bu\u7893 i \u273 \'eam \u273 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i c\uc0\u432 \u7901 i n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'eam th\'ec c\'f3 c\'e1i g\'ec m\'e0 ng\u7855 m, tr\u7901 i th\'ec kh\'f4ng tr\u259 ng kh\'f4ng sao, khuya r\u7891 i l\'e0m g\'ec c\'f3 ai m\'e0 ng\u7855 m!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'ec c\uc0\u7913  ra ngo\'e0i \u273 \'f3 ng\u7855 m r\u7891 i l\'e0m t\'ecnh ngo\'e0i \u273 \'f3..em th\'edch ki\u7875 u l\'e3ng m\u7841 n v\u7853 y. Tr\u432 \u7899 c kia kh\'e9o x\u7875 nh ra m\u7897 t c\'e1i l\'e0 \u273 \'e8 em ra m\'e0 l\'e0m c\'f2n g\'ec n\u7919 a. B\'e2y gi\u7901  ch\u7855 c l\'e0 ch\'ea em h\u7843 ?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Kh\'f4ng ch\'ea \uc0\u273 \'e2u nh\u432 ng m\'e0 s\u7907  ng\u432 \u7901 i kh\'e1c ng\'f3 l\'ean!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u272 \'eam h\'f4m th\u7871  n\'e0y th\'ec ai th\'e8m ng\'f3. N\'e0o ra n\'e0o!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i h\'ec h\uc0\u7913 ng h\u417 n r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ra ban c\'f4ng kh\'f4ng hay, ra lu\'f4n h\'e0nh lang kh\'e1ch s\uc0\u7841 n n\'f3 m\u7899 i m\'e1u ch\u7913 .\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe t\'f4i n\'f3i v\u7853 y m\u7855 t s\'e1ng nh\u432  sao r\u7891 i g\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u \u273 \u7891 ng \'fd. C\u7843  hai h\'ed h\u7917 ng l\'f2 d\'f2 m\u7903  c\u7917 a ra r\u7891 i ch\u7885 n ngay c\'e1i g\'f3c g\u7847 n thang m\'e1y. Qu\u7923 nh ng\u7891 i th\u7909 p xu\u7889 ng m\'e2n m\'ea con c\u7863 c r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y m\'fat m\u7897 t ch\'fat l\u7841 i c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c l\'ean \u273 \'e2y!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i g\uc0\u7853 t \u273 \u7847 u b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! M\'fat \u273 i em.. m\u7841 nh v\'e0o nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u m\'fat m\u7897 t c\'e1ch say m\'ea kh\'f4ng kh\'e1c g\'ec m\u7897  di\u7877 n vi\'ean chuy\'ean nghi\u7879 p c\u7843 , n\'f3i c\'e1ch kh\'e1c \u273 \'e2y c\u361 ng l\'e0 m\u7897 t ngh\u7873  nghi\u7879 p m\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \'e3 l\'e0m trong m\u7897 t hai n\u259 m n\'ean thu\u7847 n th\u7909 c l\u7855 m r\u7891 i.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u l\u432 \u7905 i, \u273 \'f4i b\'e0n tay nhanh ch\'f3ng l\'e0m cho con c\u7863 c c\u7911 a t\'f4i c\u7913 ng ng\u7855 c b\u7853 t t\u432 ng t\u432 ng l\'ean. Ng\'f3 nghi\'eang kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y ai th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh \u273 \u7913 ng d\u7853 y, d\u7841 ng ch\'e2n to ra r\u7891 i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Li\uc0\u7871 m em m\u7845 y c\'e1i r\u7891 i doggy nh\'e9!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i th\'ec kh\'f4ng th\'edch li\uc0\u7871 m l\u7855 m v\'ec ngh\u297  trong l\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh h\'e3y c\'f2n \u273 \u7847 y tinh tr\'f9ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i n\'ean b\'e2y gi\u7901  m\'e0 li\u7871 m th\'ec n\'f3 ch\u7843 y ra m\u7845 t n\'ean t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\'f2n \uc0\u273 \u7847 y tinh tr\'f9ng c\u7911 a anh trong \u273 \u7845 y k\'eca.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh nghe t\'f4i n\'f3i c\u432 \u7901 i kh\'fac kh\'edch b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7911 a anh m\'e0 l\u7841 i s\u7907  \'e0?\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 C\uc0\u7911 a anh anh m\u7899 i s\u7907  ch\u7913  c\u7911 a em th\'ec anh m\'fat h\u7871 t r\u7891 i!\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Th\'f4i m\'e0 li\uc0\u7871 m cho em m\u7897 t t\u7865 o th\'f4i!\cb1 \
\cb3 T\'f4i \uc0\u273 \'e0nh c\'fai xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u432 a l\u432 \u7905 i qu\'e9t d\u7885 c c\'e1i khe l\u7891 n th\'ec n\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n v\u7899 i t\u7881 nh tr\'f9ng n\u7891 ng n\u7891 ng c\u7911 a t\'f4i ch\u7843 y ra, nh\u7855 m m\u7855 t m\'fat h\u7871 t r\u7891 i t\'f4i b\u7843 o:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Khi\uc0\u7871 p nhi\u7873 u qu\'e1.. !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Nhi\uc0\u7873 u th\u7871  m\u7899 i th\'edch!\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh v\u7917 a tr\u7843  l\u7901 i xong th\'ec c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i b\u7845 m thang m\'e1y ra, t\'f4i v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh v\u7897 i n\'e9p sau ch\u7853 u c\'e2y r\u7891 i l\u7911 i d\u7847 n ra ph\'eda c\u7847 u thang b\u7897  v\'ec ch\u7895  n\'e0y t\u432 \u417 ng \u273 \u7889 i khu\u7845 t. Qu\u7923 nh v\u7915 a r\'f3n r\'e9n v\u7915 a n\'f3i:\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 Ki\uc0\u7875 u n\'e0y k\'edch th\'edch th\'e2t.. c\'f2n h\u417 n ng\'e0y x\u432 a \u7845 y nh\u7881 !\cb1 \
\cb3 \'96 \uc0\u7914 ! Anh l\u7841 i n\u7913 ng r\u7891 i, ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng ra \u273 i n\'e0o.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh ngay l\u7853 p t\u7913 c ch\u7893 ng m\'f4ng ra cho t\'f4i c\u7855 m con c\u7863 c v\'e0o m\'e0 \u273 \u7883 t th\u7853 t m\u7841 nh. N\u432 \u7899 c nh\u7901 n \'f3p o\'e1p ch\u7843 y ra th\'ec l\u7841 i c\'f3 ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i khi\u7871 n t\'f4i v\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh ph\u7843 i l\'e0m nh\u7865  l\u7841 i n\'fap v\'e0o g\'f3c. \u272 \u7913 ng \u7903  trong g\'f3c nh\u432 ng con c\u7863 c v\u7851 n th\'f2 th\u7909 t b\'ean trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n khi\u7871 n c\u7843  hai \u273 \u7873 u kh\'f4ng ch\u7883 u \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Kh\'f4ng hi\u7875 u ki\u7875 u n\'e0y th\u7871  n\'e0o m\'e0 ch\u7881  m\u7897 t l\'fac t\'f4i l\u7841 i b\u7855 n \u7847 m \u7847 m tinh tr\'f9ng v\'e0o trong c\'e1i l\u7895  l\u7891 n c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh th\'eam m\u7897 t l\u7847 n n\u7919 a.\cb1 \
\cb3 C\uc0\u7843  hai r\'f3n r\'e9n v\u7873  ph\'f2ng r\u7891 i ng\u7911  \u273 \u7871 n t\u7853 n s\'e1ng h\'f4m sau. S\'e1ng h\'f4m sau t\u7881 nh d\u7853 y v\u7851 n \'f4m Qu\u7923 nh nh\u432 ng t\'f4i g\u7885 i \u273 i\u7879 n cho Huy\u7873 n r\u7891 i n\'f3i chuy\u7879 n m\u7897 t ch\'fat.\cb1 \
\cb3 Sau \uc0\u273 \'eam \u273 \'f3, Qu\u7923 nh x\'f3a m\u7885 i li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i t\'f4i. T\'f4i hoang mang l\u7855 m kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 mang b\u7847 u kh\'f4ng. Huy\u7873 n th\'ec sau khi \u273 \u7907 t c\'f4ng t\'e1c v\u7873 , hai v\u7907  ch\u7891 ng \'e2n \'e1i th\'ec c\'f3 b\u7847 u lu\'f4n.\cb1 \
\cb3 Th\uc0\u7901 i gian th\u7845 m tho\'e1t t\u7893 i \u273 i \u273 \u7871 n b\u7889 n n\u259 m th\'e1ng sau th\'ec t\'f4i m\u7899 i c\'f3 th\u7875  li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i Qu\u7923 nh qua m\u7845 y \u273 \u7913 a ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e0m c\u361  c\u7911 a Qu\u7923 nh.\cb1 \
\cb3 Qu\uc0\u7923 nh chuy\u7875 n v\'e0o mi\u7873 n nam r\u7891 i m\u7903  l\u7841 i m\u7897 t c\u7917 a hi\u7879 u salon, l\'e2n la t\'f4i d\'f2 h\u7887 i m\'e3i th\'ec Qu\u7923 nh c\'f3 b\u7847 u v\u7899 i t\'f4i th\u7853 t nh\u432 ng t\'f4i kh\'f4ng bi\u7871 t l\'e0 Qu\u7923 nh sau n\'e0y c\'f3 mu\u7889 n li\'ean l\u7841 c v\u7899 i t\'f4i n\u7919 a kh\'f4ng.\cb1 \
